NK029(ha)004:1: // gnyis pa nang dbang gi chu bo las /
NK029(ha)004:2: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i dbang gi cho ga lags so //
NK029(ha)004:3: gnyis pa nang dbang gi chu bo la /
NK029(ha)004:4: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga la /
NK029(ha)004:5: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo bya /
NK029(ha)004:8: zhi ba'i dbang bskur ba dbang /
NK029(ha)004:11: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:16: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:17: rab gnas sbyin bsreg ces gsungs pas bdun ste /
NK029(ha)004:22: sku gsung thugs kyi rnam pa bgod pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:26: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad la /
NK029(ha)004:28: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad la /
NK029(ha)004:29: sor bzhi dang 'dzub gang gi tshad do //
NK029(ha)004:30: bum dbang gi dkyil 'khor chung tshad khru gang dang /
NK029(ha)004:32: 'bring tshad la khru bcu ganya sa dang bcu drug /
NK029(ha)004:36: de dag kyang gnas khang yangs dog dang /
NK029(ha)004:37: sbyin bdag 'byor ba che chung gis dbang gis ji ltar rigs par bya'o /
NK029(ha)004:38: phyag len la sngar las dang bya bas sbyangs pa'i skabs su bya ba nyid do //
NK029(ha)004:39: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad la /
NK029(ha)004:42: rab nam mkha'i dbyings bsam yas pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:43: de dag kyang slob dpon dgongs pa zab mi zab dang /
NK029(ha)004:44: slob bu las dag tshabs che chung gi dbang gis
NK029(ha)004:45: 'chad par 'gyur ba'i rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK029(ha)004:47: gnyis pa thig la bdun las /
NK029(ha)004:54: thig lta gon gyi skabs su zin la gdab pa'i thabs dang /
NK029(ha)004:57: thogs mar 'debs pa'i phyag len ni /
NK029(ha)004:58: nang par snga bar langs la /
NK029(ha)004:59: be kra sa ma yam zhes pa'i sngags dang /
NK029(ha)004:61: mdang lhag par gnas pa'i rten dang brten par bcas
NK029(ha)004:62: pa'i dkyil 'khor mdun gyi nam mkha' la bteg nas
NK029(ha)004:64: 'bru'i tshom bu rnams kyang bsdus la /
NK029(ha)004:65: tsha khang la sogs pa 'gong yugs mi 'gro ba'i sar blug la /
NK029(ha)004:66: dkyil 'khor gyi sa gzhi dri bzang po'i chus byug cing /
NK029(ha)004:69: dbang phyug kun bzang gi ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK029(ha)004:70: ye shes kyi thig skud thog nas shar du 'dug /
NK029(ha)004:72: slob bu kun tu bzang mor bskyed la /
NK029(ha)004:73: badz+ra badz+ra zhes gtad cing nub du 'dug /
NK029(ha)004:74: thig byang byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin dkar brengs kyis bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:76: bdag rdo rje slob dpon che ge mo la sogs pa la /
NK029(ha)004:77: dbang bskur ba'i ched du de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK029(ha)004:78: cad kyi sku gsung thugs gsang ba las ches gsang
NK029(ha)004:79: ba / yang gsang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK029(ha)004:80: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs pa'i thig 'debs pas /
NK029(ha)004:81: bdag la mthu bstan du gsol /
NK029(ha)004:84: rdo rje ye shes kyi thig gdab du gsol /
NK029(ha)004:85: phyogs bcu ma lus dus gsum gyi /
NK029(ha)004:86: rgyal ba sras bcas thams cad kun /
NK029(ha)004:87: thig gi sgra 'dis rab bskul nas /
NK029(ha)004:88: byin gyis brlabs par mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)004:89: badz+ra pu tra sa ma ya ma ti kra ya h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:91: gsang gnas kyi thad kar shar nub kyi tshang thig gdab //
NK029(ha)004:92: de nas thig 'gros dang bcas pas /
NK029(ha)004:94: slob ma byang du phyin la /
NK029(ha)004:95: tshig bcad dang sngags gong ltar gyis /
NK029(ha)004:97: de nas slob dpon gyis g.yas bskor gyi shar lho dang /
NK029(ha)004:98: slob ma nub byang du phyin la gong bzhin zur thig gdab /
NK029(ha)004:99: de nas slob dpon lho nub dang /
NK029(ha)004:100: slob ma byang shar du song la gong bzhin gdab /
NK029(ha)004:101: mdun gyis nam mkha' la ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba bsgom /
NK029(ha)004:102: de nas dam tshig gi thig skud sngar bzhin thogs la /
NK029(ha)004:103: phyogs bcu ma lus gyi sogs dang /
NK029(ha)004:104: sa t+wa sho d+ha ni h+aum phata brjod la /
NK029(ha)004:105: sngar bzhin tshangs thig la sogs gdab pas /
NK029(ha)004:106: sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis brlabs pa dang ldan par bsam /
NK029(ha)004:107: dkyil 'khor che chung gang yin gyi tshad cig gam /
NK029(ha)004:110: bcu drug gi cha dgos la zur thig la cha chen bcu gcig yod pa'i mtshan ma byas la /
NK029(ha)004:111: mtshan ma'i thog du thig ring po phyogs bzhi dkar gdab pas /
NK029(ha)004:112: cha chen nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa gcig gam /
NK029(ha)004:116: de la cha bran gdab pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:117: dang po dang drug pa la phyed du gdab cing /
NK029(ha)004:118: de'i phyi ma la'ang phyed du gdab /
NK029(ha)004:119: gnyis pa dang bdun pa cha bran bzhi bzhi mnyam por gdab /
NK029(ha)004:120: gsum pa dang dgu pa phyi dang nang gi cha bran re re gdab /
NK029(ha)004:121: bzhi pa dang bcu pa phyed phyed du gdab /
NK029(ha)004:122: lnga pa dang brgyad pa dbus dor la mtha' gnyis su cha bran re re gdab /
NK029(ha)004:123: cha chen bcu gcig pa ni mi gdag ste /
NK029(ha)004:125: dkyil 'khor la gdab pa'i thig rab gnas dang ldan pa de la /
NK029(ha)004:126: 'gong na bde bar gshegs pa la bskur btab par 'gyur bas /
NK029(ha)004:127: mi 'gong bar bya ba'i don du /
NK029(ha)004:128: hrih zhes pa'i sgra rings por brjod cing /
NK029(ha)004:129: dkyil 'khor gyi thig blos nam mkha' la bsteg nas /
NK029(ha)004:130: ye shes kyi thig dam tshig gi thig skud la /
NK029(ha)004:131: gnyis med du bsres pa de kun bzang /
NK029(ha)004:132: zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK029(ha)004:133: dam tshig gi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK029(ha)004:134: badz+ra muhzhe thig bskud gnyis kyi byin brlabs rang bzhin gyi gnas su gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)004:135: de nas mu khyud bskor ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:136: lte ba nas tshangs thig gi rgyud la cha bran
NK029(ha)004:137: drug pa nas bkor ba lte ba'i mu khyud nang
NK029(ha)004:138: ma bdun pa nas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)004:139: mu khyud phyi ma cha bran bcu bzhi nas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)004:140: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud nang la bco lngas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)004:141: mu khyud phyi gdugs thog gi rtse nas /
NK029(ha)004:143: cha chen bcu pa'i phyed nas bskor ba rdo rje'i ra ba /
NK029(ha)004:145: de ni zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'i thig go zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor 'bring po ni /
NK029(ha)004:146: cha bran lnga pa dang drug pa nas lte ba bskor /
NK029(ha)004:147: bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa nas 'khor lo bskor /
NK029(ha)004:148: cha chen bdun pa'i thog nas glang gur dang rdo rje bskor /
NK029(ha)004:150: dkyil 'khor brgyan pa la lte ba dang rtsibs bzhi bskor lugs gong ltar la /
NK029(ha)004:151: lte ba'i dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi bskor shar rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)004:152: lho'i rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:153: nub rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:154: byang rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhis bskor /
NK029(ha)004:159: me ri rnams gong dang mtshungs so //
NK029(ha)004:160: zhi ba'i tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i dkyil 'khor bri na'ang /
NK029(ha)004:164: dbang phyug rgyas pa'i chas su zhugs ste /
NK029(ha)004:165: sngar rab gnas byas pa'i tshon rnams ni /
NK029(ha)004:166: dkyil 'khor gyi steng du nyer sngogs byas la /
NK029(ha)004:168: 'gying bur ston la phyag g.yas pa'i sor mo lnga la /
NK029(ha)004:169: nyi ma la gnas pa'i dpa' bo 'bru lnga bsam nas /
NK029(ha)004:170: +amo sarba pany+tsa rat+na sa ma ye h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:172: yig 'bru rnams dang tshon rtsi bsres /
NK029(ha)004:173: de nas mtheb 'dzub kyi tshon sngon po 'dzin la /
NK029(ha)004:174: h+aum 'di ni chos dbyings dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)004:175: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir /
NK029(ha)004:176: rim pa dang por yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)004:177: dngos grub dam pa rtsal du gsol /
NK029(ha)004:179: dbus bskor phur gyi shul du cung zhing blag /
NK029(ha)004:180: de nas rtsig pa'i bya nga shar gyi 'tshams su
NK029(ha)004:181: re kha sngon po 'dzub gang pa gcig legs par
NK029(ha)004:182: bri / de'i lhag ma slar dbus kyi khung bur blug /'og ma kun gyi phyag len des 'dre /
NK029(ha)004:184: 'di ni me long dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)004:185: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)004:186: rim pa gnyis par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)004:187: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol /
NK029(ha)004:190: a 'di ni sor rtogs dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)004:191: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)004:192: rim pa gsum par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)004:193: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol /
NK029(ha)004:196: swa 'di ni mnyam nyid dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)004:197: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)004:198: rim pa bzhi par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)004:199: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)004:202: ha 'di ni bya grub dag ba ste /
NK029(ha)004:203: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)004:204: rim pa lnga par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)004:205: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)004:206: brjod pas byang shar mtshams su re kha ljang khu bri /
NK029(ha)004:207: phud lhag dbus kyi khung bur slug la kham lnga
NK029(ha)004:208: dag par bya ba'i don du 'byung ba rim brtsegs
NK029(ha)004:209: bsgom / don la ye shes lnga tshon pa'i rtags
NK029(ha)004:210: rin po che lnga las grub pa'i ri rab tu
NK029(ha)004:211: bsgom / bsgom / ri rab de'i steng du gzhal yas khang bzhengs par bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:213: thog ma song par bya ste /
NK029(ha)004:214: phyis ban rag 'dren pa'i dus su spra brtag cing /
NK029(ha)004:216: de nas zhal lung thob pa'i slob bu rnams kyi lag sor lnga la /
NK029(ha)004:217: nyi ma la gnas pa'i dpa' bo 'bru lngas bskor la /
NK029(ha)004:219: dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi gru chad rtsigs pa mun pa /
NK029(ha)004:233: chu srin kha nas rdo ra /
NK029(ha)004:236: me ri rnams legs par bri'o //
NK029(ha)004:238: gzhan rnams gong dang 'dra ba la /
NK029(ha)004:241: dkyil 'khor brgyas pa la gzhan rnams dkyil 'khor 'bring po dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)004:242: dbus kyi lte ba'i dkyil 'khor lo rtsiiibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:243: shar rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:246: nub rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:249: tshom bu gcig pa dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)004:251: gzhan dkyil 'khor 'bring po dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)004:252: dbus kyi lte bar 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:253: shar rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:254: nub rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi bri'o //
NK029(ha)004:255: tshom bu lnga pa la gzhan tshom bu gsum pa dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)004:256: lho rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:257: byang rtsibs kyi dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi bri'o //
NK029(ha)004:258: bzhi pa tshon ni dbus kyi lte ba ni mthing kha'o //
NK029(ha)004:259: lte ba'i mu khyud ni 'od zer ro //'khor lo rtsibs bzhi ni /
NK029(ha)004:263: byang ljang khu ste rigs lnga yab yum gyi gnas so /
NK029(ha)004:264: gong ras bzhi ni shar lho nas g.yas bskor kyi 'khor lo'i kha dog dang mtshungs pas ste /
NK029(ha)004:265: kha dog re re la lnga lnga gsungs pas rigs mthun la /
NK029(ha)004:267: nang sems dpa' yab yum gyis pa'o //'khor lo phyi'i mu khyud ni nag po'o //
NK029(ha)004:268: gru chad ni phyed ma'i kha dog can ste /
NK029(ha)004:269: phyi sems dpa' yab yum gyi pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:270: de bzhin du bar 'khyams sgo dang bcas pa ni rigs kyi kha dog ste /
NK029(ha)004:276: don lhag pa'i ye shes tshon pa'i rtags /
NK029(ha)004:277: lha med pa'i khang stong bzhi ste rigs kyi kha dog can no //
NK029(ha)004:278: bar 'khyams ni kun bzang yab yum dang /
NK029(ha)004:281: tshon spra la bkab pa ka pa la gsal la /
NK029(ha)004:283: re kha lngas 'tshams sbyar la drangs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:284: mun pa dang glang rgyab nag pa'o //'dod rnams dmar po /
NK029(ha)004:288: dra gdan nag la dra ba dmar po dang dkar po /
NK029(ha)004:289: shar bu'i ba dan dmar po la shar bu dngul
NK029(ha)004:290: dam kha thur du bstan pa lta bu'i dkar po
NK029(ha)004:291: byeed / mda' yab bzhi nag po /
NK029(ha)004:292: mda' yab mchod rten dkar po sgrigs /
NK029(ha)004:293: rta babs snam bu bzhi la gnyis gnyis su byas te brgyad ni /
NK029(ha)004:296: rin chen sgrom bu rnams 'phyang yees bya ste za ra tsha seng ge rin chen shar bu /
NK029(ha)004:297: 'phreng ba dang brgyad po mas rim kyi brtsegs la ci ltar mdzes par bri'o //
NK029(ha)004:301: rtsigs pa dang mtshungs par bris /
NK029(ha)004:302: chos 'khor dang ri dwags gser po /
NK029(ha)004:306: chu srin gyi kha nas phyung pa'i rdo rje rtse gsum pa phyogs mdog pad bskor ni sna tshogs /
NK029(ha)004:307: rdo rje'i ra ba sngon po'i gser po /
NK029(ha)004:308: me ri sna tshogs su tshon legs par 'gyed /
NK029(ha)004:314: tshom bu gcig pa yang dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang mtshungs so //
NK029(ha)004:317: tshom bu lnga pa rnams 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:318: lte ba dang lnga sngon po la /
NK029(ha)004:319: de'i steng gi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:326: tshon thal shor na dal yams 'byung /
NK029(ha)004:328: de nas zhal bsros kyi mchod pa bshams la /
NK029(ha)004:329: dkyil 'khor bris pa la lhag mo sbyangs /
NK029(ha)004:331: mdun gyi nam mkha' yi lta gon gyi lha tshogs dang /
NK029(ha)004:332: thig gi lha tshogs rnams brdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor la bstim /
NK029(ha)004:335: bzhi bsnol gyi sngags kyis mchod do //
NK029(ha)004:336: dam tshig gi phyag rgyas badz+ra mu /
NK029(ha)004:337: zhes brjod la tshon gyi rab gnas rang bzhin gyi gnas su gshegs /
NK029(ha)004:338: rdul tshon lhag ma rnams snod sor sor slug go /
NK029(ha)004:339: lnga pa rnam par bgod pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:340: thog mar tshul phyag byas la /
NK029(ha)004:346: spa ra sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)004:347: rdo rje rtse lnga par gyur /
NK029(ha)004:349: badz+ra kro ta a mri ta kun+da li h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:351: bdag bdud rtsid 'khyil pa sku mdog ljang khu /
NK029(ha)004:352: sna tshogs rdo rje rtse gsum pa gcig bsnams pa gcig tu bskyed la /
NK029(ha)004:353: h+aum yang dag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir /
NK029(ha)004:354: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas /
NK029(ha)004:355: 'dul ba'i las ni ma rtogs pa /
NK029(ha)004:356: thams cad thugs rjes bskang zin gyis /
NK029(ha)004:357: da lta nyid du so sor dengs /
NK029(ha)004:358: ci ste bka' las 'da' gyur na /
NK029(ha)004:359: rdo rje mtshon chen 'bar ba yis /
NK029(ha)004:360: de ma thag du bkas nas shog /
NK029(ha)004:361: na ma sa man+ta ka ya wa ga tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra nan /
NK029(ha)004:362: na mo badz+ra kra d+ha y+aa /
NK029(ha)004:363: ma h+aa d+ha d+hod i ta ka b+he ra /
NK029(ha)004:364: a si mu la sa ra shu pa sha ha ta ya /
NK029(ha)004:365: a mri ta kun ta li /
NK029(ha)004:367: kh+aa hi kh+aa hi tash+thi tish+tha /
NK029(ha)004:376: sarba big nan ba na yak+sha /
NK029(ha)004:378: a d+ha ka ra ya h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:379: gnod byed thams cad ma ra ya h+aum phatahcesa brjod pas /
NK029(ha)004:380: rang 'dra ba'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phros nas /
NK029(ha)004:381: bgegs rnams thams cad bskrad par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)004:382: h+aum zhes pas khro bo'i gur du gyur pa bsam /
NK029(ha)004:386: bskal pa'i rlung gis kyang mi tshugs par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)004:387: dbang phyug kun bzangs su gsal ba'i thugs kha nas /
NK029(ha)004:391: lam gyi yig 'bru mas rim gyis spros pas /
NK029(ha)004:392: spa ra sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)004:393: 'byung ba rang kha ma'i rtogs pa sbyangs nas /
NK029(ha)004:394: kham lnga rnam par dag pa'i 'byung ba rim brtsegs gsal gdab /
NK029(ha)004:397: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor de nyid /
NK029(ha)004:398: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi brten gzhal yas khang gsal gdab la /
NK029(ha)004:399: de las brtan pa lha bgod pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:400: rtsa rgyud kyi le'u dgu pa las /
NK029(ha)004:401: sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang 'god /
NK029(ha)004:405: gsung yig 'bru yang rung mod kyi /
NK029(ha)004:406: 'grub na gser dngul zangs lcags la /
NK029(ha)004:409: ba so la sogs pa bskos pa'am /
NK029(ha)004:410: rin po che'i che ma dang /
NK029(ha)004:411: spos dri la sogs pa'i lde gu 'am /
NK029(ha)004:413: shu gu la bris su bris pa'ang rung ste /
NK029(ha)004:414: gzungs dang ldan pa'i lhas sku rnams dbang phyug gi phyag tu bsnams la /
NK029(ha)004:415: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rig mum da du shwa ri zhes brjod cing /
NK029(ha)004:416: mi skyod pa yab yum kyi sku /
NK029(ha)004:417: dkyil 'khor kyi dbus kyi lte ba la bkod pas /
NK029(ha)004:418: sku gzi mdangs dang ldan zhing /
NK029(ha)004:420: de'i steng du man bya li dbus kyi bum pa'ang 'god do //
NK029(ha)004:421: de bzhin du dzi na dzig la sogs pas /
NK029(ha)004:422: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po thams cad rim pa
NK029(ha)004:423: bzhin rang rang gi gnas su rdzogs par 'god do
NK029(ha)004:424: // bum pa rnams kyang lha grangs dang mnyam pa yod na /
NK029(ha)004:425: thad so nas thad sor dgod pa'am /
NK029(ha)004:427: phyogs bzhi'i lha rnams kyi steng du dgod do //
NK029(ha)004:428: de yang dbus kyi lha'i zhal dang /
NK029(ha)004:429: bum pa'i mchu ni shar du bstan no //
NK029(ha)004:430: gzhan rnams ni gtso bo la /
NK029(ha)004:432: 'on kyang sgo ba ni zhal phyir bstan par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:433: las thams cad pa'i bum pa dbang phyug gi g.yas phyogs su dgod do //
NK029(ha)004:434: rdo rje rnams dkyil 'khor gyi lho phyogs su /
NK029(ha)004:435: dril bu rnams byang phyogs su dgod do //
NK029(ha)004:436: yi dam gyi mchod gtor lho nub tu /
NK029(ha)004:437: ma mgon gyi byang shar dgod /
NK029(ha)004:438: dge bsnyen gyi shar lho dang /
NK029(ha)004:440: sman rag gzed zhal dang bcas pa shar du'o //
NK029(ha)004:441: bzhi ba snol gzed zhal dang bcas pa nub tu'o //
NK029(ha)004:442: gzhan yang dbu brgyan la sogs pa /
NK029(ha)004:443: phan dbang gi dbang rdzas dang /
NK029(ha)004:444: ka pa li la sog pa nub dbang gi dbang rdzas dang /
NK029(ha)004:446: rtsa rgyud le'u dgu pa las /
NK029(ha)004:447: bcos bu'i ras ni sna tshogs dang /
NK029(ha)004:448: brgyan 'phreng gtung dang bro bas bskor /
NK029(ha)004:452: bar brgyan la sogs pa dang mchod pa'i bye brag ji ltar 'byor pa phun sum tshogs par bya /
NK029(ha)004:453: mdor na gong sta gon gyi skabs su bkod pa'i mchod gtor /
NK029(ha)004:457: ral gri la sogs pa legs par bgram mo //
NK029(ha)004:458: drug pa rab gnas la bcu ste /
NK029(ha)004:459: sngon du bya ba'i cho ga dang /
NK029(ha)004:460: ting nge 'dzin gyi lha bskyed pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:461: ye shes pa spyan drangs shing stim pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:462: dbang po la sogs kyi skyon sbyangs pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:463: che ba'i yon tan gyi dbang bskur mnga' gsol dang /
NK029(ha)004:464: chu bdun gyis bkru zhing sku phyi ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:465: phyi nang gsang gsum gyi puk+tsa 'bul ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:466: bden pa brjod cing bstan bzhugs bya ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:467: yon bdag la sogs kyis phyag bskor ba bya ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:468: mi 'bral zhing smon lam gdab pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:475: mdun bskyed kyi bsnyen bsgrub po /
NK029(ha)004:481: dang po yongs su smin par bya ba'i yan lag ni /
NK029(ha)004:482: dpon slob rnams bstan la 'khod de /
NK029(ha)004:483: rol mo'i byin dbab pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK029(ha)004:485: rtsa ba'i bla ma rdo rje sems dpa'i rnam pa
NK029(ha)004:486: la phyog bcu dus bzhi'i skyabs yul ma tshang ba
NK029(ha)004:487: med pa / mkha' khyab kyi 'khor lo bzhugs pa thams cad mngon sum du sad pa la /
NK029(ha)004:488: bdag dang mkha' mnyam sems can rnams /
NK029(ha)004:489: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal /
NK029(ha)004:490: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)004:491: mchog gsum ston pa'i zhing gyur la /
NK029(ha)004:492: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi /
NK029(ha)004:493: dngos 'byor yid kyi rnam sprul pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:494: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:495: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i bgegs //
NK029(ha)004:496: nyes byas ma lus gshegs par bgyis //
NK029(ha)004:497: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK029(ha)004:498: ma chags spyod la rje yi rangs //
NK029(ha)004:499: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK029(ha)004:500: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK029(ha)004:501: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK029(ha)004:502: dag pa gsum gyis lus 'bul lo //
NK029(ha)004:503: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK029(ha)004:504: bsdus ste byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK029(ha)004:505: zhes lan gsum la sogs par brjod la /
NK029(ha)004:506: skyabs yul rnams rang la bsdus ste /
NK029(ha)004:507: ka dag gnyis su med pa'i klong du rang babs su bzhag /
NK029(ha)004:508: gnyis pa mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:509: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka /
NK029(ha)004:510: bdag nyid skad cig gi rdo rje he ru ka
NK029(ha)004:511: sku mdog mthing nag mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum
NK029(ha)004:512: phyag drug gis dang po gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse
NK029(ha)004:514: bar ba gnyis kyis rtse lnga dang b+hany+tsa /
NK029(ha)004:515: tha ma gnyis kyi zhing dbyug dang 'dzin 'deg pa'i tshul can /
NK029(ha)004:516: zhabs bzhi g.yon brkyang ba'i gyad kyi dor stabs kyi
NK029(ha)004:517: ru tra pho mo byi chings su bsnol ba gnan
NK029(ha)004:518: pa / yum rdo rje khro mo'i dbang phyug ma
NK029(ha)004:519: sngon mo g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud
NK029(ha)004:520: cing g.yon dung khrag zhal du stob pa zhing gi
NK029(ha)004:521: pa / g.yang gzhi / glang chen gyi ko rlon /
NK029(ha)004:524: thod pa sko rlon tshal bu'i con pan /
NK029(ha)004:525: sa ral dpung brgyan dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)004:526: dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu /
NK029(ha)004:527: smin dbus su rak+ta'i thig le /
NK029(ha)004:528: os ko la zhag gi zo ris te /
NK029(ha)004:529: dur khrod chas brgyan kyis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)004:530: khyad par yum la gzig gi lpags pa'i sham thabs can cher gtum zhing 'khros pa /
NK029(ha)004:531: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:532: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shu badz+ra krod+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata /
NK029(ha)004:533: ha la ha la ha la h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:534: zhes brjod pas yab yum gnyis kyi sbyor mtshams nas khro bo 'chol pa /
NK029(ha)004:535: mtshon cha'i char 'beb pa dpag tu med pa 'phros /
NK029(ha)004:536: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad gang /
NK029(ha)004:537: bdud bgegs log par 'dren pa thams cad zil gyis mnan pas /
NK029(ha)004:540: gsang ba'i dam bcas so so nas /
NK029(ha)004:541: 'du ba'i lha ni ma gtogs pa //
NK029(ha)004:542: thams cad thugs rjes bkang zin gyis //
NK029(ha)004:543: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK029(ha)004:545: rdo rje khro bo'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK029(ha)004:546: de ma thag tu bkas nas ni //
NK029(ha)004:547: gdon gyur rigs rnams brlag par 'gyur //
NK029(ha)004:548: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka mah+aa tsan+da sarba
NK029(ha)004:549: 'adush+ta ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK029(ha)004:550: h+aum h+aum phata / zhes brjod cing bskul bas khro bo'i tshogs rnams kyis /
NK029(ha)004:551: gsang spyod lta bar mi dbang pa'i bgegs thams cad bsdig bskrad rlag par byas /
NK029(ha)004:552: badz+ra pany+tsa ram yam kham khro bo'i tshogs rnams slar 'dus ste /
NK029(ha)004:553: khro bo'i rang bzhin gyi rdo rje'i gur khang chen
NK029(ha)004:554: por bltam pa'i phyi rol kun nas bskal pa'i me
NK029(ha)004:556: rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs 'khrug pa'i ra ba gsum rims
NK029(ha)004:557: nam mkha' klas pas gang pas mtshams bcad par gyur
NK029(ha)004:558: / gsum pa gshegs pa bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:559: badz+ra sa ma dzahyisa bla ma rigs 'dzin zhi khro
NK029(ha)004:560: rgyal ba rab 'byam mngon du sad pa'i spyan sngar
NK029(ha)004:561: / sems can kyi don du mchog gi byang chub
NK029(ha)004:562: tshe 'di nyid kyis mngon du bya ba mnyam dran
NK029(ha)004:563: / pas / tshe rab 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas ma 'tshal ste /
NK029(ha)004:564: sdig pa mi dge ba'i las ci bgyis pa thams cad la gnong zhing 'gyod /
NK029(ha)004:565: phyin chad srog la bab kyang mi bgyid /
NK029(ha)004:566: sngar byas kyi gnyen por rnal 'byor gyis rim pa
NK029(ha)004:567: la 'jug snyam pa'i sems bstan par mngon sum du
NK029(ha)004:569: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni //
NK029(ha)004:570: zla rgyas bzhin du spros pa mi mnga' yang //
NK029(ha)004:571: thugs rjes nyi gsal 'od bzhin snyoms mdzad pa //'dir gshegs bdag la dgongs shing bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:572: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK029(ha)004:573: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs sku rigs lnga gtso //
NK029(ha)004:574: thugs rje thabs mkhas rgya che rol ba'i sku //
NK029(ha)004:575: zhi khro sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)004:576: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyi rnam sprul pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:577: kun tu bzang po bla med mchod sprin gyis //
NK029(ha)004:578: mkha' dbyings rnam dag rgya che yongs bkod de //
NK029(ha)004:579: phyi nang gsang ba mchod pa rgya mtshos mchod //
NK029(ha)004:580: kun tu bzang mo gsang ba'i b+ha ga la //
NK029(ha)004:581: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rab 'byams ma lus kun //'du 'bral med pa'i ngang du ro gcig pa //
NK029(ha)004:582: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi mnyes gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:583: sems kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK029(ha)004:584: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas 'od gsal zhing //
NK029(ha)004:585: rnal 'byor nyid dbyings smra bsam las 'das pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:586: mnyam nyid byang chub sems la rtag tu 'dud /
NK029(ha)004:587: kun bzang rdzogs chen ye nas brdal ba la //
NK029(ha)004:588: phyi nang gsang ba bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK029(ha)004:589: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings //'byung dang 'byung gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK029(ha)004:590: gsang chen rab dgyes gzugs can bdag nyid ma /
NK029(ha)004:591: mkha' dbyings klong yangs pad+mo 'khyil ba la //
NK029(ha)004:592: gnyis med thig le chen por 'od gsal zhing //
NK029(ha)004:593: ma bcos spros med byang chub snying po'i sku //
NK029(ha)004:594: cir yang snang ba bde chen g.yung drung lha //'du 'bral med pa gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK029(ha)004:595: bdag nyid chen po rigs lnga yab yum dang //
NK029(ha)004:596: byang chub lcam bral khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK029(ha)004:597: rdo rje lha mo tshogs rje tshogs kyi bdag /
NK029(ha)004:598: rigs lnga dpal chen khro rgyal yab yum bcu //
NK029(ha)004:599: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya sgo ma bzhi //
NK029(ha)004:600: ye shes sprul pa'i lha tshogs mang po dang //
NK029(ha)004:601: ma ltar byams shing sring ltar gdung la sogs //
NK029(ha)004:602: legs nyes stangs 'dzin dam tshig rjes spyod ma //
NK029(ha)004:603: phyi nang mkha' 'gro rnam 'byor ma yi tshogs //
NK029(ha)004:604: dpang gyur rdo rje dam can dgongs su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:606: thugs rjes gdung 'tshob rigs 'dzin bdag cag gis //'gro ba'i don du byang chub sems skyed de //
NK029(ha)004:607: bla med go 'phangs bgrod par bya ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)004:608: bstan pa rgya mtsho'i so so'i 'dul khrims dang //
NK029(ha)004:609: sku gsung thugs dang mnyam sbyor bsdom pa'i mchog /
NK029(ha)004:610: rdo rje 'da' dka' dam tshig gnyan gyi gter //
NK029(ha)004:611: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK029(ha)004:612: snga phyir mnos shing gnyer du smras so 'tshal //
NK029(ha)004:613: yun du mi gtong 'da' bar mi bgyid cing //
NK029(ha)004:614: don la gol shing ldog sems ma mchis kyang //
NK029(ha)004:615: gdod bya long yod mnyam pa'i le lo yis /
NK029(ha)004:616: klong du ma gyur rtsal shugs chung pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:617: shes bzhin mi ldan bag med dbang gyur ste //
NK029(ha)004:618: bsgom la mi brtson bsnyen bsgrub g.yel la sogs //
NK029(ha)004:619: tshor dang ma tshor ma rig dbang gis na //
NK029(ha)004:620: ston pa'i bka' dang dam las 'das gyur ste //
NK029(ha)004:621: rnal 'byor gang zhig dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:622: skad cig tsam yang 'phrad par mi bya zhes //
NK029(ha)004:623: bka' las byang zhing de ltar ma lcogs te //
NK029(ha)004:624: gsang sgo 'chol bas dbye gsal dka' ba dang //
NK029(ha)004:625: mngon shes chung pas skyon can ma rtogs ste //
NK029(ha)004:626: nyams dang tshogs 'dres nyams pa bkang ba dang //
NK029(ha)004:627: nyams dang snod min rnams la chos bshad dang //
NK029(ha)004:628: nyams la mi 'dzem nyams pa'i skyon la sogs //
NK029(ha)004:629: nyams grib skyon gyi gos par gyur to 'tshal //
NK029(ha)004:630: tshe 'di'i rkyen dang yun gyis sgribs gyur rnams //
NK029(ha)004:631: rang mnong 'gyod pa'i sems kyi mthol lo bshags //
NK029(ha)004:632: byams pa'i thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)004:633: gnyis med dbyings las mi 'gyur bdag bkod de //
NK029(ha)004:634: dmigs med btang snyoms ngang la bzhugs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)004:635: gnyis med don gyi tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)004:636: don dam brjod med spros las 'das pa la //
NK029(ha)004:637: rnam rtog gang yang dmigs par mi 'gyur zhing //
NK029(ha)004:638: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam gyi dbang gi na //
NK029(ha)004:639: nongs pa mchis na rang gnong bzod par gsol //
NK029(ha)004:640: bzhi pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:641: lhag pa'i bsam pa brtan pos //
NK029(ha)004:642: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa /
NK029(ha)004:643: 'gro la phan mdzad thugs rjes dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK029(ha)004:644: srid pa gsum gyi gnyer gyur gcig pu pa //
NK029(ha)004:645: lha yi lha khyod bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:646: bde bar gshegs pa'i sprul pa rgya mtsho dang //
NK029(ha)004:647: rnal 'byor dbang phyug grub pa'i tshogs chen po //
NK029(ha)004:648: lha dang lha min sngags 'chang dam tshig can //
NK029(ha)004:649: kun nas 'dus pa rnams kyang dgongs su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:650: bdag cag rgyal srid mtho rigs longs spyod dang //'dod
NK029(ha)004:651: pa'i yon tan bdag grub ma lags ste //'gro la
NK029(ha)004:652: snying brtse kho nas don brtson pa //'di la kun
NK029(ha)004:653: mkhyen khyed ni dpang du gsol //
NK029(ha)004:654: mgon po ye shes sgrib pa mi mnga' bas //
NK029(ha)004:655: bdag gis lhag pa'i bsam pa khyed kyi mkhyen //'phags mchog spyan sngar ji ltar dam bcas pas //
NK029(ha)004:656: sun par mi bgyid mgon khyod bslu ma lags //
NK029(ha)004:657: snying nas bdag gi khe dang grags la sogs //
NK029(ha)004:658: g.yo dang zang zing sems kyis bstan spangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:659: gzhan don sgrub pa gcig pu'i sems bzhag te //
NK029(ha)004:660: rnal 'byor spyod pa chen po bdag gis spyad //
NK029(ha)004:661: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yis //
NK029(ha)004:662: byang chub mchog tu bdag gi sems bskyed de //
NK029(ha)004:663: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK029(ha)004:664: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyis //
NK029(ha)004:665: srog chags thams cad gal te bdud gyur nas //
NK029(ha)004:666: dum bu stong du bdag gis lus gtub kyang //
NK029(ha)004:667: byang chub sems mchog shes rab snying rje dang //
NK029(ha)004:668: yi dam rgyal ba khyed ni yongs mi spongs //
NK029(ha)004:669: rdo rje dam tshig chen po rnams dang ni //
NK029(ha)004:670: rdo rje slob dpon rdo rje mched lcam dang //
NK029(ha)004:671: gzhan yang theg pa mchog la bzhugs pa rnams //
NK029(ha)004:672: srog gi phyir yang mi btong ci nus bsrungs //'khor ba bdag med sgyu ma'i rang bzhin las //
NK029(ha)004:673: bdag ni 'jig pa ci yang ma mchis ste //
NK029(ha)004:674: ma rig skye bo rnams kyi don slad du //
NK029(ha)004:675: phyi ma mthar thug bar du gnas par spro //
NK029(ha)004:676: gzhan yang 'khor ba rnams su spyod pa na //
NK029(ha)004:677: byang chub spyod pa brlabs chen bdag gi spyad //'gro drug sems can rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK029(ha)004:678: rang dbang du ni skye ba blangs par bgyi //
NK029(ha)004:679: bdag ni yongs su bzung ba'i 'jig rten nam //
NK029(ha)004:680: mya ngan 'das la sproo ba ma mchis ste //
NK029(ha)004:681: gang dang gang du sdug bsngal gnas rnams su //
NK029(ha)004:682: bskal pa rgya mtshor gnas shing phan par bgyi //
NK029(ha)004:683: srid pa yun ring dus su brtson pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:684: byang chub sems dpa'i yi dam lags pa na //
NK029(ha)004:685: ji srid ngan song stong bar ma gyur na //
NK029(ha)004:686: de srid bdag gi skyo ba'i sems mi skye //
NK029(ha)004:687: shes rab thabs kyi 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)004:688: snying rje longs spyod de las ma mchis pas //
NK029(ha)004:689: sems can dmyal ba yi dwags gshen rje'i 'jig rten yang //
NK029(ha)004:690: lha'i dga' 'tshal lta bur blta bar gyis /
NK029(ha)004:691: 'gro la thugs brtse dpal gyi mgur nas gsungs //
NK029(ha)004:692: rnal 'byor dam chos bdud rtsi mchog rnams ni //
NK029(ha)004:693: bdag gi 'jig rten thugs pa ma mchis bar //
NK029(ha)004:694: ji ltar mtshams pa bzhin du rgyas par bgyi //
NK029(ha)004:695: srid pa las dang rkyen gyi dbang gyur ste //
NK029(ha)004:696: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jig pa der //
NK029(ha)004:697: me tshogs spu gri'i so la rgal nas ni //
NK029(ha)004:698: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK029(ha)004:699: bla med byang chub mchog du sems bskyed de //
NK029(ha)004:700: sgrub pa mchog la bzhugs pa'i skye bo la //
NK029(ha)004:701: tshe rabs rnams su mthu rtsal ci mchis kyang //
NK029(ha)004:702: skyes chen rnams kyi dgongs pa rtag tu bskangs //
NK029(ha)004:703: dam pa'i chos dang sgrub pa'i gegs gyur pa //
NK029(ha)004:704: mi dang mi min gdug pa gang yang rung //
NK029(ha)004:705: bdag gi zhi dang khro bo'i 'phrin las kyis //
NK029(ha)004:706: yongs su zhi zhing rnam par bzhom par bgyi //
NK029(ha)004:707: rnal 'byor mchog gi theg chen bla med dang //
NK029(ha)004:708: rdo rje rgyal po khyed la brten pa ni //
NK029(ha)004:709: sangs rgyas zhing sbyangs 'gro la sman slad du //
NK029(ha)004:710: byang chub snying po bdag gi rtogs par bgyis //
NK029(ha)004:711: bdag ni 'phags mchog phyag rgyas sngon sprul ste //
NK029(ha)004:712: gal te skabs med 'chi ba'i dus byung tshe //
NK029(ha)004:713: gsang sngags mgon po ye shes dkyil 'khor can //
NK029(ha)004:714: khyed kyi zhabs kyi drung du 'chi bar bgyi //
NK029(ha)004:715: srid gsum sdug bsngal ci 'dra khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK029(ha)004:716: dmyal sogs me dpung zhi bar bgyid lags so //
NK029(ha)004:717: sems can don la myur du bdag mchis na //
NK029(ha)004:718: dam pa rnams kyis nus mthu stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)004:719: lnga pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:721: b+ha ga wan sa ma ya ho /
NK029(ha)004:723: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)004:724: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)004:725: mthu rtsal 'byung pa'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)004:726: byin gyis barlobasa pa'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)004:727: dbang mchog bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK029(ha)004:729: byin chen byin phobs bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)004:730: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)004:731: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)004:732: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK029(ha)004:733: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum gis byin bsdus pas /
NK029(ha)004:734: nam mkha' gang ba'i lha tshogs thams cad rang la thim ste /
NK029(ha)004:735: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo byin gyis brlabs par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)004:736: drug pa mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:737: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ris phyi mchod rnams bsang /
NK029(ha)004:738: ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:739: stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK029(ha)004:740: nga rdor sems su gsal ba'i thugs kha'i h+aum las a d+hu pu a gan rnams 'phros /
NK029(ha)004:748: bud d+ha nam ga ga kham sa ma ya h+aum swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:749: sh+ri badz+ra r+aa ga d+ha be d+hu /
NK029(ha)004:751: a lo ke hrih g+han+he gan /
NK029(ha)004:752: bsil chab ma la sogs pa'i mchod pa'i lha mo khrus zhong dang /
NK029(ha)004:753: spos khang la sogs pa thogs pa nam mkha' gang ba rnams su gyur par bsam pas /
NK029(ha)004:754: phyi mchod rnams byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)004:756: ram yam kham stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK029(ha)004:757: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud d+he badz+ra dz+nya na tsakra man+da la b+h+rum /
NK029(ha)004:758: bdud rtsi'i snod gzhal yas khang du gsal ba'i dbus
NK029(ha)004:759: su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i lte bar dri chen
NK029(ha)004:760: la h+aum mum / shar du byang sems la lam /
NK029(ha)004:761: lhor sha chen la swa mam /
NK029(ha)004:762: nub tu rak+ta la am lam /
NK029(ha)004:763: byang du dri chu la ha tam /
NK029(ha)004:771: so so'i rigs kyi dril bu rnams su gyur /
NK029(ha)004:776: dbus su mi skyod pa yab yum mthing kh+aa /
NK029(ha)004:779: shar du rnam snang yab yum dkar po /
NK029(ha)004:782: lhor rin 'byung yab yum gser po /
NK029(ha)004:785: nub du snang mtha' yab yum dmar po /
NK029(ha)004:788: byang du don yod grub pa yab yum ljang khu /
NK029(ha)004:791: a nu ra ga ya mi /
NK029(ha)004:792: a nu ra ga ho ham /
NK029(ha)004:795: rigs lnga yab yum rjes chags kyi sbyor bas zhu ba las byung pa'i ye shes kyi bdud rtsi /
NK029(ha)004:796: gyi mtshan pa'i kha spyod rdo rje rgya gram gyi lte bar /
NK029(ha)004:797: pad+ma ta krid badz+ra mah+aa kro d+ha h+ya g+h+ri wa h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:798: rta mgrin dmar po pad+ma dang rgya gram 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:799: lte ba yan chod thon pa /
NK029(ha)004:800: rwa bzhi la shar du mi pham ma dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:801: lhor khro gnyer ma ser mo zhags pa /
NK029(ha)004:802: nub du ro lang ma dmar mo lcags sgrog /
NK029(ha)004:803: byang shar du ral gcig ma ljang khu dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:804: gyi 'od zer gyi 'khor 'das kyi bdud rtsi thams
NK029(ha)004:805: cad kun dam tshig gi bdud rtsi la ro mnyam
NK029(ha)004:806: par bsam la / g.yon pa'i mtheb srin gyis rdo rje gzung bas /
NK029(ha)004:809: sarba pan tsa a mri ta h+aum hrihthah zhes bzlas shing /
NK029(ha)004:810: mthar g.yon bskor du dkrugs ste /
NK029(ha)004:812: zhes brjod pas yab yum bzhi bdud rtsi la thim par bsam /
NK029(ha)004:813: gtor ma ram yam kham stong pa nyid kyi ngang las /
NK029(ha)004:814: b+h+rum pad+ma b+ha lim ta bi shwa tsakra b+h+rum /
NK029(ha)004:815: gtor gzhong pad+ma'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du /
NK029(ha)004:816: gtor rdzas 'dod yon gyi rnam pa /
NK029(ha)004:817: ma tshang ba med pa la /
NK029(ha)004:818: s+pha sam b+ha lamngii ta te dzo b+ha lamngi ta
NK029(ha)004:819: b+ha la b+aa rgya gu h+ya sa ma ye swah+aa
NK029(ha)004:820: / lan bdun brjod pas 'dod pa drug gi lha
NK029(ha)004:821: mo nam mkha' gang ba 'dod yon gyi rnam pa
NK029(ha)004:822: ma tshang ba med par spro ba'i bdag nyid du
NK029(ha)004:823: / gyur par bsam / rak+ta ram yam kham /
NK029(ha)004:824: stong pa nyid kyi ngang las b+h+rum /
NK029(ha)004:826: dmar gyi dung chen yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du /
NK029(ha)004:830: mah+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h+aum hrihthah rak+ta'i rgya
NK029(ha)004:831: mtsho rba rlabs 'khrugs pa nam mkha' gang bar bsam
NK029(ha)004:832: / dngos gzhi la bdun gyi dang po sems bskyed pa la gnyis las /
NK029(ha)004:833: kun rdzob sems bskyed pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:834: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK029(ha)004:835: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang /
NK029(ha)004:836: rtog pa'i dbang gi 'khor ba las //
NK029(ha)004:837: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK029(ha)004:838: gnyis pa don dam sems bskyed ni /
NK029(ha)004:839: e ma ho ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK029(ha)004:840: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //
NK029(ha)004:841: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK029(ha)004:842: skyes pa nyid ni skye ba med //
NK029(ha)004:843: e ma ho ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK029(ha)004:844: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //'gag pa med
NK029(ha)004:845: las thams cad 'gag /'gag pa nyid na 'gag pa
NK029(ha)004:846: med // e ma ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK029(ha)004:847: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //
NK029(ha)004:848: gnas pa med la thams cad gnas //
NK029(ha)004:849: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK029(ha)004:850: e ma ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK029(ha)004:851: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK029(ha)004:852: dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK029(ha)004:853: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK029(ha)004:854: e ma ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK029(ha)004:855: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyis gsang //'gro 'ong med
NK029(ha)004:857: med // gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gsum ni /
NK029(ha)004:858: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pa //
NK029(ha)004:859: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK029(ha)004:860: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK029(ha)004:861: de phyir dngos po dngos med pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:862: zhes pa'i don sgom pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:863: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:864: de bzhin nyid ni spros med kyang //
NK029(ha)004:865: rang bzhin kun tu snang ba'i dbyings //
NK029(ha)004:866: sems can kun la snying brtse'i phyir //
NK029(ha)004:867: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha'i bsgom //
NK029(ha)004:869: dngos po med las dngos po'i sprin //
NK029(ha)004:871: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK029(ha)004:872: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK029(ha)004:873: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK029(ha)004:874: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK029(ha)004:875: yi ge mchog ni bsgom par bya /
NK029(ha)004:877: sems nyid a dkar po'i rnam par bsgom pa de rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK029(ha)004:878: gsum pa rten gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni //
NK029(ha)004:879: sems nyid a dkar po gsal ba las /
NK029(ha)004:880: e yam wam sum lam ram rnams chad /
NK029(ha)004:883: e las nam mkha' chos 'byung 'jam klas pa /
NK029(ha)004:884: de'i steng du yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor sngon po gzhu'i dbyibs can /
NK029(ha)004:885: de'i steng du bam las chu'i dkyil 'khor dkar po bzlum po /
NK029(ha)004:886: de'i steng du sum las sa'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhi gser po /
NK029(ha)004:887: de'i steng du lam las ri rab rin po che sna bzhi'i rang bzhin zur bzhi pa /
NK029(ha)004:888: ram las me'i 'khor yug nam mkha'i mtha' klas par 'khor ba /
NK029(ha)004:889: ri rab kyi steng du b+hum /
NK029(ha)004:893: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa /
NK029(ha)004:894: yon tan dpag tu med pa rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK029(ha)004:895: lhag pa'i ye shes glo bur gyis mdzes pa /
NK029(ha)004:896: rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad /
NK029(ha)004:897: so so ma yin zhing ngo bo nyid gcig pa'i ye shes kun tu 'khyil ba /
NK029(ha)004:898: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes rin po che'i dbyibs dang /
NK029(ha)004:899: gzhi dang brgyan dang kha dog dang bkod pa tshad med pas 'phags pa /
NK029(ha)004:900: zag pa med pa'i 'dod yon gyi rnam pa ma
NK029(ha)004:901: tshang ba med pa thams cad kyi nam mkha'i mthas
NK029(ha)004:902: klas pas gang ba'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)004:903: seng ge brgyad kyi bteg pa'i rin po che'i khri bkod pa phun sum tshogs pa'i steng du /
NK029(ha)004:904: pam pad+ma man+dala la sur+ya man+da la /
NK029(ha)004:906: pad nyi zla ba'i gdan cha shas yongs su rdzogs par gyur /
NK029(ha)004:907: bzhi ba lha bskyed pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:908: rang gi sems nyid ar gsal ba zla ba'i steng du babs /
NK029(ha)004:909: yongs su gyur pa las h+aum mthing nag ye shes lnga'i 'od zer 'bar ba /
NK029(ha)004:912: badz+ra h+aum de rdo rje gyur /
NK029(ha)004:915: rdo rje yongs su gyur pa las /
NK029(ha)004:916: rang nyid rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog mthing kha mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal /
NK029(ha)004:917: zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas dang po rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin zhing /
NK029(ha)004:918: g.yon dang po dril bu 'dzin pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:919: bar pa gnyis kyis 'khor lo rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:920: tha ma gnyis kyi pad+ma dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:921: mnyam pa'i dkyil mo dkrung gis bzhugs pa //
NK029(ha)004:922: de'i thugs kha nas g.yon gyi barla steng su mum chad /
NK029(ha)004:927: mum d+ha t+wi shwa ri yab kyi g.yon phyogs su
NK029(ha)004:928: nye ba'i spang du yum rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang
NK029(ha)004:929: phyug ma sngon mo phyag g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas
NK029(ha)004:931: g.yon rdo rje thugs khar 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:932: brtul zhugs gyi dkyil mo dkrung gis 'khril ba /
NK029(ha)004:933: gnyis ka'ang dar la'i bstod g.yogs cod pan zi 'dir gar gyi phu rung can /
NK029(ha)004:934: rin po che'i dbus brgyan snyan cha mgul brgyan sen mo do //
NK029(ha)004:935: phyag gdub zhabs gdub ska rag do shal rnams kyis mdzes par spras pa /
NK029(ha)004:936: mnyen cug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can //
NK029(ha)004:937: gsal mtsher lhun sdug gzi sbyin ldan pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:938: zhi ba'i nyams dgus rgyas pa /
NK029(ha)004:939: 'od zer kha dog drug re re yang /
NK029(ha)004:940: bye ba phrag drug du 'phro ba'i klong na /
NK029(ha)004:941: bde stong gnyis su med pa'i ngo bor bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:942: rang gi lus rdor sems yab yum du gsal ba'i /
NK029(ha)004:943: yab kyi gtsug gtor gyi rtsal /
NK029(ha)004:945: rnam snang dkar po g.yas 'khor lo thugs khar 'dzin cing /
NK029(ha)004:946: g.yon des mtshan pa'i dril bu skur rten pa /
NK029(ha)004:947: lag pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)004:949: kun tu bzang po mthing kha /
NK029(ha)004:950: mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK029(ha)004:953: rin 'byung gser po g.yas rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:954: g.yon des mtshan pa'i dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:955: rkang pa gnyis kyi 'doms rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)004:957: don 'grub ljang khu g.yas ral gri /
NK029(ha)004:958: g.yon des mtshan pa'i dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:961: snang mtha' dmar po g.yas pad+ma /
NK029(ha)004:962: g.yon des mtshan pa'i dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:963: kun tu bzang mo rdo rje dkyil mo dkrungs dang /
NK029(ha)004:964: gzhan rnams mnyam pa'i dkyil dkrung gi bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:965: mig gi 'doms rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)004:967: sa snying dkar po g.yas rin po che'i myu gu 'dzin cing /
NK029(ha)004:968: g.yon dril bu skur brten pa /
NK029(ha)004:969: g.yon gyi cha la mee d+ha ra ni swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)004:970: byams pa dkar ser g.yas klu shing /
NK029(ha)004:972: rna ba'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)004:973: badz+ra ku ru pany+tsa hrih phyag rdor mthing kha g.yas rdo rje g.yon dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:975: tha lhim ni swa ram b+aa ya /
NK029(ha)004:976: sgribs sel dmar ser g.yas chos kyi 'khor lo /
NK029(ha)004:980: nam snying ser po g.yas ral gri g.yon dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:981: g.yon gyi cha la h+aum pa r+aa dz+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK029(ha)004:982: kun bzang dmar ljang g.yas rin po che'i snye ma /
NK029(ha)004:984: lce'i 'doms rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)004:986: spyan ras gzigs dmar g.yas pad+ma dkar po /
NK029(ha)004:989: mum sh+ri a ram g+aa y+aa s+w+aah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:990: 'jam dpal dkar ljang g.yas ud pa la /
NK029(ha)004:992: brgyad ka'ang zhabs g.yas cung zad brkyang pa'i phyed dkyil kyis bzhugs pa lag mthil g.yas la /
NK029(ha)004:993: h+aum ya man+ta krid phata gshin rje smug nag mi mgo kha gdang pa 'dzin pa g.yon la /
NK029(ha)004:995: stobs po che gser nag thod pa rdo rjes mnon thabs su 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:999: rgya gram gnon thabs su 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1002: rta mgrin dmar nag thod pa sprul gyis dkris pa 'dzin ba /
NK029(ha)004:1003: bzhi ka'ang g.yas su phyogs pa'i gyad kyi dor thabs kyis bzhugs pa'o //'tshogs dmar mu ne trim swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:1004: lha yi thub pa dkar po pi wang 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1007: lha min gyi thub pa mthing kha go cha 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1010: mi'i thub pa gser po gseg shang 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1011: lte bar mu ne pram swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:1012: byol song gi thub pa dmar nag /
NK029(ha)004:1014: mgrin par mu ne k+sham swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)004:1015: yi dwags kyi thub pa gser nag /
NK029(ha)004:1016: rin po che'i sgrmo bu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1019: dmyal ba'i thub pa du kha me chu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1020: drug kha'ang 'greng thabs su gshegs pa'i tshul can /
NK029(ha)004:1021: yum rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma'i gtsug gtor gyi rtse la /
NK029(ha)004:1023: spyan ma dkar mo g.yas 'khor los mtshan pa'i dril bu bskur brten cing /
NK029(ha)004:1025: lag pa gnyis kyis 'dom rtsi'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)004:1026: a a a badz+ra b+ha tri sa man+ta a /
NK029(ha)004:1028: thal mo thugs khar sbyar ba /
NK029(ha)004:1031: m+aa ma ki ser mo g.yas rin po ches mtshan pa'i dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1033: rkang pa gnyis kyi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)004:1035: dam tshig sgrol ma ljang khu g.yas ral gris mtshan pa'i dril /
NK029(ha)004:1038: gos dkar mo dmar mo g.yas pad+mas mtshan pa'i dril /
NK029(ha)004:1040: kun tu bzang mo pad+ma'i dkyil dkrungs dang /
NK029(ha)004:1041: yum bzhi brtul zhugs kyi dkyil mo dkrungs du bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1042: mig gi 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)004:1043: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK029(ha)004:1044: sgeg mo dkar mo me long 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1046: dzahd+hu pe pra be sha gdugs spos ma dkar ser /
NK029(ha)004:1048: rna ba'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)004:1049: tram ma le sa ma ya ho /
NK029(ha)004:1050: 'phreng ba ma gser mo rin po che'i 'phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1056: hrih girti ra ga ho ha /
NK029(ha)004:1057: glu ma dmar mo pi wang 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1059: bam d+ai pa pu khi ni /
NK029(ha)004:1060: mar me ma dmar ljang mar me'i sdong bu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1061: lce'i 'dom rtsa'i g.yas kyi cha la /
NK029(ha)004:1062: a ni r+ya ra ga ya m+ai /
NK029(ha)004:1063: gar ma ljang khu gar gyi phu rung 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1065: ho gan+te tsit+ta dri chab ma dkar ljang dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1066: brgyad ka'ang zhabs g.yon pa bstan gtsugs shing /
NK029(ha)004:1067: g.yas pa dkyil dkrungs phyed pas bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1068: lag thil g.yas mah+aa badz+ra d+ha ra mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ra dz+wi la sh+ai h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:1069: lcags kyu ma smug nag lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1070: g.yon la mah+aa rat+na d+ha ra mah+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK029(ha)004:1071: zhags pa ma ser nag zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1073: mah+aa karma d+ha ra mah+aa kro d+hi sh+aa ri dz+aa la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:1074: dril bu ma ljang nag dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1075: g.yon la ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro di sh+aahr dz+ai la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:1076: lcags sgrogs ma dmar nag lcags sgrogs 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:1077: bzhi ka'ang g.yon du phyogs pa'i gyad kyi dor stabs kyi bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1082: kun bzang yab yum rnams zhi ba'i brgyan chas bcu gsum gyis mdzes shing /
NK029(ha)004:1083: tshul dgu'i nyams kyis rgyas pa /
NK029(ha)004:1084: thub pa drug gtsug gtor dang ldan zhing /
NK029(ha)004:1085: tshangs par spyod pa'i cha lugs can /
NK029(ha)004:1086: khro bo yab yum thod pa dang sbrul gyis brgyan can /
NK029(ha)004:1087: zhing chen gyi stod g.yogs dang /
NK029(ha)004:1088: stag gi lpags pa'i sham thabs gsol ba /
NK029(ha)004:1089: bskal pa'i me'i klong na bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1090: thams cad kyang rdo rje sems dpa' snang stong sgyu
NK029(ha)004:1091: 'phrul d+r+wa pa'i rang bzhin gyi sku gsung thugs mi
NK029(ha)004:1092: zad brgyan gyis 'khor lo'i rnam par dag pa /
NK029(ha)004:1093: rang rang gi srog gi gor rang rang 'dra ba'i
NK029(ha)004:1094: ye shes sems dpa' mtshon gang pa re re dang
NK029(ha)004:1095: bcas pa'o // lnga pa dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:1098: bstan par bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:1102: bzlas pa byed pa rnams 'og bum bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)004:1104: thun mongs du shes par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:1105: gnyis pa bum bskyed la gzhi ste /
NK029(ha)004:1106: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:1107: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:1109: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK029(ha)004:1110: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK029(ha)004:1111: dngos rnams nyid nas dngos med pa /
NK029(ha)004:1112: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das /
NK029(ha)004:1113: shes chos kyi dbyings sems nyid de kho na nyid /
NK029(ha)004:1114: rig pas rtog shing nyams su myong ba'o //
NK029(ha)004:1116: sems can rnams la snying brtse'i phyir /
NK029(ha)004:1117: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom /
NK029(ha)004:1118: zhes de ltar ma rtogs pa'i nam mkhas khyab tshad kyi /
NK029(ha)004:1119: sems can la sgyu ma lta bu'i snying rje phyogs rigs med par nam mkha' lta bur bsgom /
NK029(ha)004:1120: gsum pa rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK029(ha)004:1121: yi ge mchog ni bsgom par bya /
NK029(ha)004:1122: rab tu brtan gyur a dkar la /
NK029(ha)004:1124: snying rje dbyer med pa'i ngo bo yi ge a
NK029(ha)004:1125: dkar po gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad dang ldan par
NK029(ha)004:1126: bsgom / bzhi pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin la bzhi ste /
NK029(ha)004:1129: byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)004:1132: brten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:1133: brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1134: dang po ni rgyu'i yig a las 'og tu e 'phros pa las /
NK029(ha)004:1135: chos 'byung drug gsum mthing nag tshad dpag tu med pa /
NK029(ha)004:1136: de'i steng du yam 'phros pa las /
NK029(ha)004:1137: rlung gi dkyil 'khor zla gam sra zhing mkhreg pa du kha /
NK029(ha)004:1139: bam 'phros pa las chu'i dkyil 'khor zlum po dkar po mtha' ma bum pas mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1140: de'i steng du lam 'phros pa las gser gyi sa gzhi zlum po gser po /
NK029(ha)004:1141: tha ma bum pa rdo rjes mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1142: de'i steng du sum 'phros pa las //
NK029(ha)004:1143: rin po che sna bzhi la grub pa'i ri'i rgyal po ri rab gru bzhi pa /
NK029(ha)004:1145: gling bzhi gling phran mtsho lcags ri dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)004:1146: de'i steng du ram las me'i dkyil 'khor du gyur ste /
NK029(ha)004:1149: phyed ri rab kyi steng du /
NK029(ha)004:1150: me'i gur khang du gyur de'i nang du h+aum 'phros pa las /
NK029(ha)004:1151: rdo rje'i gur khang 'og gzhi sna tshogs rdo rje leb mo lte ba gru bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:1152: ra rtse gsum gsum dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1156: zhes rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i phyi bum pa'i dbyibs /
NK029(ha)004:1157: nang gzhal yas kyi khang pa gru bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:1158: sgo bzhi steng pad rag gi rtsigs pa lnga rims /
NK029(ha)004:1159: de la shar dkar po 'khor los mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1160: lho ser po rin po ches mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1161: nub dmar po pad+mas mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1162: byang ljang khu ral griis mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1164: shar bu la dra ba dang dra phyed pa 'phyang ba /
NK029(ha)004:1165: nang ka ba brgyad kyi btegs pa'i gdung bzhi la sogs pas /
NK029(ha)004:1166: byang chub chen po'i mchod rten gyi dbyibs legs par phub ste /
NK029(ha)004:1167: bang rim bzhi la rdo rje'i gyo lding /
NK029(ha)004:1168: phyi'i rtse la mda' yab dkar po /
NK029(ha)004:1172: sgo khang phyi zur bzhi nas ka ba bzhi bzhis bteg pa'i rta babs rnam bu /
NK029(ha)004:1173: bzhi pa'am brgyad kyi mdzes pa /
NK029(ha)004:1175: pad+ma chos 'khor gdugs ri dwags dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)004:1176: gzhal yas khang de'i phyi rol du /
NK029(ha)004:1177: ta la'i shing dpag bsam gyi shing la gser gyi nyag thag gis bres shing //
NK029(ha)004:1178: dril bu dang dril bu g.yer kha 'chang ba /
NK029(ha)004:1180: g.yu'i ne'u sing me tog zlum rtsigs dkar po'i tshal /
NK029(ha)004:1181: gzhal yas khang de'i nang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:1186: gru chad phyogs mdog /'khor lo'i dbus su seng ge brgyad la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)004:1187: rtsibs bzhi la glang po che dang /
NK029(ha)004:1190: shang shang la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)004:1191: sgo bzhir nyi ma bzhi'i steng du /
NK029(ha)004:1193: gnyis pa brten pa lha'i gzhal yas khang bskyed pa la gsum ste /
NK029(ha)004:1195: thugs phyag mtshan gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)004:1197: dang po ni rgyu'i yi ge a dkar po las k+sha sngon po byung ste /
NK029(ha)004:1198: a dang k+sha sbyor ba'i khyad par las /
NK029(ha)004:1199: dbus kyi gdan gyi steng du tha dang /
NK029(ha)004:1201: shar du ta dang ta dkar po gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1202: lhor da dang da ser po gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1203: nub du d+ha dang d+ha dmar po gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1204: byang du na dang na ljang khu gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1205: shar sgor nga dang sha dkar po /
NK029(ha)004:1206: lho sgor nya dang sha ser po /
NK029(ha)004:1207: nub sgor ma dang a dmar po /
NK029(ha)004:1208: byang sgor dang ha ljang khu /
NK029(ha)004:1209: a dang k+sha gnyis dbus kyi tha tha la thim /
NK029(ha)004:1211: sems can ngag gi sgrib pa byang //
NK029(ha)004:1212: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK029(ha)004:1213: phyag mtshan bcu dang brgyad du gyur //
NK029(ha)004:1214: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)004:1215: shar du 'khor lo dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)004:1216: lhor rin chen dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)004:1217: byang du ral gri dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)004:1218: shar sgor thod dbyug dang lcags kyu //
NK029(ha)004:1219: lho sgor rdo rje dbyug pa dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)004:1220: nub sgor pad+ma dang dbyug pa lcags sgrog /
NK029(ha)004:1221: byang sgor rgya gram dbyug pa dang dril bu //'od 'phros bde gshegs thugs la mchod //
NK029(ha)004:1222: sems can yid kyi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK029(ha)004:1223: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK029(ha)004:1224: phra mo bcu dang brgyad du gyur //'od 'phros bde gshegs sku la mchod //
NK029(ha)004:1225: sems can lus kyi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK029(ha)004:1226: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK029(ha)004:1227: yongs rdzogs bcu dang brgyad du gyur //
NK029(ha)004:1228: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rig mum d+ha du shwa ri /
NK029(ha)004:1229: dbus su kun tu bzang po dang /
NK029(ha)004:1230: mi skyod pa dbyer med pa sku mdog mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhal g.yas dkar /
NK029(ha)004:1232: dbus mthing sa la ral pa'i thor gtsugs nag po
NK029(ha)004:1233: 'gying pa phyag drug gi dang po gnyis rdo rje
NK029(ha)004:1234: dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1235: g.yas bar pa na 'khor lo 'og ma rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1238: phyag rgya de dag la ye shes kyii me 'bar ba /
NK029(ha)004:1239: zhabs snyoms pa'i dkyil dkrungs gis bzhugs pa //
NK029(ha)004:1240: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1241: dpe byad byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1242: yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma sku mdog yab dang
NK029(ha)004:1243: mthun pa zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas yab la 'khyud
NK029(ha)004:1244: cing / g.yon dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1245: dzi na dzig lam ste sha ra te /
NK029(ha)004:1246: shar du rnam par snang mdzad dkar po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)004:1249: phyag dang po gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1251: tha ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1254: swa rat+na d+h+rig mam ha ra ti /
NK029(ha)004:1256: rin chen 'byung ldan sku mdog ser po /
NK029(ha)004:1259: phyag dang po gnyis rin po che dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1260: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)004:1264: am a ro lig pyam r+aa ga ra ti /
NK029(ha)004:1266: snang ba mtha' yas dmar po zhal gsum phyag drug zhal g.yas dkar /
NK029(ha)004:1268: phyag dang po gnyis kyis pad+ma dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1269: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)004:1271: g.yon bar ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1273: ham pra dz+nya d+h+rig tam badz+ra ra ti /
NK029(ha)004:1274: zhes byang du don yod grub pa /
NK029(ha)004:1277: phyag dang po gnyis ral gri dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa //
NK029(ha)004:1278: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)004:1280: g.yon par ma rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1282: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag kyang ral pa'i mthor btsugs nag po 'gying pa /
NK029(ha)004:1283: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1284: dpe byad bzang po brgyad bcu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1286: brtul zhugs kyi dkyil dkrung gis rang rang gi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1287: yum thams cad sku mdog yab dang 'dra ba /
NK029(ha)004:1289: phyag g.yas pa yab la 'khyud cing /
NK029(ha)004:1291: yab yum bcu po de rnams ni /
NK029(ha)004:1292: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yin te /
NK029(ha)004:1294: spyan gcig gis gcig la gzigs so //
NK029(ha)004:1296: badz+ra d+ha ra mah+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:1297: shar sgor khro bo chen po gshin rje gshed dang yum rdo rje lcags kyu ma /
NK029(ha)004:1298: sku mdog mthing nag zhal cig phyag gnyis spyan gsum mche ba bzhi gtsigs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1299: yab kyi phyag g.yas na thod dbyug g.yon thod khrag /
NK029(ha)004:1300: yum gyi phyag na lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1301: dpal chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1302: phung po'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1303: h+aum pra dz+nya ta krid phata /
NK029(ha)004:1304: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:1306: lho sgor khro bo chen po stobs po che dang /
NK029(ha)004:1307: yum rdo rje zhags pa ma sku mdog gser nag yab kyi g.yas na rdo rje dbyug pa /
NK029(ha)004:1309: yum gyi phyag na zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1310: nyon mongs pa'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1312: pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:1314: khro bo chen po rta mgrin dang /
NK029(ha)004:1315: yum rdo rje lcags sgrog ma /
NK029(ha)004:1317: yab kyi phyag g.yas na pad+ma'i thod dbyug sbrul gyis dkris pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1318: yum gyi phyag na lcags sgrog bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1319: nyon mongs pa'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1320: h+aum big nan ta krid phata /
NK029(ha)004:1321: karma d+ha ra kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:1322: ces byang sgor khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:1323: yum rdo rje dril bu sku mdog ljang nag yab kyi g.yas rdo rje rgya gram gyis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1324: yum gyi phyag na dril bu 'khril ba lha'i bu'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1325: khro bo yab yum de rnams ni rdo rje'i sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)004:1326: kun kyang spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1327: chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1328: g.yon na thod pa khrag gis bkang ba bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1329: de ni dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'i mngon rtogs so //
NK029(ha)004:1330: yang na dkyil 'khor 'bring po ltar na /
NK029(ha)004:1331: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:1334: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis rten gzhal yas khang la /
NK029(ha)004:1336: zhes pa la sogs gong dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)004:1337: gzhal yas khang de'i nang gi dbus 'khor lo'i lte ba zlum po mthing kha la /
NK029(ha)004:1338: rtsibs bzhi ser po byung pa /
NK029(ha)004:1340: de'i phyi rol mu khyud rdo rje'i ra bas brgyan te /
NK029(ha)004:1341: de'i phyir rol grub chad bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)004:1343: de'i phyi rol lha rnams bsgo bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1344: de nas gdan sting ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:1345: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan /
NK029(ha)004:1346: seng ge glang chen rta dang khyung //
NK029(ha)004:1347: nam mkha' lding gi khri chen la //
NK029(ha)004:1348: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK029(ha)004:1350: dbus su mi 'jigs pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i dbus
NK029(ha)004:1351: su seng ge brgyad kyi khri 'byung par 'gyur te
NK029(ha)004:1352: / shar du stobs bcu dang ldan rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:1353: glang po che brgyad kyi khri byung pa /
NK029(ha)004:1354: lhor rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:1356: nub du dbang bcu dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:1357: rma bya brgyad kyi khri byung /
NK029(ha)004:1358: byang du 'phrin las bzhi'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:1359: shang shang brgyad kyi khri byung ngo //
NK029(ha)004:1360: de dag gi bar mtshams su rin po che'i ka bas brgyan pa la /
NK029(ha)004:1361: rin po che'i khri'i steng na mu tig gi dra bas g.yogs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1362: de'i steng pad+ma dang 'dab ma stong dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1365: rtsibs 'chan bzhi grub chad bzhi dang brgyad la /
NK029(ha)004:1366: rin po che'i khri pad zla nyi ma sum brtsegs dang ldan pa re re /
NK029(ha)004:1368: sgo bzhir bdud bzhi'i steng na nyi ma'o //
NK029(ha)004:1370: gnyis pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul la gsum ste /
NK029(ha)004:1372: thugs phyag mtshan gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)004:1375: a dkar po las k+sha sngon po byung ste /
NK029(ha)004:1376: a dang k+sha'i khyad par la yi ge bzhi bcu byung ste /
NK029(ha)004:1377: dbus tha dang tha sngon po gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1378: shar du ta dang ta dkar po gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1379: lhor da dang da ser po gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1380: nub tu d+ha dang d+ha dmar po gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1381: byang du na dang na ljang khu gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1383: lho nub du kha dang tsha nub byang du ga dang dza /
NK029(ha)004:1384: byang shar du g+ha dang dz+nya /
NK029(ha)004:1385: yang shar lho'i gru chad la sa dang ya /
NK029(ha)004:1386: lho nub tu pha dang wam /
NK029(ha)004:1387: nub byang du ba dang ra /
NK029(ha)004:1388: byang shar du b+ha dang la /
NK029(ha)004:1400: gnyis pa thugs phyag mtshan ni /
NK029(ha)004:1402: sems can ngag gi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK029(ha)004:1403: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK029(ha)004:1404: phyag mtshan bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur //
NK029(ha)004:1405: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)004:1406: shar du 'khor lo dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)004:1407: nub du pad+ma dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)004:1408: byang du ral gri dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)004:1410: rin po che'i myu gu dang me long /
NK029(ha)004:1411: lho nub du ral gri dang rin po che'i 'phreng ba /
NK029(ha)004:1412: nub byang pad+ma dkar po dang pi wam /
NK029(ha)004:1413: byang shar du rdo rje dang gar gyi lag pa /
NK029(ha)004:1414: shar lho'i gru chad la klu shing dang gdug spos /
NK029(ha)004:1415: lho nub chos kyi 'khor lo dang me tog /
NK029(ha)004:1416: nub byang du rin po che'i snye ma dang mar me /
NK029(ha)004:1417: byang shar du u pa la dang dri cha /
NK029(ha)004:1418: shar du rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK029(ha)004:1422: lho bsreg shang dang lhung bzed /
NK029(ha)004:1423: nub byang du chos kyi glegs bam /
NK029(ha)004:1424: lho nub du rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1425: shar sgor thod dbyug dang lcags kyu /
NK029(ha)004:1426: lho sgor rdo rje dbyug pa dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)004:1427: nub sgor pad+ma'i dbyug pa dang lcags sgrog /
NK029(ha)004:1428: byang sgor rgya gram dang dbyug pa dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1429: gsum pa sku phyag rgya'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK029(ha)004:1431: sems can yid kyi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK029(ha)004:1432: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las //
NK029(ha)004:1433: phra mo bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur //'od 'phros bde gshegs sku la mchod //
NK029(ha)004:1434: sems can lus kyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK029(ha)004:1435: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK029(ha)004:1436: yongs rdzogs bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur //
NK029(ha)004:1440: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes las byung pa'i rtags su sku mdog mthing nag /
NK029(ha)004:1444: dbu ral pa'i mthor gtsugs nag po 'gyings pa /
NK029(ha)004:1445: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang /
NK029(ha)004:1446: dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1447: g.yas bar ma 'khor lo //'og ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1450: phyag rgya de dag la ye shes kyi me 'bar ba /
NK029(ha)004:1451: zhabs mnyam pa'i dkyil mo dkrung gi bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1452: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1453: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1454: yum rdo rje dbyings dbyug ma yab dang mthun pa /
NK029(ha)004:1460: shar du rnam par snang mdzad me long lta bu'i
NK029(ha)004:1461: ye shes las 'byung ba'i rtags su sku mdog dkar
NK029(ha)004:1465: phyag dang po gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1466: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)004:1467: tha ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1470: swa rat+na d+h+rig mam mo ha ra ti /
NK029(ha)004:1471: zhes lho phyogs su rin chen 'byung ldan mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes las byung ba'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:1472: sku mdog gser po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)004:1475: phyag dang po gnyis rin po che dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1476: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)004:1479: pyam ra ga ti zhes nub phyogs su snang ba
NK029(ha)004:1480: mtha' yas so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes las byung
NK029(ha)004:1481: ba'i rtags su / sku mdog dmar po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)004:1484: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis pad+ma dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1485: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)004:1487: g.yon bar ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1491: zhes byang du don yon grub pa /
NK029(ha)004:1492: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes las byung ba'i rtags /
NK029(ha)004:1496: phyag dang po gnyis pa ral gri dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1497: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)004:1499: g.yon bar ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1501: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag ral pa'i thor gtsug nag po 'gying pa /
NK029(ha)004:1502: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1503: dpe byad bzang brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1504: zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs kyi dkyil mo dkrung gis rang gi gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1505: yum thams cad sku mdog yab dang 'dra ba /
NK029(ha)004:1506: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1507: g.yon pa dril bu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1508: yab yum bcu po de rnams ni langs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)004:1509: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:1510: yab yum zhal sbyor byas shing /
NK029(ha)004:1511: spyan gcig gis gcig la gzigs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1512: sems dpa' yab yum bskyed pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:1514: h+aum la s+ya sa ma ya stam /
NK029(ha)004:1515: zhes shar lho dpal ka la /
NK029(ha)004:1516: sa'i snying po sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1517: yab kyi phyag g.yas ni rin po che'i myu gu /
NK029(ha)004:1518: g.yon na skyabs sbyin yang na dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1519: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyi me long /
NK029(ha)004:1520: zhabs phyed dkrung gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1521: yab yum zhal sbyor du bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1522: yab yum de gnyis ni de bzhin gshegs pa rnam
NK029(ha)004:1523: par snang mdzad kyi thugs dang sku la 'byung pa'o
NK029(ha)004:1525: tram ma le sa ma ya ho //
NK029(ha)004:1526: zhes lho nub kyi rtsibs 'chan la nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK029(ha)004:1527: rin po che'i 'phreng ba ma sku mdog gser mo //
NK029(ha)004:1528: yab kyi g.yas na ral gri /
NK029(ha)004:1529: yum gyi g.yas na rin po che'i 'phreng ba bsnams ste yab kyi dbu la thad bcings pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1530: hri ha ho pad+ma b+ha d+ha ma /
NK029(ha)004:1531: hri g+hirti ra g+ha ya ho //
NK029(ha)004:1532: zhes nub byang gi rtsibs bar ma la //
NK029(ha)004:1533: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang /
NK029(ha)004:1534: lha mo dbyangs mkhan ma sku mdog dmar po /
NK029(ha)004:1535: yab kyi g.yas na pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1536: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyi chos kyi pi wam brdeb pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1537: dzem gu ru pa na hri /
NK029(ha)004:1538: a nirti ra ga ya mi /
NK029(ha)004:1539: zhes byang shar gyi rtsibs bar ma la phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK029(ha)004:1540: lha mo gar ma sku mdog ljang khu /
NK029(ha)004:1541: yab kyi phyag g.yas na rdo rje rtse dgu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1542: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyis gar gyi lag pa bsgyur
NK029(ha)004:1543: nas zhal zas ro mchog rgya dang ldan pa yab
NK029(ha)004:1544: la stobs pa / don yod grub pa'i thugs dang sku la 'byung ba'o /
NK029(ha)004:1545: me d+ha ra ni swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)004:1546: dza du pe pra be sha zhes shar lho'i gru chad la /
NK029(ha)004:1547: byams pa dang gdug spos ma sku mdog dkar ser /
NK029(ha)004:1548: yab kyi phyag na klu shing dang /
NK029(ha)004:1550: yum gyi phyag na gdug spos bsnams so //
NK029(ha)004:1551: thing lha ni swa da b+ha ya swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:1553: zhes lho nub kyi gru chad la sgrib pa rnam par sel ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:1554: lho me tog ma sku mdog ser mo /
NK029(ha)004:1555: yab kyi phyag na chos kyi 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1556: yum gyi phyag na me tog 'phreng ba bsnams so //
NK029(ha)004:1557: h+aum swa ra tsa ya swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)004:1558: bam ti pa pu ke ni /
NK029(ha)004:1559: zhes nub byang gi gru chad la kun tu bzang po dang /
NK029(ha)004:1560: lha mo mar me ma sku mdog dmar mo //
NK029(ha)004:1561: yab kyi phyag na rin po che'i snye ma bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1562: yum gyi phyag na mar me bsnams so //
NK029(ha)004:1563: mum sh+ri am ra ga ye swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)004:1565: zhes byang shar gyi gru chad la /
NK029(ha)004:1566: 'jam dpal gzhon nu gyur pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:1567: lha mo dri chab ma sku mdog ljang khu //
NK029(ha)004:1568: yab kyi phyag na u pa la bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1569: yum gyi phyag gnyis na dri chab bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1570: sems dpa' yab yum de rnams ni kun kyang ral pa'i thor gtsugs mnga' ba /
NK029(ha)004:1571: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1572: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1573: zhabs phyed dkrung gi bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1574: yab yum zhal sbyor du gnas te /
NK029(ha)004:1575: thugs rjes sems can thams cad la bu gcig pa la ma byams pa ltar sems ste /
NK029(ha)004:1576: yab yum de rnams ni mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK029(ha)004:1577: h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta h+aum zhes pas shar du
NK029(ha)004:1578: bcom ldan 'das byed pa po yid kun tu bzang
NK029(ha)004:1579: po sku mdog sngon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis phyag
NK029(ha)004:1580: mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya'i dkyil na /
NK029(ha)004:1581: rdo rje dkar po brtsegs pa la ye shes kyi me 'bar ba /
NK029(ha)004:1582: zhabs mnyam par bzhag pa'i dkyil mo dkrung gis pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1583: nub tu a a a badz+ra sa man+ta zhes pas
NK029(ha)004:1584: chos 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas thams cad gnas
NK029(ha)004:1585: su dag pa'i yum kun tu bzang mo //
NK029(ha)004:1586: shes bya'i bag chags dag pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:1587: sku mdog dkar mo phyag gnyis chos 'byung gi phyag rgya byas ste /
NK029(ha)004:1588: gdan pad+ma'i steng na zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i dkyil dkrung gis bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1589: yab yum de gnyis ni chos kyi sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)004:1590: dbyings mkhyen pa dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:1591: yum gyi zhal shar du gzigs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1592: mkhyen pa'i shes bya dngos po thams cad dbyings su gzigs pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:1593: yab kyi zhal nub tu gzigs so //
NK029(ha)004:1595: shar lho lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wammm bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1597: byang du lha ma yin gyi thub pa ljang nag g.yas ral gri /
NK029(ha)004:1600: lhor mi'i thub pa ser po g.yas bsreg shang /
NK029(ha)004:1603: nub byang du byol song gi thub pa ljang ser spyi bo nas chos kyi glegs bam khur ba /
NK029(ha)004:1604: ma rig pa'i mun khang 'byed pa /
NK029(ha)004:1606: lho nub du yi dwags kyi thub pa ljang gser
NK029(ha)004:1607: phyag na rin po che'i za ma tog bsnams pa'i
NK029(ha)004:1608: nang nas yi dwags thams cad la mchod sbyin gtong
NK029(ha)004:1610: byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa nag po g.yas g.yon du me chu bsnams ste /
NK029(ha)004:1611: tsha grang gi sdug bsngal sel bar mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)004:1612: thub pa de rnams ni sprul pa'i sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)004:1613: kun dge slong gi cha byad can /
NK029(ha)004:1614: 'gro ba'i don la bsnyel ba mi mnga' ba'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:1617: badz+ra d+aa ra mah+aa kro d+hi sh+aa ri la ni
NK029(ha)004:1618: h+aum phatahcesa shar sgor khro bo chen po gshen rje
NK029(ha)004:1619: gshed dang / yum rdo rje lcags kyu ma sku
NK029(ha)004:1620: mdog mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum ma
NK029(ha)004:1622: yab kyi g.yas na thod dbyug /
NK029(ha)004:1623: g.yon thod khrag yum gyi phyag na lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1624: dpal gyi chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1625: phung po'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs par sgom mo //
NK029(ha)004:1627: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:1628: ces pas lho sgor khro bo stobs po che dang /
NK029(ha)004:1629: yum rdo rje zhags pa ma sku mdog ser nag yab kyi g.yas na rdo rje dbyug pa /
NK029(ha)004:1630: g.yon na thod khrag yum gyi phyag na zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1631: 'chi bdag gi bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1633: pad+ma d+ha ra mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:1634: ces nub sgor khro bo chen po rta mgrin dang /
NK029(ha)004:1635: yum rdo rje lcags sgrog ma sku mdog dmar nag
NK029(ha)004:1636: yab kyi phyag g.yas pad+ma'i dbyug pa sbrul gyis dkris
NK029(ha)004:1637: pa bsnams pa / yum gyis phyag na lcags sgrogs bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1638: nyon mongs pa'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1639: h+aum big nan ta krid phata /
NK029(ha)004:1640: karma d+ha ra mah+aa kro ti shwa ri dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:1641: ces byang sgor khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:1642: yum rdo rje dril bu ma sku mdog ljang nag
NK029(ha)004:1643: yab kyi g.yas rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbyug pa
NK029(ha)004:1644: / yum gyi phyag na gser gyi dril chen 'khrol ba /
NK029(ha)004:1645: lha'i bu'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1646: khro bo yab yum de rnams ni rdo rje'i sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)004:1647: kun kyang spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1648: chas chen po bcu drug gi brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1649: g.yon na thod pa khrag gi gang ba bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1650: gzhal yas khang de dag kyang khro bo de dag gi me dpung gis 'khrigs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1651: me ri 'bar ba'i dkyil na bde bar gshegs pa rnams bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1652: de ni dkyil 'khor 'bring po'i bum bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)004:1654: yang na dkyil 'khor rgyas pa ltar na /
NK029(ha)004:1655: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:1656: kun tu snang dang rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:1657: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi gzhal yas khang la ldum rdzings dkar po'i 'tshal /
NK029(ha)004:1658: zhes pa la sogs gong dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)004:1659: gzhal yas khang de'i nang gi dbus 'khor lo'i lte
NK029(ha)004:1660: ba zlum po mthing kha yi dbus su 'khor lo
NK029(ha)004:1661: gser po rtsibs bzhi lte ba la seng ge la
NK029(ha)004:1665: rgyu'i a la h+aum zung lnga rnams spros /
NK029(ha)004:1666: rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang lngar babs sar sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)004:1668: phyag mtshan du gyur pa bsgom ste /
NK029(ha)004:1669: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1670: shar du 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1671: lhor rin po che dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1672: nub du pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1673: byang du ral gri dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1674: bar sang gis spro bsdu 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las /
NK029(ha)004:1675: sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:1677: badz+ra d+ha ri shwa ra h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:1678: zhes mi skyod pa dang kun bzang dbyer med pa sku mdog mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)004:1680: dbus mthing pa la ral ba'i thor gtsugs nag po 'gying ba /
NK029(ha)004:1681: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1682: g.yas bar ma 'khor lo //'og ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1685: phyag rgya de dag la ye shes kyi me 'bar ba /
NK029(ha)004:1686: zhabs snyoms pa'i dkyil dkrung gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1687: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1688: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1689: yum rdo rje dbyings phyag ma sku mdog yab dang mthun pa zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1694: sems dpa'i rdo rje sngon po 'khor lo dril bu bsnams pa yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1695: yum rdo rje bstan ma sngon mo /
NK029(ha)004:1696: rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1697: yab sems dpa'i dkyil dkrung ste /
NK029(ha)004:1698: zhabs g.yon pa cung zad gdan la 'bebs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1701: zhes rin po chen rdo rje sku mdog sngon po
NK029(ha)004:1702: rin po che dang dril bu bsnams pas yum la
NK029(ha)004:1703: 'khyud pa / 'bar ma rdo rje sngon mo //
NK029(ha)004:1704: rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1707: zhes pas rdo rje sku mdog sngon po pad+ma dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1708: sdud ma sngon mo rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1711: zhes las kyi rdo rje sku mdog sngon po ral
NK029(ha)004:1712: gri dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)004:1713: / bskyod ma rdo rje sku mdog sngon mo yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1716: shar gyi 'khor lo lte ba rtsibs bzhi gser po'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)004:1717: glang po che la sogs pa gdan drug brtsegs brtsegs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1718: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i steng du babs sar sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)004:1719: lha rang rang gi phyag mtshan du gyur ste /
NK029(ha)004:1720: dbus su 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1721: shar du rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1722: lhor lcags kyu dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1724: byang du rgya gram dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1725: yang sar sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)004:1728: 'khor lo'i dbus su rnam par snang mdzad sku mdog dkar po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)004:1730: phyag dang po gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1731: g.yas bar pa na rdo rje /
