NK029(ha)004:1732: tha ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1733: g.yon bar pa na pa pad+ma /
NK029(ha)004:1734: tha ma na ral gri yum bud+d+ha dbyings phyag ma
NK029(ha)004:1735: zhal gcig phyag gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bu bsnams
NK029(ha)004:1739: zhes rdo rje sems dpa' dkar po /
NK029(ha)004:1740: rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1741: yum la se ma dkar mo me long dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1744: zhes rdo rje rgyal po sku mdog dkar po lcags
NK029(ha)004:1745: kyu dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)004:1746: / d+hu pe ma sku mdog dkar po spos khang dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1750: zhes rdo rje chags pa sku mdog dkar po mda'
NK029(ha)004:1751: gzhu dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)004:1752: / yum rdo rje lcags kyu ma sku mdog dkar
NK029(ha)004:1753: mo lcags kyu dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la
NK029(ha)004:1754: / 'khyud pa / g.yon du badz+ra sa du //
NK029(ha)004:1756: zhes pas rdo rje legs pa se gol brdab pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1757: yum rdo rje sgrol ma sngo //'phreng ba bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1758: lho rtsibs sngon po'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)004:1759: 'khor lo gser po rtsibs bzhi'i lte ba rta mchog brgyad la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)004:1760: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)004:1761: rgyu'i yi ge a las tram zung lnga 'phros /
NK029(ha)004:1762: dbus dang rtsibs bzhi la babs /
NK029(ha)004:1764: yig 'bru rnams kyang 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las /
NK029(ha)004:1765: 'khor lo lte ba'i gdan gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)004:1766: rin po che dang dril bur gyur par bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:1767: de bzhin du shar gyi rtsibs la /
NK029(ha)004:1769: lho'i rtsibs la nyi ma dang me tog nub kyi rtsibs la rgyan dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)004:1775: dbus su rin chen 'byung ldan sku mdog gser po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)004:1778: phyag dang po gnyis rin po che dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1779: g.yas bar pa na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)004:1781: g.yon bar pa na pad+ma dang /
NK029(ha)004:1783: yum rin chen dbyings phyug ma sku mdog gser mo
NK029(ha)004:1784: rin po che dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la
NK029(ha)004:1785: 'khyud pa / yab yum gnyis zhabs brtul zhugs kyi dkyil mo dkrung gi bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1786: mdun du rdo rje rin po che sku mdog ser
NK029(ha)004:1787: po rin po che'i myu gu dang dril bu bsnams
NK029(ha)004:1789: yum rdo rje 'phreng ba ma 'phreng ba dang dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1790: g.yas su badz+ra su rgya tram /
NK029(ha)004:1792: zhes rdo rje gzi brjid sku mdog ser po nyi dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1793: yum me tog ma ser mo me tog dang dril bu bsnams nas yab 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1794: rgyab du badz+ra ke tu tram /
NK029(ha)004:1797: rdo rje rgyal mtshan sku mdog ser po rgyal mtshan dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1798: yum rdo rje zhags pa ma ser mo yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1801: badz+ra ra tri tram zhes rdo rje bzhad pa sku
NK029(ha)004:1802: mdog ser po tshems kyi 'phreng ba dang dril bu
NK029(ha)004:1804: yum rdo rje bsil ma sku mdog ser mo bsil
NK029(ha)004:1805: g.yab dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa'o
NK029(ha)004:1806: // nub rtsibs sngon po'i steng du 'khor lo gser
NK029(ha)004:1807: po rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar rma bya la sogs pa'i
NK029(ha)004:1808: // gdan drug brtsegs / rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)004:1809: rgyu'i yi ge a las hrihzunga lnga 'phros /
NK029(ha)004:1810: dbus dang rtsibs bzhi la babs /
NK029(ha)004:1812: yig 'bru rnams 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las /
NK029(ha)004:1813: 'khor lo'i lte ba'i gdan gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)004:1816: pad+ma myu gu dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1817: g.yas su ral gri dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1820: g.yon du lce dang dril bu sogs /
NK029(ha)004:1822: am a ro lig pyam ra ga ra ti /
NK029(ha)004:1824: snang ba mtha' yas sku mdog dmar po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)004:1827: phyag drug dang po gnyis kyis pad+ma dang dril bus yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1828: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)004:1830: g.yon bar ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1831: tha ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1832: yum pad+ma dbyings phyug ma sku mdog dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu bsnams pas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1835: badz+ra girti hri zhes rdo rje chos sku mdog dmar
NK029(ha)004:1836: po pad+ma dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud
NK029(ha)004:1837: pa / yum rdo rje glu chen ma dmar mo
NK029(ha)004:1838: pi wamm dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud
NK029(ha)004:1843: rdo rje rnon po dmar po ral gri dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1844: yum rdo rje dmar mo mar me dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1846: badz+ra po ta hrih zhes rdo rje sku dmar po
NK029(ha)004:1847: 'khor lo dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud
NK029(ha)004:1848: pa / yum rdo rje lcags sgrogs ma dmar mo
NK029(ha)004:1849: lcags sgrogs dang dril bu bsnams nas nas yab la
NK029(ha)004:1851: badz+ra pa sha hrih badz+ra a lo ke hri /
NK029(ha)004:1852: zhes rdo rje smra ba sku mdog dmar po rdo
NK029(ha)004:1853: rje'i lce dang dril bu bsnams pas yum la 'khyud
NK029(ha)004:1854: pa / yum rdo rje gsal tra ma dmar mo
NK029(ha)004:1855: sgron me dang dril bu bsnams ste yab la 'khyud
NK029(ha)004:1856: pa / pa'o // byang rtsibs sngon po'i steng du /
NK029(ha)004:1857: 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi lte bar shang shang brgyad la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)004:1858: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)004:1859: rgyu'i yi ge a las ha zung lnga 'phros /
NK029(ha)004:1860: dbus dang rtsibs bzhi la babs /
NK029(ha)004:1861: sar sang gi spro bsdus yig 'bru rnams 'od du
NK029(ha)004:1862: zhu ba'i 'od phung gi 'khor lo'i lte ba'i gdan
NK029(ha)004:1863: gyi steng du / rdo rje rgya gram dang dril bu //
NK029(ha)004:1864: mdun du ral gri dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1865: g.yas su rdo rje'i go cha dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1866: rgyab tu mche ba dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:1867: g.yon du rdo rje dang dril bu la sogs /
NK029(ha)004:1870: tam badz+ra ra ti zhes dbus su don yod grub pa sku mdog ljang khu zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)004:1873: phyag dang po gnyis rgya gram dang dril bu yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1874: g.yas bar ma na rdo rje /
NK029(ha)004:1876: g.yon bar ma na rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:1878: yum las kyi dbyings phyug ma sku mdog ljang khu
NK029(ha)004:1879: rgya gram dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud
NK029(ha)004:1884: rdo rje las sku mdog ljang khu ral gri dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1885: yum gar ma ljang khu rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin zhing /
NK029(ha)004:1886: gar bsgyur ste yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1891: rdo rje bsrungs ba sku mdog ljang khu go cha dang dril bu bsnams ste yum 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:1892: yum rdo rje byug pa ma ljang khu dri'i dung
NK029(ha)004:1893: chos dang dril bu bsnams ste yab la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)004:1897: zhes rdo rje gdon sbyin sku mdog ljang khu mche
NK029(ha)004:1898: ba dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)004:1901: zhes khu tshur ljang khu rdo rje khu tshur gyis
NK029(ha)004:1902: rdo rje dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)004:1903: / yum rdo rje 'bebs ma rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams nas ye shes 'bebs bar mdzad pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1904: de ltar gtso 'khor de dag yab yum thams cad kyang zhi ba'i tshul dgu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1905: brgyad chas bcu gsum gyis brgyan par bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:1906: dbus kyi gtso bo rnams rdo rje dkyil dkrungs dang /
NK029(ha)004:1907: 'khor rnams sems da pa'i tshul can yab yum rnams 'khril sbyor mdzad pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1908: de nas rgyu'i yi ge a las /
NK029(ha)004:1909: yig ge sum cu rtsa gcig 'phros ste /
NK029(ha)004:1910: shar lho'i rtsibs 'chan la ka dang tsa /
NK029(ha)004:1911: lho nub du kha dang tsha /
NK029(ha)004:1912: nub byang du ga dang dza /
NK029(ha)004:1913: byang shar du g+ha dang dz+ha /
NK029(ha)004:1916: lho nub du ya dang wa /
NK029(ha)004:1917: nub byang du ba dang ra /
NK029(ha)004:1918: byang shar du b+ha dang la /
NK029(ha)004:1920: lha rnams kyi byang du i /
NK029(ha)004:1929: lha rnams kyi shar du sha /
NK029(ha)004:1931: lha rnams kyi nub blo 'bur gyi steng du babs /
NK029(ha)004:1933: phyag mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis su gyur /
NK029(ha)004:1934: sar sang gi spro bsdus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK029(ha)004:1936: h'u la s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK029(ha)004:1937: zhes shar lho'i dbal ka la /
NK029(ha)004:1938: sa'i snying bo yab yum sku mdog dkar po /
NK029(ha)004:1940: yab kyi phyag na rin po che'i myu gu /
NK029(ha)004:1941: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyis me long zhabs phyed dkrung gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1942: yab yum zhal sbyor du byas pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1944: tram ma le sa ma ya ho //
NK029(ha)004:1946: lho nub kyi rtsibs 'chan la nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK029(ha)004:1947: rin po che'i 'phreng ba ma sku mdog ser mo //
NK029(ha)004:1948: yab kyi g.yas na ral gri /
NK029(ha)004:1949: yum gyi phyag na rin po che'i 'phreng ba bsnams ste /
NK029(ha)004:1950: yab kyi dbu la thod bcings pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1951: hri ha ho pad+ma b+ha tra ma /
NK029(ha)004:1953: zhes nub byang gi rtsibs bar ma /
NK029(ha)004:1954: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang /
NK029(ha)004:1955: lha mo dbyangs can ma sku mdog dmar mo //
NK029(ha)004:1956: yab kyi g.yas na pad+ma dkar po bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1957: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyi chos kyi pi wam bsdeb pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1958: dzem ku ru pa na hri /
NK029(ha)004:1959: a ni rti ra ga ya mi /
NK029(ha)004:1961: byang shar gyi rtsibs bar la phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK029(ha)004:1962: lha mo gar mkhan ma sku mdog ljang khu /
NK029(ha)004:1963: yab kyi phyag g.yas na rdo rje rtse dgu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1964: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyis gar gyi lag pa bsgyur nas /
NK029(ha)004:1965: zhal zas ro mchog brgyad dang ldan pa yab la stobs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1967: dza du be pra be sha zhes shar lho'i gru chad la /
NK029(ha)004:1968: byams pa dang gdug spos ma sku mdog dkar ser /
NK029(ha)004:1969: yab kyi phyag g.yas na klu shing dang g+hen d+he bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1970: yum gyi phyag na gdug spos bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1974: zhes lho nub kyi gru chad la /
NK029(ha)004:1975: sgrib pa rnam par sel ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:1976: lha mo me tog ma sku mdog gser mo //
NK029(ha)004:1977: yab kyi phyag na chos kyi 'khor lo bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1978: yum gyi phyag na me tog gi 'phreng ba bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1979: h'u swa ra tsa sa swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:1980: bam ta pa bu ke ni /
NK029(ha)004:1981: zhes nub byang gi gru chad la /
NK029(ha)004:1983: lha mo mar me ma sku mdog dmar mo //
NK029(ha)004:1984: yab kyi phyag na rin po che'i snye ma bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:1985: yum gyi phyag na mar me bsnams so //
NK029(ha)004:1986: mum sh+ri am ra ga ya swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:1988: byang shar gyi gru chad la /
NK029(ha)004:1989: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:1990: lha mo dri chab ma sku mdog ljang khu yab kyi phyag na /
NK029(ha)004:1992: yum gyi phyag gnyis kyi dri chab bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:1993: sems dpa' yab yum de rnams ni kun kyang dbu ral pa'i thor gtsugs mnga' ba /
NK029(ha)004:1994: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:1995: dpe byad brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:1996: zhabs phyed dkrung gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:1997: yab yum zhal sbyor du byas te /
NK029(ha)004:1998: thugs rjes sems can thams cad la bu gcig pa la ma byams pa ltar sems te /
NK029(ha)004:1999: yab yum de rnams ni mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK029(ha)004:2000: h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2002: shar du bcom ldan 'das rdo rje byed pa po /
NK029(ha)004:2003: yid kun tu bzang po sku mdog sngon po zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:2004: mnyam pa'i phyag rgya'i dkyil na /
NK029(ha)004:2005: rdo rje dkar po brtsegs pa la //
NK029(ha)004:2007: zhabs mnyam pa'i dkyil mo dkrung gis pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2008: nub tu a a a badz+ra sa man+ta /
NK029(ha)004:2010: chos 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas thams cad gnas su dag pa'i yum kun bzang mo //
NK029(ha)004:2011: shes bya'i bag chags dag pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:2012: sku mdog dkar mo phyag gnyis chos 'byung gi phyag rgya bcas te /
NK029(ha)004:2014: zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i dkyil dkrung gi bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2015: yab yum de gnyis ni chos kyi sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)004:2016: dbyings mkhyen dang ldan pa'i rtags su yum gyis zhal shar du gzigs pa /
NK029(ha)004:2017: mkhyen pa'i shes bya dngos po thams cad dbyings su gzigs pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:2018: yab kyi zhal nub tu gzigs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2020: shar lhor lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wam bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:2022: byang du lha min gyi thub pa ljang nag g.yas ral gri g.yon khrab /
NK029(ha)004:2024: lhor mi'i thub pa ser po g.yas bsreg shang /
NK029(ha)004:2027: nub byang du byol song gi thub pa ljang ser /
NK029(ha)004:2028: spyi bo nas chos kyi glegs bam khur ba /
NK029(ha)004:2029: ma rig pa'i mun khang 'byed pa /
NK029(ha)004:2031: lho nub du yi dwags kyi thub pa ljang ser
NK029(ha)004:2032: phyag na rin po che'i za ma tog bsnams pa'i
NK029(ha)004:2033: nang nas yi dwags thams cad la mchod sbyin gtong
NK029(ha)004:2035: byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa nag po g.yas su me chu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:2036: tsha grang gi sdug bsngal sel bar mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)004:2037: thub pa de rnams ni sprul pa'i sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)004:2038: kun dge slong gi cha byad can /
NK029(ha)004:2039: 'gro ba'i don la bsnyel pa mi mnga' ba'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:2042: badz+ra da ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la na h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2043: ces shar sgor khro bo chen po gshin rje gshed dang /
NK029(ha)004:2044: yum rdo rje lcags kyu ma sku mdog mthing nag
NK029(ha)004:2045: zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs pa
NK029(ha)004:2046: / yab kyi g.yas na thod dbyug /
NK029(ha)004:2048: yum gyi phyag na lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:2049: dpal gyi chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)004:2050: phung po'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs par bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)004:2052: rat+na d+ha ra mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri dza la h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2054: lho sgor khro bo chen po stobs po che dang /
NK029(ha)004:2055: yum rdo rje zhags pa ma sku mdog gser nag g.yas na rdo rje dbyug pa /
NK029(ha)004:2057: yum gyi phyag na zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:2058: 'chi bdag gi bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2060: pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2062: nub sgor khro bo chen po rta mgrin dang /
NK029(ha)004:2063: yum rdo rje lcags sgrogs ma /
NK029(ha)004:2064: sku mdog dmar nag yab kyi phyag g.yas na pad+ma'i dbyug pa /
NK029(ha)004:2065: sprul gyis dkris pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:2066: yum gyi phyag na lcags sgrogs bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:2067: nyon mongs pa'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o h+aum big nan ta krid phata /
NK029(ha)004:2068: karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwi ra dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2069: ces byang sgor khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:2070: yum rdo rje dril bu ma sku mdog ljang nag yab kyi g.yas rdo rje rgya gram dbyug pa /
NK029(ha)004:2071: yum gyi phyag na gser gyi dril chen 'khrol ba /
NK029(ha)004:2072: lha'i bu'i bdud kyi gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2073: khro bo yab yum de rnams rdo rje'i sku yin ste /
NK029(ha)004:2074: kun kyang spyan gsum mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK029(ha)004:2075: chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2076: g.yon na thod pa khrag gi gang ba bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2077: gzhal yas khang de dag kyang khro bo de dag
NK029(ha)004:2078: gi me dpung 'khrigs pa me ri 'bar ba'i dkyil
NK029(ha)004:2079: na bde bar gshegs pa rnams bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2080: de ni dkyil 'khor rgyas pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:2082: mdun bskyed gang la'ang rung ngo //
NK029(ha)004:2083: yang na tshom bu gcig pa'i dkyil 'khor ltar na /
NK029(ha)004:2084: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:2085: kun tu snang gi ting 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:2087: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis rten gzhal yas khang ldum rdzings dkar po'i tshal /
NK029(ha)004:2088: zhes pa la sogs pa gong dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)004:2089: gzhal yas khang de'i nang gi dbus su 'khor lo'i
NK029(ha)004:2090: lte ba zlum po mthing ka rtsibs bzhi ser po
NK029(ha)004:2094: seng ge la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)004:2095: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)004:2096: sgo bzhir nyi ma bdud bzhi'i gdan la /
NK029(ha)004:2097: rgyu'i yi ge a las h+aum zung lnga 'phros /
NK029(ha)004:2098: lte ba dang rtsibs bzhi la babs /
NK029(ha)004:2100: h+aum h+aum h+aum bam h+aum ho //
NK029(ha)004:2102: sar sang gi spro bsdus 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las phyag mtshan du gyur par sgom ste /
NK029(ha)004:2103: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:2106: lhor rin po che dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:2107: nub du pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:2108: byang du ral gri dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:2109: shar sgor thod dbyug dang lcags kyu /
NK029(ha)004:2110: lho sgor rdo rje rtse lnga dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)004:2111: nub sgor thod sbrul dang lcags sgrogs /
NK029(ha)004:2112: byang sgor sna tshogs rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams par bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:2115: sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed de /
NK029(ha)004:2119: zhes pa mi bskyod pa sku mdog sngon po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK029(ha)004:2123: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:2124: g.yas bar ma 'khor lo //'og ma rin po che /
NK029(ha)004:2127: phyag rgya de dag la ye shes kyi me 'bar ba zhabs mnyam pa'i dkyil dkrungs gis bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:2128: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:2129: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:2130: yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma sku mdog sngon po /
NK029(ha)004:2132: rdo rje dang dril bus yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:2136: sems dpa' sngon po 'khor lo dang dril bu bsnams ste yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:2137: yum rdo rje bstan ma rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:2138: yab sems dpa'i dkyil dkrung ste /
NK029(ha)004:2139: zhabs g.yon pa cung zad gdan la babs pa /
NK029(ha)004:2142: zhes rin po che rdo rje sku mdog sngon po
NK029(ha)004:2143: rin po che dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la
NK029(ha)004:2144: 'khyud pa / bar ma rdo rje sngon mo rdo
NK029(ha)004:2145: rje dang dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)004:2149: chos sku rdo rje sku mdog sngon po pad+ma dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:2150: yum sdud ma sngon mo rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams ste yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:2153: zhes las kyi rdo rje sku mdog sngon po ral
NK029(ha)004:2154: gri dang dril bu bsnams nas yum la 'khyud pa
NK029(ha)004:2155: / bskyod ma rdo rje sku mdog sngon mo yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:2156: de ltar gtso 'khor yab yum thams cad kyang zhi ba'i tshul dgu dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:2157: brgyan chas bcu gsum gyis brgyan par bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:2158: de yang dbus kyi gtso bo rdo rje dkyil dkrung dang /
NK029(ha)004:2159: 'khor rnams sems dpa'i tshul can yum rnams kyis g.yon zur nas 'khyud pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2163: gshin rje gshed smug nag pe con bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:2164: rdo rje lcags kyu ma sngon mo lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:2166: badz+ra pa sha h+aum zhes lho sgor stobs po che ser nag rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:2167: rdo rje zhags pa ma ser mo zhags pa bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:2170: zhes nub sgor rta mgrin dmar nag thod pa sprul gyis dkris pa bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:2171: rdo rje lcags sgrogs ma dmar mo lcags sgrogs bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:2175: byang sgor bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang nag /
NK029(ha)004:2176: sna tshogs rdo rje bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:2177: rdo rje dril bu ma ljang khu dril bu 'khrol ba /
NK029(ha)004:2178: sgo ma yab yum brgyad po thams cad kyang /
NK029(ha)004:2179: nyi ma'i gdan la zhal phyogs pa /
NK029(ha)004:2181: yum g.yas brkyang gis gyad kyi dor thabs kyis bsgrad pa /
NK029(ha)004:2182: khro bo'i chas kyi brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)004:2183: me ri dang me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa bskyed do /
NK029(ha)004:2184: de ni tshom bu gcig pa'i lha ste /
NK029(ha)004:2185: bum bskyed dang mdun bskyed gang yang rung pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2186: tshom bu gsum pa'i dkyil 'khor ltar na /
NK029(ha)004:2187: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:2188: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:2190: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rten gzhal yas khang gi ldum rdzings dkar po'i tshal /
NK029(ha)004:2191: zhes pa man chad gong dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)004:2192: gzhal yas khang de'i nang gi dbus 'khor lo'i lte ba zlum po mthing kha rtsibs bzhi sngon po /
NK029(ha)004:2195: sgo dbus lte ba sngon po'i dbus su 'khor lo
NK029(ha)004:2196: ser po rtsibs bzhi pa'i lte bar seng ge la
NK029(ha)004:2198: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)004:2199: shar rtsibs sngon po'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)004:2200: 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar /
NK029(ha)004:2201: glang po che la sogs gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)004:2202: rtsibs bzhi la pad nyi zla ba'i gdan /
NK029(ha)004:2203: nub rtsibs sngon pa'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)004:2204: 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar rma bya la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)004:2205: rtsibs bzhi la pad+ma nyi zla ba'i gdan /
NK029(ha)004:2206: gru chad bzhi dang sgo bzhi la nyi ma la
NK029(ha)004:2207: sogs kyi gdan rgyu'i yi ge a las h+aum zung
NK029(ha)004:2208: lnga / dbus su babs zung lnga /
NK029(ha)004:2210: nub kyi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i steng du babs /
NK029(ha)004:2212: gru chad bzhi dang sgo bzhir babs /
NK029(ha)004:2213: sar sang gi 'od du zhu ba las /
NK029(ha)004:2214: phyag mtshan bzhi bcu zhe drug du gyur sar sang 'od du zhu ba las /
NK029(ha)004:2215: sku yongs su rdzogs pa zhe drug tu gyur te /
NK029(ha)004:2217: dbus su rdo rje sems dpa' zhal gsum phyag drug yab yum /
NK029(ha)004:2219: rdoo rje rigs kyi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad sgom /
NK029(ha)004:2220: shar rtsibs kyi 'khor lo'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)004:2221: rnam snang dkar po zhal gsum phyag drug yab yum /
NK029(ha)004:2222: rtsibs bzhi la de bzhin rigs kyi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad sgom /
NK029(ha)004:2223: nub rtsibs kyi 'khor lo'i dbus su snang mtha' yab
NK029(ha)004:2224: yum zhal gsum phyag drug la pad+ma rigs kyi sems
NK029(ha)004:2225: dpa' yab yum brgyad kyis bskor bar bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)004:2226: ci ltar bsgom pa'i tshul ni /
NK029(ha)004:2227: gong dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i skabs su bshad pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus dang /
NK029(ha)004:2231: badz+ra krod+ha h+aum ka ra h+aum zhes pas /
NK029(ha)004:2232: shar sgor khro bo rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:2233: yum rdo rje snyem ma sku mdog dmar mo zhal
NK029(ha)004:2234: gcig phyag gnyis lcags kyu dang dril bu bsnams pa
NK029(ha)004:2235: / badz+ra kro d+ha ni la rten ta h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2236: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2238: khro bo chen po dbyug sngon can sku mdog dkar po dang /
NK029(ha)004:2239: yum rdo rje sder mo yab yum zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:2240: badz+ra kro d+ha ya man+ta ka h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2241: pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2242: lho sgor khro bo chen po gshen rje gshed dang /
NK029(ha)004:2243: yum rdo rje dur khrod bdag mo sku mdog ser mo zhags pa dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:2244: badz+ra kro d+ha ar+ya a tsa la h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2245: ban d+ha ban d+ha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2246: lho nub gyi gru chad la /
NK029(ha)004:2247: khro bo chen po mi g.yo sngon po /
NK029(ha)004:2248: yum rdo rje gtun khu ma sku mdog dmar gser zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:2249: badz+ra kro ta ha ya g+h+ri wa hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2250: nub sgor khro bo chen po rta mgrin dang /
NK029(ha)004:2251: yum rdo rje gtum mo sku mdog dmar mo zhal
NK029(ha)004:2252: gcig phyag gnyis lcags sgrogs dang dril bu bsnams pa
NK029(ha)004:2253: / badz+ra kro ta a par tsi ta h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2254: ti tha ti tha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2255: nub byang gi gru chad la /
NK029(ha)004:2256: khro bo chen po gzhan gyi mi thub pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:2257: yum rdo rje mda' snyem ma sku mdog dmar ljang zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:2258: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2259: tshin d+hi tshin d+ha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2261: khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:2262: yum rdo rje rlung 'byin ma sku mdog ljang khu rgya gram dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:2263: badz+ra kro d+ha kre lo kya b+ai dza ya h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2264: ban d+ha ban d+ha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2266: khro bo chen po khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:2267: yum rdo rje krod ma sku mdog dkar ljang zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK029(ha)004:2268: khro bo yab yum de rnams ni nyi ma'i gdan la yab g.yon brkyang dang /
NK029(ha)004:2269: yum g.yas brkyang gi dor thabs kyis bsgrad pa /
NK029(ha)004:2270: khro bo'i chas kyis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)004:2271: me ri me dpung gi khung na bzhugs pa bskyed do //
NK029(ha)004:2272: de ni tshom bu gsum pa'i mngon rtogs de /
NK029(ha)004:2273: lha bzhi bcu zhe drug yod /
NK029(ha)004:2274: tshom bu lnga pa'i mngon rtogs ltar na /
NK029(ha)004:2275: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:2276: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:2277: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi brten gzhal
NK029(ha)004:2278: yas khang gi ldum rdzings dkar po'i tshil zhes pa
NK029(ha)004:2279: yan chad gong dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)004:2280: gzhal yas khang de'i nang gi dbus su /
NK029(ha)004:2281: 'khor lo'i lte ba zlum po mthing kha rtsibs bzhi sngon po /
NK029(ha)004:2283: gru chad phyogs mdog la sgo dbus lte ba sngon
NK029(ha)004:2284: po'i dbus su 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi pa'i
NK029(ha)004:2285: lte bar / seng ge la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)004:2286: rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)004:2287: shar rtsibs sngon po'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)004:2288: 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi lte bar /
NK029(ha)004:2289: glang po che la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)004:2290: rtsibs bzhi pad nyi zla ba'i gdan /
NK029(ha)004:2291: lho rtsibs sngon po'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)004:2292: 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi lte bar rta mchog la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)004:2293: rtsibs bzhi la pad nyi nyi ma'i gdan /
NK029(ha)004:2294: nub rtsibs sngon po'i dbus su 'khor lo ser po
NK029(ha)004:2295: rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar rma bya la sogs pa'i gdan
NK029(ha)004:2296: drug brtsegs / rtsibs bzhi la pad nyi zla ba'i gdan /
NK029(ha)004:2297: byang rtsibs sngon po'i dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i lte bar /
NK029(ha)004:2298: shang shang la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK029(ha)004:2299: rtsibs bzhi la pad nyi zla ba'i gdan /
NK029(ha)004:2300: gru chad bzhi sgo bzhi steng 'og gnyis dang /
NK029(ha)004:2301: phyogs bcur nyi ma dang phyogs skyong bcu'i gdan sgom /
NK029(ha)004:2302: rgyu'i yi ge a las h+aum zung lnga dbus su bab zung lnga shar du /
NK029(ha)004:2306: h+aum bsgril bcu phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og gnyis dang bcu ru babs /
NK029(ha)004:2307: rgyu'i a dbus kyi h+aum la thim sar sang gis
NK029(ha)004:2308: 'od du zhu ba las phyag mtshan bdun bcur gyur
NK029(ha)004:2309: / sar sang gi 'od du zhu ba las sku yongs rdzogs bdun bcur gyur te /
NK029(ha)004:2310: ci ltar bsgom pa'i tshul ni /
NK029(ha)004:2311: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i skabs ltar pho brang gi lha lnga bcur bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:2312: khro bo yab yum bcu drug kyang /
NK029(ha)004:2313: gong tshom bu gsum pa ltar la /
NK029(ha)004:2314: badz+ra kro ta h+aum ka ra phata /
NK029(ha)004:2315: gar tsha gar tsha h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2316: steng du khro bo chen po h+aum mdzad yab yum /
NK029(ha)004:2317: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa pa la h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2318: s+pho ta s+pho ta h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2319: 'og tu khro bo chen po stobs po che yab yum /
NK029(ha)004:2320: lha bdun bcu po de ni tshom bu lnga pa'i mngon rtogs te /
NK029(ha)004:2321: bum bskyed dang mdun bskyed gang la'ang mthad do //
NK029(ha)004:2322: de yongs su rdzogs pa'i cho 'phrul de song nas /
NK029(ha)004:2324: byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)004:2325: mchod pa 'bul ba'i cho 'phrul dang gsum 'og mdun bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)004:2326: gong bdag bskyed thun mong du bstan no //
NK029(ha)004:2327: gsum pa mdun bskyed la drug ste /
NK029(ha)004:2328: dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'i mdun bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)004:2330: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i mdun bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)004:2331: tshom bu gcig pa'i mdun bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)004:2332: tshom bu gsum pa'i mdun bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)004:2333: tshom bu lnga pa'i mdun bskyed dang /
NK029(ha)004:2334: de drug gi de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:2335: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK029(ha)004:2337: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin las bskyed pa'i
NK029(ha)004:2338: cho 'phrul yan chad gong bum bskyed dang mthun la
NK029(ha)004:2339: / gnyis pa dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK029(ha)004:2340: don ye shes lnga'i dbang dang /
NK029(ha)004:2341: rtags rgyal ba rigs lnga'i dbu brgyan gyi dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)004:2343: ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:2345: chos thams cad yid dam rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor de
NK029(ha)004:2346: dag don dam par chos kyi dbyings mnyam pa chen
NK029(ha)004:2347: po'i rang bzhin la g.yos pa med par rtog pa
NK029(ha)004:2350: rgyal ba de dag gi spyi gtsug tu mi skyod
NK029(ha)004:2351: pa sku mdog mthing kha res dbu brgyan par bya'o
NK029(ha)004:2352: // ma h+aa a ta ri sha dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa at+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:2353: ces don dam par rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor de dag thams cad kyang /
NK029(ha)004:2354: chos kyi dbyings las 'gag pa med pa'i ye shes rang snang pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2355: rtags rgyal ba de dag gi sprul bar rnam par
NK029(ha)004:2356: snang mdzad sku mdog dkar po re re sgom mo
NK029(ha)004:2357: // ma h+aa sa man+ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:2358: zhes don dam par rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor la 'gag pa'i snang ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:2359: ngo bo chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos par ye nas dbyer med par shes par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:2360: rtags sna ltag g.yas par rin chen 'byung ldan sku mdog ser po re re bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)004:2361: ma h+aa pra d+ha spra b+ae sha dz+nya na badz+ra s+w+aa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:2362: zhes rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor de dag kyang gdul bya
NK029(ha)004:2363: tha dad pa la mos pa tha dad par shes
NK029(ha)004:2364: par bya'o // rtags ltag pa'i steng du snang ba mtha' yas sku dmar po re bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)004:2365: mah+aa kri te a nu ta dz+nya na badz+ra s+w+aab+ha wa ad+ma ko ham zhes /
NK029(ha)004:2366: don dam par rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du ma 'gag par snang ba ni gzhan don no //
NK029(ha)004:2367: ngo bo ma skyes pa ni bdag don ste /
NK029(ha)004:2369: don dam phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2370: rtags sna ltag g.yon pa'i steng du don yod grub pa re re bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)004:2371: de nas rgyal ba de dag gi dbu la rin po che'i dbu brgyan dang /
NK029(ha)004:2379: sham thabs la sogs pa'i rgyan chen po rnams kyis brgyan par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:2380: de ni dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK029(ha)004:2381: gsum pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul gnyis ni /
NK029(ha)004:2382: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)004:2383: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor phyogs bcu nas spyan drangs nas byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2384: dang po ni sarba ta tha ga ta mah+aa ka ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:2385: zhes bdag gi dbu'i nang du zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)004:2386: sku rdo rje sku mdog dkar po 'khor lo dang dril bu can /
NK029(ha)004:2387: de'i thugs khar 'khor lo gyis mtshan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2388: sarba ta tha ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swab+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:2389: zhes bdag gi lce thog du pad+ma'i steng du gsung
NK029(ha)004:2390: rdo rje sku mdog dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu
NK029(ha)004:2391: can / de'i thugs khar pad+ma am gyis mtshan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2392: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa tsit+ta badz+ra s+w+aab+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:2393: bdag gi thugs khar nyi ma'i steng du /
NK029(ha)004:2394: thugs rdo rje sku mdog mthing nag rdo rje dang dril bu can /
NK029(ha)004:2395: de'i thugs khar rdo rje h'u gis mtshan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2396: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa a nu ra ga badz+ra s+w+aa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:2397: lte bar rin po che zur brgyad kyi steng du /
NK029(ha)004:2398: chags pa'i rdo rje sku mdog gser po rin po che dang dril bu can /
NK029(ha)004:2399: de'i thugs khar rin po che zur brgyad pa sogs mtshan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2400: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa pu tsa badz+ra swa b+ha wa a d+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:2401: zhes gsang gnas su chos 'byung gru gsum gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)004:2402: mchod pa'i rdo rje sku mdog ljang khu ral gri dang dril bu can /
NK029(ha)004:2403: de'i thugs kar ral gri ham gis mtshan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2404: lha de dag thams cad kyi thugs khar ye shes sems dpa' re re /
NK029(ha)004:2405: de'i thugs khar phyag mtshan la rang sngags kyi yi ge rnams kyis mtshan pa re re bsgom /
NK029(ha)004:2406: de'i mtha' bskor du rang rang gi sngags kyis bskor ba re re bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)004:2407: gnyis pa spyan drangs nas byin gyis brlabs pa la gsum ste /
NK029(ha)004:2410: bstan par bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:2411: dang po ni se go la snol mar rtog cing /
NK029(ha)004:2412: h+aum dmigs med mkha' ltar dag cing khyab pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)004:2413: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang /
NK029(ha)004:2414: thugs rje'i nga nga can chos sku dag pa la /
NK029(ha)004:2415: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)004:2416: badz+ra sa man ta dza h+aum dza /
NK029(ha)004:2417: gnyis pa spyan drangs pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:2418: yod med stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor mthus //
NK029(ha)004:2419: nam mkha' bzhin du dam tshig nye bar gshegs //
NK029(ha)004:2420: ye shes rgya mtsho rnam par grol ba'i klong //
NK029(ha)004:2421: mi gnas mi dmigs nam mkha'i dbyings gnas shing //
NK029(ha)004:2422: tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs thams cad dbyings kyi lha //
NK029(ha)004:2423: longs spyod rdzogs mdzad rol ba chen po'i sku //
NK029(ha)004:2424: rdo rje sems dpa' bskal bzang dpal khyod bdag /
NK029(ha)004:2425: thabs kyi ma rmongs bde chen dbyings nas bzhengs /
NK029(ha)004:2426: ye shes sgyu ma rnam par rol ba'i sku //'phags rje sprul pa mang po 'byung pa'i gnas //
NK029(ha)004:2427: thabs dang shes rab che la mnga' mnyes pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:2428: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs pa bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:2429: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan /
NK029(ha)004:2430: mah+aa ka ru ni ka tri sha ho /
NK029(ha)004:2435: a gad dza ya h+aum dza /
NK029(ha)004:2436: gsum pa bstan par bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:2437: h+aum bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)004:2438: thugs rje chen po byon pa legs //
NK029(ha)004:2439: bdag cag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK029(ha)004:2440: dgyes shing bstan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:2445: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi bzhi pa mchod pa 'bul ba'i cho 'phrul la bzhi ste /
NK029(ha)004:2451: phyog bcu dus bzhi sogs pa yi //
NK029(ha)004:2452: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK029(ha)004:2454: snang stong thig le kun rdzob ho //
NK029(ha)004:2455: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK029(ha)004:2456: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK029(ha)004:2457: rdo rje sgra can mtha' yas pa //
NK029(ha)004:2458: rdo rje rgyal po dkyil 'khor che //
NK029(ha)004:2459: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa chee //
NK029(ha)004:2460: yon tan 'phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK029(ha)004:2461: ye nas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang //'dus pa'i rdzogs chen thig le che //
NK029(ha)004:2462: mi 'khrug mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings /
NK029(ha)004:2463: mtha' yas kun tu sna tshogs 'phros //
NK029(ha)004:2464: mtha' yas kun tu lhun gyis thim //
NK029(ha)004:2465: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen ho //
NK029(ha)004:2466: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten brdul snyed du //
NK029(ha)004:2467: rgyal ba'i don rnams brdul bran rnyed //
NK029(ha)004:2468: sprul pa'i brdul bran bsam yas kyi //
NK029(ha)004:2469: skad cig yud la lhun gyi grub //
NK029(ha)004:2471: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK029(ha)004:2472: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK029(ha)004:2473: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK029(ha)004:2474: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le ho //
NK029(ha)004:2475: gnyis pa mchod pa la dgu ste //
NK029(ha)004:2476: kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:2478: mchod pa gar tshogs kyi mchod pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:2481: smad du byung pa bdud rtsi'i mchod pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:2484: dang po kun bzang kyi mchod pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:2485: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)004:2486: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK029(ha)004:2487: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kyis //
NK029(ha)004:2488: spyod pa rgya mtsho smad byung kun //
NK029(ha)004:2489: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK029(ha)004:2490: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu khe b+h+ya sarba tad kham ang+gu te /
NK029(ha)004:2491: s+pha ra na ham mam ga ga na kham s+w+aah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:2493: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni /
NK029(ha)004:2494: sems kyi yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK029(ha)004:2495: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas zhing //
NK029(ha)004:2496: gnyen 'jam reg na bde ba yi //
NK029(ha)004:2497: sna tshogs rin po che yi gzhi //
NK029(ha)004:2498: mdzes par bris shing spras pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:2500: dbyibs legs rdzing bu bro mchog gsil //
NK029(ha)004:2501: rin chen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK029(ha)004:2502: brgyan dang dpag bsam 'byon pa'i tshul //
NK029(ha)004:2503: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK029(ha)004:2504: bla res rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK029(ha)004:2505: do shal dpung brgyan sen mo do //
NK029(ha)004:2506: bza' dang btung ba'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK029(ha)004:2507: rang la mdzes par brgyan pa yis //
NK029(ha)004:2508: lha dang lha mo'i brdul brnyed kyis //
NK029(ha)004:2509: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa ni //
NK029(ha)004:2510: bro gar la sogs bsam yas kyis //
NK029(ha)004:2511: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK029(ha)004:2513: phyag rgya gar tshogs kyi mchod pa 'di //
NK029(ha)004:2514: sgyu 'phrul dra ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:2515: dbang po yul du gang bsgyur ba //
NK029(ha)004:2516: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:2517: mnyam pa'i ngang nyid stongs gsal nas //
NK029(ha)004:2518: thams cad byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK029(ha)004:2519: bskyed can 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK029(ha)004:2520: thabs dang shes rab thams cad kun //
NK029(ha)004:2522: bsgul skyod thams cad phyag rgya yin //'di ni spyi rgya chen po ste //
NK029(ha)004:2523: bla med chen pos 'di skad gsungs //
NK029(ha)004:2524: gsang ba de nyid nges pa yis //
NK029(ha)004:2526: mi skyod nyi ma'i dkyil yi ge /
NK029(ha)004:2527: rin chen zla ba'i dkyil yi ge /
NK029(ha)004:2528: lnga gnyis zung du 'phros pa las //
NK029(ha)004:2529: sbyor bas phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK029(ha)004:2530: dang mum gnyis rtse sbyar te //'bru brgyad bsnol nas rtse sprad de //
NK029(ha)004:2531: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK029(ha)004:2532: bde ba chen po sbyin pa'i rgya //'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs khar bkan //
NK029(ha)004:2533: h'u sgreng rtse mor rdo rje 'bar //
NK029(ha)004:2534: zla btul 'brug sgras dril gsil zhing //'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la rten //
NK029(ha)004:2535: badz+ra d+h+rig /'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs khar bkan //
NK029(ha)004:2536: mum sgrengs rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK029(ha)004:2537: nyi ma 'bru lnga las la mkhril //
NK029(ha)004:2538: bsdud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi lta //
NK029(ha)004:2540: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs khar bkan //
NK029(ha)004:2542: zla btul 'brug sgras dril bsil zhing //'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten //
NK029(ha)004:2543: dzi na dzig /'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs khar bkan //
NK029(ha)004:2544: lam sgreng rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK029(ha)004:2546: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi lta /
NK029(ha)004:2547: lam te sha ra te 'bru bzhi sbas //
NK029(ha)004:2548: swo rtse 'bar ba rin po che //
NK029(ha)004:2549: zla btul 'khril ba'i tshul gyi swa rat+na d+h+rika /'bru
NK029(ha)004:2550: bzhi mam sgring nyi ma 'bru lnga btud de mam
NK029(ha)004:2552: 'bru bzhi sgreng rtse mor pad+ma zla btul 'khril ba'i a ro lika /'bru bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:2553: pyam sgreng rtse mor dril gsil nas //
NK029(ha)004:2554: nyi ma 'bru lnga btud de pyam ga ra ti /
NK029(ha)004:2555: 'bru ham sgreng rtse mor ral gri 'bar /
NK029(ha)004:2556: zla btul 'khril ha pradz+nya d+h+rika /'bru bzhi sbas nas
NK029(ha)004:2557: t+r+aam sgreng rtse mor dril bsil 'bar //nyi ma 'bru
NK029(ha)004:2558: lnga btud de t+r+aam badz+ra ra ti /
NK029(ha)004:2559: thugs khar rin chen myu gu 'dzin //
NK029(ha)004:2560: rin chen dril bsil chos la brten //'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi lta ba ni //
NK029(ha)004:2561: sa yi snying po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK029(ha)004:2563: rdo rje rin chen khur tshur cang //
NK029(ha)004:2564: sku yi thad khar gzung ba ni //'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis 'dud pa ni //
NK029(ha)004:2565: sgeg mo'i phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK029(ha)004:2566: h+aum la s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK029(ha)004:2567: rdo rje ral gri thugs kha nas //
NK029(ha)004:2568: rin chen dril bsil chos la brten //'dzum pa'i nam mkha'i snying po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK029(ha)004:2570: rdo rje rin chen rna ltag bzhag /
NK029(ha)004:2571: rin chen 'phreng ba gzung pa ru //'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis 'phreng ba'i phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK029(ha)004:2572: tram ma le sa ma ya /
NK029(ha)004:2573: rdo rje pad+ma thugs ka nas //
NK029(ha)004:2574: rin chen dril bsil chos la 'dzum pa'i spyan ras gzigs kyi hrihha h+aum pad+ma /
NK029(ha)004:2575: rin chen pi wam 'dzin par bya //
NK029(ha)004:2576: rdo rje len par byas nas ni //'dzum pa'i dbyangs kyi hrihgi rti ra ga ya ham /
NK029(ha)004:2578: rin chen dril bsil chos 'dzum pa'i phyag na rdo
NK029(ha)004:2579: rje'i phyag rgya dz+him ku ru pa na hrih rin
NK029(ha)004:2580: chen gar thabs bskor na ni //
NK029(ha)004:2581: rdo rje thal mo las la 'khril //'dzum pa'i gar gyi phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK029(ha)004:2582: a nirti ra ga ya mi //
NK029(ha)004:2583: rdo rje klu shing thugs kha nas //
NK029(ha)004:2584: rin chen dril 'dzum pa'i byams pa mee tri'i phyag rgya yin //
NK029(ha)004:2586: rin chen gdugs spos thugs kha nas //
NK029(ha)004:2587: rdo rje las la rab tu 'khril //'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi gdug spos phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK029(ha)004:2588: dza d+hup+pe pra be sha ya /
NK029(ha)004:2589: rdo rje po ti thugs ka nas //
NK029(ha)004:2590: rin chen dril gsil 'dzum pa'i sgrib pa rnam sel phyag rgya yin //
NK029(ha)004:2591: th+l+ham ni pa ram sa ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:2592: rdo rje rin chen rnam ltag du //
NK029(ha)004:2593: me tog snod bcas 'dzin pa la //'dzum pa'i me
NK029(ha)004:2594: tog phyag rgya yin par h+aum push+pe a be sha
NK029(ha)004:2595: ya / rdo rje nyi ma thugs ka nas //
NK029(ha)004:2596: rin chen dril gsil 'dzum pa'i kun tu bzang po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK029(ha)004:2597: h+aum swa ra ts+aa ya swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:2598: rin chen mar me thugs ka na //
NK029(ha)004:2599: rdo rje sems dpa' las la 'khril //'dzum pa'i mar
NK029(ha)004:2600: me'i phyag rgya yin par pam ti bam su ki
NK029(ha)004:2601: ni swah+aa // rdo rje u pal thugs ka na //
NK029(ha)004:2602: rin chen dril gsil 'dzum pa'i 'jam dpal gyis ni phyag rgya yin //
NK029(ha)004:2603: mum sh+ri ra ga ya swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:2604: rin chen dbyug pa thugs ka na //
NK029(ha)004:2605: rdo rje dbyug par byed pa ni //'dzum pa'i dri'i phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK029(ha)004:2607: rni g+ho gdengs pa gshed po ste //
NK029(ha)004:2609: 'dzub gnyis lkug la lcags kyu'i rgya /
NK029(ha)004:2610: badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2611: rdo rje gnon pa stobs chen rgya /
NK029(ha)004:2613: 'dzub rtse gnyis sprad bzhag pa'i rgya //
NK029(ha)004:2614: rat+na thod sbrul gnon pa rta mgrin rgya //
NK029(ha)004:2617: pad+ma d+ha ra rgya gram gnon pa 'khyil ba'i rgya //
NK029(ha)004:2620: karma d+ha ra pi wam len pa lha'i rgya //
NK029(ha)004:2624: lha min phyag rgya go cha yin //
NK029(ha)004:2626: chos kyi dkyil 'khor byol song rgya //
NK029(ha)004:2628: za ma tog ni yi dwags rgya //
NK029(ha)004:2630: me chu gnyis ni dmyal ba'i rgya //
NK029(ha)004:2632: yab kyi spyi rgya kun bzang gi /
NK029(ha)004:2633: h+aum h+aum h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2634: yum gyi spyi rgya bzang mor bshad //
NK029(ha)004:2635: a a a badz+ra pa tra sa man ta /
NK029(ha)004:2636: yang na kun bzang yab yum gyi //
NK029(ha)004:2637: rdo rje thal mo nyid du bshad //
NK029(ha)004:2639: rin chen pad+ma dkyil 'jam 'di //'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi 'bul lags kyi //
NK029(ha)004:2640: dgyes par rdo rje gsor mdzod nas //
NK029(ha)004:2641: byang chub sems sprin dbab du gsol /
NK029(ha)004:2642: rdo rje gsor ba'i dga' chags 'di //'jam zhing mkhyil ba'i gnas su rol //
NK029(ha)004:2644: rdo rje 'dzin mar gdan la byung //
NK029(ha)004:2645: shes rab dbyings ma yum gyi gzhal yas su //
NK029(ha)004:2646: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus chags bkod de //
NK029(ha)004:2647: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i sbyor mchod kyis //
NK029(ha)004:2648: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor tshogs la mchod pa 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:2652: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs bsgom bsgral //
NK029(ha)004:2653: de nas gnyis med blo yi ni //
NK029(ha)004:2654: blo ngan 'jigs rten snying re rje //
NK029(ha)004:2655: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK029(ha)004:2656: zhi gyur chags dang chags bral rnams //
NK029(ha)004:2657: nyi zla'i dkyil du mkhas pas bzhag /
NK029(ha)004:2658: ngar rgyal lag gi 'du byed bsgom //
NK029(ha)004:2659: h+aum du gyur pas rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)004:2660: dbyings su thim nas phyag rgyar 'bar //
NK029(ha)004:2662: gtsug du rnam par rgyal ba bsgom //
NK029(ha)004:2663: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar ba'i thabs //
NK029(ha)004:2664: ye nas bskyed byed de bzhin nyid //
NK029(ha)004:2665: sbyor bsgrol bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK029(ha)004:2666: de la byas pa brdul tsam med //
NK029(ha)004:2668: ho rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NK029(ha)004:2669: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK029(ha)004:2670: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK029(ha)004:2671: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK029(ha)004:2672: rgyud lnga'i sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK029(ha)004:2673: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK029(ha)004:2674: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK029(ha)004:2675: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs can dang //
NK029(ha)004:2676: khro bo rgyal po mtha' yas dang //
NK029(ha)004:2677: ma mo mkha' 'gro tshogs chen dang //
NK029(ha)004:2678: lha dang lha min gsang ba'i mchog /
NK029(ha)004:2679: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i mchog /'di ni sngon gyi dam tshig go /
NK029(ha)004:2680: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK029(ha)004:2681: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid 'di //
NK029(ha)004:2682: bdag chags dad pas 'bul lags na //
NK029(ha)004:2683: bzhes de kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK029(ha)004:2684: phul ba'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)004:2685: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa argam pra ti tsa ho /
NK029(ha)004:2686: ho rgyal ba rgya mtsho ye shes kyi /
NK029(ha)004:2687: srid pa'i sdug bsngal zhi mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)004:2688: bde chen kun bzang yab yum la //
NK029(ha)004:2689: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:2691: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba lnga //
NK029(ha)004:2692: ye shes dbyings su rnam dag pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:2693: rigs lnga bde chen yab yum la //
NK029(ha)004:2694: dam tshig mchog gi mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:2696: rnam shes tshogs dang spyod yul rnams //
NK029(ha)004:2697: byang chub sems su rnam dag pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:2698: sems dpa' lcam bral tshogs rnams la //
NK029(ha)004:2699: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa na ma /
NK029(ha)004:2700: thugs rje chen po 'i byin brlabs kyis //'gro drug dbyings su sbyangs mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)004:2701: sprul pa thub pa drug rnams la //
NK029(ha)004:2702: dam tshig mchog gi mo na ma /
NK029(ha)004:2703: phyi nang bdud tshogs thams cad 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:2704: gnas yul ro langs rdo rje bcings sdom 'bebs //
NK029(ha)004:2705: sprul pa sgo skyong khro rgyal yab yum la //
NK029(ha)004:2706: dam tshig mchog gi na ma /
NK029(ha)004:2707: tshe rab sngon nas las kyi 'phro mthun pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:2708: mched dang lcam bral karma ging la sogs //
NK029(ha)004:2709: rdo rje lcam dral ma lus tshogs rnams la //
NK029(ha)004:2710: dam tshig mchog gi na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta argam pra ti dza ho //
NK029(ha)004:2711: smad 'byung tshogs kyis gtor mas mchod pa ni //
NK029(ha)004:2712: h+aum gzugs ni lag gnyis me long 'dzin //
NK029(ha)004:2713: gzugs mdzes spyod pas phyogs ba cur g.yos //
NK029(ha)004:2714: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK029(ha)004:2715: gzugs kyi lha mo spyan la thim //
NK029(ha)004:2717: sgra ni lag gnyis pi wam brdeb //
NK029(ha)004:2718: bde ba'i sgra snyan phyogs bcur bsgrog /
NK029(ha)004:2720: sgra'i lha mo snyan la thim //
NK029(ha)004:2722: dri ni lag gnyis spos bsnams ste //
NK029(ha)004:2723: spos kyi sprin lding gdug pa 'phro //
NK029(ha)004:2724: kun tu tshim byed bro bsrungs thim //
NK029(ha)004:2725: dri yi lha mo shangs la thim //
NK029(ha)004:2727: ro ni lag gnyis snod bsnams ste //
NK029(ha)004:2728: bcud ldan ro mchog lnga brgyar ldan //
NK029(ha)004:2729: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK029(ha)004:2730: ro'i lha mo ljags la thim //
NK029(ha)004:2732: reg ni rdo rje yongs 'khyud ma //
NK029(ha)004:2733: gnyen 'jam reg na bde ba yi //
NK029(ha)004:2734: gzugs mdzes spyod pa phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK029(ha)004:2735: reg gi lha mo sku la 'khril //
NK029(ha)004:2737: h+aum chos ni 'dul byas 'dus ma byas //
NK029(ha)004:2738: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i sku //
NK029(ha)004:2739: shin tu sgeg pa'i gzi brjid 'bar //
NK029(ha)004:2740: chos kyi lha mo thugs khar thim //
NK029(ha)004:2741: d+harma d+hartu badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:2743: h+aum bza' dang bca' dang btung dang sgo //
NK029(ha)004:2744: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK029(ha)004:2746: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i sngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:2748: bro gar phyag rgya 'phro 'du yis //'dzum ma nam mkhar 'gro bar 'gyur //
NK029(ha)004:2749: glu tshig sgra'i phyag rgya yis //
NK029(ha)004:2750: chos kyi dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK029(ha)004:2751: brgyan dang bgo ba'i phyag rgya yis //'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med 'gyur //
NK029(ha)004:2752: bza' dang btung ba'i phyag rgya yis //
NK029(ha)004:2753: yid bzhin sku dang bdud rtsir 'grub //
NK029(ha)004:2754: a li ka li'i phyag rgya yis //
NK029(ha)004:2756: spyi don gsum pa bstod pa ni //
NK029(ha)004:2757: zhi ba'i glu drug nyid dam /
NK029(ha)004:2758: thabs kyi zhags pa nas 'byung ba'i glu brgyad kyis bstod de /
NK029(ha)004:2760: rgyal ba gang bzhugs 'khor dang bcas //
NK029(ha)004:2761: bla med lha dang lha mo'i tshogs //
NK029(ha)004:2762: grub pa'i byin brlabs bsam mi khyab //
NK029(ha)004:2763: sems dpa' bcu drug rigs kyi gtso //
NK029(ha)004:2764: sems ma bcu drug rigs kyi yum //
NK029(ha)004:2765: mthu chen khro bo khro mo dang //
NK029(ha)004:2766: pho nya 'jig rten skyong bar ldan //
NK029(ha)004:2767: sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni //'jig rten thams cad ma lus kun //
NK029(ha)004:2768: rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyor bas na //
NK029(ha)004:2769: phyag rgya chen po bdag sbyor cig /
NK029(ha)004:2770: dpa' bo chen po mthu ldan rnams //
NK029(ha)004:2771: thugs rje chen po'i byin brlabs kyis //
NK029(ha)004:2772: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa rnams //'grub par byin gyis brlabs du gsol //
NK029(ha)004:2773: khams gsum zhing du sbyor la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)004:2774: dmigs med chos kyi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)004:2775: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)004:2776: cir yang sprul pa'i sku la de nas yi dam kun la kha h+ai brjod //
NK029(ha)004:2781: phyag 'tshal mchod bstod la sogs pas gzhung bsrang /
NK029(ha)004:2782: de nas ma tshang ba tshang ba kha bskang la /
NK029(ha)004:2784: yi ge brgya pa rnams brjod /
NK029(ha)004:2785: de nas rgyu 'phrul dbang rgyud kyi gsol 'debs byed pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2786: de nas bsnyen pa byed pa ni gnyiis te /
NK029(ha)004:2787: lha tog gi bsnyen pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:2792: rtog tshogs gang dang gang yin pa de lha de dang der gyur bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:2793: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid ces sogs dang /
NK029(ha)004:2795: mum da du shwa ri sogs brjod /
NK029(ha)004:2797: mnyam rdzogs dang mnyam rdzogs chen po'o //
NK029(ha)004:2798: dang po ni dkyil 'khor mi bsdu bar rang rdo
NK029(ha)004:2799: rje sems dpa' yab yum du gsal ba'i thugs khar
NK029(ha)004:2800: sngar 'khor bkod / de nas sngar kyi 'phreng ba
NK029(ha)004:2801: rang gi shang gong g.yas su phyung nas yum gyi
NK029(ha)004:2802: g.yon du rgyud bsgril ma g.yon du 'khor /
NK029(ha)004:2803: yang yum gyis g.yas nas rang gi g.yon du zhugs ste snying khar thim /
NK029(ha)004:2804: bsgril mar g.yas su 'khor bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:2805: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika mum da ru shwa ri brjod /
NK029(ha)004:2806: de bzhin du dmigs pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:2808: gnyis pa mnyam rdzogs chen po ni /
NK029(ha)004:2809: lha tshogs kun rang yab yum du bsdu la /
NK029(ha)004:2810: lha tshogs spyi'i bsnyen pa rang yab yum gyis byas ste /
NK029(ha)004:2814: nang mchod sman rag gtor gsum /
NK029(ha)004:2818: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi bdag ye shes rgya mtsho sogs kyis bstod /
NK029(ha)004:2819: de nas dam blangs pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:2820: rdo rje gcig pa'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK029(ha)004:2821: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK029(ha)004:2822: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:2823: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas rnams //'gro la phan phyir don du spyad //
NK029(ha)004:2824: byang chub spyod mchog dam pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:2825: sku gsung thug kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK029(ha)004:2826: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong na //
NK029(ha)004:2827: rdo rje rgyal pos byin brlabs cig /
NK029(ha)004:2830: bo d+hi tsit+ta sa ma ya h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2832: zhes gnas gsum du gtug go /
NK029(ha)004:2834: dang po byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:2835: dza gad dang mam sa gtso bor gyur pa'i tshogs
NK029(ha)004:2836: kyi yo byad rnams dkyil 'khor dang nya bar bshams
NK029(ha)004:2837: la / mah+aa kro d+hi shwa ri sogs kyis bsangs /
NK029(ha)004:2838: ram yam kham gyi bsreg sogs bya /
NK029(ha)004:2840: zhal zas kyi snod du nyi ma la /
NK029(ha)004:2841: +aah h+aum tram kham 'od du zhu ba las byung
NK029(ha)004:2842: ba'i bza' btung gi dngos po ye shes lnga'i rang
NK029(ha)004:2843: bzhin gyi bdud rtsi ro brgya dang /
NK029(ha)004:2844: 'dod yon gyi rnam pa ma tshang ba med pa /
NK029(ha)004:2845: so so'i lha mo rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang bcas pa'i sprin 'phro bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:2846: yi ge gsum lan gsum du brjod pas byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)004:2847: gnyis pa tshogs phul spyan drangs pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:2848: bsod nams ye shes yongs rdzogs shing //
NK029(ha)004:2849: ma rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK029(ha)004:2850: ye shes zhi khro 'khor lo'i tshul //
NK029(ha)004:2851: tshogs mchog dkyil 'khor gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:2852: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' nyid //
NK029(ha)004:2853: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo dang //'khor gyi khro bo sems dpar bcas //
NK029(ha)004:2854: sgo ba bzhi sogs gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:2855: e h+ya hi sogs kyi tshogs zhing dpag tu med
NK029(ha)004:2856: pa zhig tshogs su sad par byas la thugs rje'i
NK029(ha)004:2857: lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK029(ha)004:2865: h+aum he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang /
NK029(ha)004:2866: dur drod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK029(ha)004:2868: dur drod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK029(ha)004:2869: zhing chen gsar rnying gdan du gting //
NK029(ha)004:2870: dmar gyi argam rgya mtshor dkyil //
NK029(ha)004:2871: ma lus gshegs nas bsnams su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:2872: ru lu ru lu ru lu h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2873: e h+ya hi a na ya dza h+aum bam hoh
NK029(ha)004:2874: yis khro tshogs dpag tu med pa spyan drangs la
NK029(ha)004:2875: dgu sogs bya / gsum pa mchod pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:2876: h+aum spos kyi sprin lding gdug pa mo sogs dang /
NK029(ha)004:2877: sh+ri badz+ra r+aa ga d+hu pa d+hu sogs bzhi bsnol dang /
NK029(ha)004:2878: h+aum rdo rje sgeg mo rdo rje can //
NK029(ha)004:2879: sems dpa' sngon po'i ye shes 'bebs //
NK029(ha)004:2880: me long lta bu'i ye shes las //
NK029(ha)004:2882: sh+ri badz+ra ra ga la s+ye h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2883: yid bzhin rin chen 'od 'bar ma //'jam dpal sngon po'i dngos grub 'dzin //
NK029(ha)004:2884: mnyam pa nyid kyi badz+ra ma l+ye'i badz+ra ma le'i ma le tram /
NK029(ha)004:2885: pad+ma dbyangs mkhan rma bya'i mgrin //
NK029(ha)004:2886: spyan ras gzigs kyi dngos grub 'dzin //
NK029(ha)004:2887: so sor rtog pa'i badz+ra g+hirti'i g+hirti hri /
NK029(ha)004:2888: gar mkhan 'gying bag gzi ldan ma //
NK029(ha)004:2890: bya ba nan tan ye shes badz+ra n+rirti n+rirta a /
NK029(ha)004:2891: bzhi pa tshogs mchod 'bul ba ni //
NK029(ha)004:2896: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa ni //
NK029(ha)004:2897: ye shes lnga'i 'od zer rnam par 'phros //'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan ste //
NK029(ha)004:2898: thugs dam bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:2899: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya chos //'dod yon lha mo nam mkha' gang //
NK029(ha)004:2901: spyan sogs bde bas tshim gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:2903: u pa b+h+yo ka ma ha hri pra ti ts+tsha ho /
NK029(ha)004:2906: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas //
NK029(ha)004:2907: rtsa ba yan lag bcas pa'i dam tshig la //
NK029(ha)004:2908: sems can dbang gi nor 'khrul ci mchis pa //
NK029(ha)004:2909: mi 'chab 'gyod pa'i sems kyi mthol lo bshags //
NK029(ha)004:2910: badz+ra sat+wa sogs kyi yi ge brgya pa brjod /
NK029(ha)004:2912: las kyi lam thod pa mtshan ngan du ling ga bcas la /
NK029(ha)004:2913: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:2914: bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa' dang zhi ba la gdug pa can bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)004:2916: na mo dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)004:2917: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:2918: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bka' chos can sgyu
NK029(ha)004:2919: 'bras bslu ba med pa' zhi khro sgyu 'phrul rnam
NK029(ha)004:2920: par rol ba'i lha tshogs rnams kyis sprul pa yang
NK029(ha)004:2921: srid bka' nyan dang bcas pa rnams kyis rigs sngags
NK029(ha)004:2922: 'chang rnams kyi lhag pa'i bsam pa rnam par dag
NK029(ha)004:2924: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK029(ha)004:2925: ma rung ba'i sems can bsgral ba'i zhing bcur rtogs pa thams cad /
NK029(ha)004:2926: mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la skad cig tsam gyis mchis par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:2930: tri badz+ra a ng+gu sha dza /
NK029(ha)004:2931: zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas bskug la /
NK029(ha)004:2932: dza h+aum bam ho yis dgug stim zhing myos par
NK029(ha)004:2933: byas ste gdug pa'i snying khar dwangs ma ye shes
NK029(ha)004:2934: kyi a dkar po dang bcas pa /
NK029(ha)004:2935: bdag dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kyi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK029(ha)004:2937: bzas pa po'i snying kha'i sgo phye /
NK029(ha)004:2939: ye shes lngar 'bab dug lnga ye shes gnas gyur /
NK029(ha)004:2940: dngas ma lnga sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i 'khor lor spar ste sangs rgyas par gyur /
NK029(ha)004:2942: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma r+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tana /
NK029(ha)004:2943: sa ma ya mu tra mat+tam kha kha /
NK029(ha)004:2945: hri da ya pi pa h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:2946: snying ma rang snang sgyu 'phrul gyi 'khor lo khro
NK029(ha)004:2947: tshogs su 'bar bas rdo rje bza' ba'i dam tshig
NK029(ha)004:2949: h+aum nga ni za byed chen po ste /
NK029(ha)004:2950: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:2951: gdul da ka' ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)004:2952: sha rus la sogs za bar bya /
NK029(ha)004:2954: sarba dush+tana ma ra ya h+aum phata kyis /
NK029(ha)004:2955: ling ka'i gnas lngar phur bu btab pas bsad /
NK029(ha)004:2957: dum bur gtubs khog pa phral ste /
NK029(ha)004:2960: sh+ri badz+ra he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK029(ha)004:2964: ma h+aa ba su ta ma h+aa pan tsa a
NK029(ha)004:2965: mri ta kha kha kha le le le h+aum b+h+yo
NK029(ha)004:2967: h+aum bgegs dang dpa' ba 'jigs su rung pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:2968: rgod dang bshed dang 'jigs par ston pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:2969: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba la sogs pas //
NK029(ha)004:2970: sku yi dngos po shin tu bsgyur ba yin //
NK029(ha)004:2971: gar yang bsgrub po rnam 'byor las //
NK029(ha)004:2972: gar gyis dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK029(ha)004:2973: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK029(ha)004:2974: mam sa la sogs ro mchog bsil //
NK029(ha)004:2975: me tog la sogs tsan dan dri //
NK029(ha)004:2976: bzang dgu dbul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:2977: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog /
NK029(ha)004:2978: byin gyis barlobasa shig rnam 'byor las //
NK029(ha)004:2979: bsgrub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la /
NK029(ha)004:2980: h+aum dang phata kyi ldan par mdzod /
NK029(ha)004:2981: ces pas bsgral thal sbyor ba'i dam tshig chen por bsgrubs pas lha thams cad tshim par byas la /
NK029(ha)004:2982: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika kyis rdor sems zhi bar nga rgyal 'phos ste /
NK029(ha)004:2984: h+aum rnam dag sgrib spangs srid gsum skyon bral zhing /
NK029(ha)004:2985: ston ka'i zla gsal dri med zhal mnga' ba //
NK029(ha)004:2986: bcom ldan bde gshegs rdo rje dbyings kyi 'khor //
NK029(ha)004:2987: dus gsum bde gshegs thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK029(ha)004:2988: shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum rnams dang //
NK029(ha)004:2989: phyag gnyan khro gtum rngam pa'i tshogs la sogs //
NK029(ha)004:2990: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyi zhing rab rdzogs //
NK029(ha)004:2991: dgyes par rol cig mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK029(ha)004:2992: zhes ste a la la yis dgyes par mdzod /
NK029(ha)004:2993: badz+ra e sa h+aum se sa h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2995: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:2998: zhes pas 'khor gsum bde ba chen por ro mnyam pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:2999: tshogs phud bzhi pa phud lhag bsre ba'i chas su bzhag /
NK029(ha)004:3000: lnga pa tshogs la rol ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:3001: dbang gi mthar mdzad pa phyag len yin no //
NK029(ha)004:3002: de nas rjes chog bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:3006: dang po lhag ma bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:3007: bdag gi thugs kha nas 'dod pa'i rgyal po phyung ste /
NK029(ha)004:3008: mkha' 'gro ma sum cu rtsa drug rang dbang med pa spyan 'dren nas /
NK029(ha)004:3009: bcom ldan 'das rigs lnga'i 'khor brgyad brgyad zur bzhi bzhir bzhugs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:3024: sarba nan badz+ra ta ki hri da ya h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:3026: so so'i snying po phul nas /
NK029(ha)004:3027: zhing tshal pa'i gdan la bzhugs te /
NK029(ha)004:3032: mtshams rnams kyang de ltar bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:3033: kun kyang lag na gri dang thod pa thogs pa /
NK029(ha)004:3034: rus pa'i brgyan gyis lhub pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:3036: bdag gi ljags steng na h+r+aih las bdud rtsi'i chu
NK029(ha)004:3037: rgyun babs pas lha 'gron rnams ljags steng du thim
NK029(ha)004:3039: gtor ma bdud rtsi'i dgongs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:3040: yang gtor ma bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor gyur par gsal bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:3041: h+aum sarba badz+ra t+aa ka t+aa ki ni /
NK029(ha)004:3042: pra ti dza e mam b+ha ling ta h+aum phata kha hi /
NK029(ha)004:3043: sarba bud+ha t+aa ka ta ki ni pra ti dza e mam b+ha lim ta phata kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)004:3045: tram sarba rat+na t+aa ka t+aa ki ni pra ti
NK029(ha)004:3046: dza e mam b+ha lim ta tram phata kha hi
NK029(ha)004:3048: hrihsarba pad+ma t+aa ka t+aa ki ni pra ti dza he mam b+ha ling ta hrihphata kha hi /
NK029(ha)004:3050: ha sarba karma t+aa ki t+aa ki ni pra ti
NK029(ha)004:3051: dza e mam b+ha lim ta ha phata kha hi
NK029(ha)004:3052: / byang gi dagu'o //'di rnams rgyas par ni so so'i grangs tshad du bazla'o //
NK029(ha)004:3053: gtor ma dug gsum gyi rgya mtsho sha khrag rus
NK029(ha)004:3054: par bsgom nas mkha' 'gro ma rnams la btab pa
NK029(ha)004:3055: ni / dug gsum gyi dgongs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:3056: de nas mkha' 'gro ma rnams cag ge nyan par bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:3057: rdo rje dril bu thogs la 'di skad do //
NK029(ha)004:3058: h+aum bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' la //
NK029(ha)004:3059: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyi bskor ba ni //
NK029(ha)004:3060: mngon par dag pa'i 'jig rten na //
NK029(ha)004:3061: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)004:3062: yi dwags stan la yang dag bzhugs //
NK029(ha)004:3063: dbang po 'jigs pa'i gzugs bzhin can //
NK029(ha)004:3064: skal ldan rang gi lag char ldan //
NK029(ha)004:3065: gdug pa'i sems kyi ma rig byed //
NK029(ha)004:3066: sha khrag dang ni rgyu ma dang //
NK029(ha)004:3067: rkang dang tshil bu za spyod rnams //
NK029(ha)004:3068: za bar byed cing 'dren par byed //
NK029(ha)004:3069: gsod par byed cing 'phrog par byed //
NK029(ha)004:3070: kun gyi rang gi dam tshig ldan //
NK029(ha)004:3071: shar gyi phyogs nas gshegs su gsol //'dir gshegs brgyan gyi gtor ma bzhes //
NK029(ha)004:3073: bdag gi bsam pa nye bar bsgrubs //
NK029(ha)004:3074: las bcol 'phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)004:3075: dpal dang ldan pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK029(ha)004:3076: rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)004:3077: gzi brjid che dang 'bar byed ma //'joms byed ma dang bong sna'i mgo /
NK029(ha)004:3078: kun kyang rang gi lho'i phyogs nas gshegs su gsol
NK029(ha)004:3079: //'dur gshegs brgyan gyi gtor ma bka'i pha 'bab 'di
NK029(ha)004:3080: bdag gi bsam pa las bcol bde ba can gyi
NK029(ha)004:3081: 'jig rten nas // rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)004:3082: chags chen ma dang chags bral ma //'khor lo ma dang rgyas 'debs ma //
NK029(ha)004:3083: kun kyang nub kyi phyogs nas gshegs bka'i gtor ma
NK029(ha)004:3084: bdag gi las bcol rnam par dag pa'i 'jig rten
NK029(ha)004:3085: nas // rdo rje nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)004:3086: sna tshogs lus dang bsrungs ba mo //
NK029(ha)004:3087: gnod sbyin mo dang yang dag 'phrog /
NK029(ha)004:3088: kun kyang byang gi phyogs nas 'dir gshegs bka'i gtor
NK029(ha)004:3089: ma bdag gi las sha chen spungs pa'i 'jig rten
NK029(ha)004:3090: nas // bya rog gdong gi mig 'phrul can //'jigs pa'i mig dang 'jigs pa'i gdong //
NK029(ha)004:3091: shar lho'i nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)004:3092: lag par gri dang khrag zhong thogs //
NK029(ha)004:3093: mchog tu sha dang khrag la dgyes //
NK029(ha)004:3094: kun kyang shar lho'i mtshams nas 'dir gshegs bka'i bdag
NK029(ha)004:3095: gi las bcol keng rus dpungs pa'i 'jig rten nas
NK029(ha)004:3097: khros pas khyi dang phag gi gdong /
NK029(ha)004:3098: lhun grub nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)004:3100: kun kyang lho nub nam mkhar 'dir gshegs bka' yi
NK029(ha)004:3101: bdag gi las bcol rak+ta khrag gi rba klong nas
NK029(ha)004:3102: / rnga mo bung bu'i gdong 'dzin ma //
NK029(ha)004:3103: khros pas ra dang byi la'i gdong //
NK029(ha)004:3104: nub byang nam mkhar 'gro ba rnams //
NK029(ha)004:3105: rgyu ma'i mgo nas za bar byed //
NK029(ha)004:3106: kun kyang nub byang 'tshams nas 'dir gshegs bka'i bdag las bcol thal chen spungs pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK029(ha)004:3107: keng rus dkar po 'dzin pa ste //
NK029(ha)004:3108: khros pas rus pa'i 'phreng ba klubs //
NK029(ha)004:3111: lce spyang gis ni 'khor gyis bskor //'jig rten drag po'i mche ba gtsigs //
NK029(ha)004:3112: kun kyang byang shar 'dir gshegs bka'i bdag gi las bcol dpa' ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yi //
NK029(ha)004:3113: dkyil 'khor de yi grwa bzhi nas //'jigs byed mkha' 'gro bzhi byung ba //
NK029(ha)004:3114: shar gyi phyogs nas byung ba ni //
NK029(ha)004:3115: rdo rje mkha' 'gro chen mo ste //
NK029(ha)004:3116: srin po bong sna gshegs su gsol //'jigs byed 'bum phrag bcu dang bcas //
NK029(ha)004:3117: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka'i bdag gi las bcol lho'i phyogs nas 'byung pa ni //
NK029(ha)004:3118: rin chen mkha' 'gro chen mo ste //
NK029(ha)004:3119: rdo rje dus mtshan gshegs su gsol //'jigs byed 'bum phrag lnga dang bcas //
NK029(ha)004:3120: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka'i las bcol nub kyi phyogs nas byung pa ni //
NK029(ha)004:3122: rdo rje dus kyi 'khor lo yang //'jigs byed bye ba 'bum dang bcas //
NK029(ha)004:3123: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka'i las bcol byang gi phyogs nas byung ba ni //
NK029(ha)004:3124: las kyi mkha' 'gro chen mo ste //
NK029(ha)004:3125: rdo rje lang ka mgrin bcu yang //
NK029(ha)004:3126: gnod sbyin bye ba gsum dang bcas //
NK029(ha)004:3127: byang gi phyogs nas gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:3128: kun kyang 'dir gshegs bka'i bdag gi las bcol mkha' 'gro pho mo khyed rnams kyang //
NK029(ha)004:3129: sngon tshe bcom ldan rigs lnga yis //
NK029(ha)004:3130: pho rnams btul ste gdan du byas //
NK029(ha)004:3131: mo rnams btul ste 'dza' mor bya //
NK029(ha)004:3132: sems dpa' dam tshig dgongs pa bzhin //
NK029(ha)004:3133: bdag kyang rgyal ba'i bstan bsrung na //
NK029(ha)004:3134: las bcol 'phrin las mdzad du gsol //
NK029(ha)004:3135: bar du gcod pa'i dgra bgegs rnams //
NK029(ha)004:3136: myur du bsgral la med par mdzod //
NK029(ha)004:3137: bdud 'dul mthu dang skal ldan tshe //
NK029(ha)004:3138: mdzod ldan nor dang 'khor rnams kyis //
NK029(ha)004:3139: dngos grub dam pa bdag la stsol //
NK029(ha)004:3140: de nas gtor ma nam mkha' mthong par phyir dpags la /
NK029(ha)004:3141: gangs ri'ii rgyud la yod pa'i brtan ma spyan 'dren pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:3142: h+aum dkyil 'khor de'i phyi rims nas /
NK029(ha)004:3143: gangs ri'i rgyud la gnas pa yi //
NK029(ha)004:3144: brtan ma'i tshogs kyi bskur ba ni //
NK029(ha)004:3145: lag tu rdo rje byin nas ming gis dbang bskur bas //
NK029(ha)004:3146: bod khams skyong ba ma mo'i tshogs //
NK029(ha)004:3147: bstan ma chen mo bcu gnyis kyang //
NK029(ha)004:3148: sngon gyi thugs dam bskong mdzod la //'dir gshegs bcol ba'i b+h+yo gung sngon mthon po'i yar stengs na //
NK029(ha)004:3149: nam mkha'i rgyal po rdo rje ting lo sman //
NK029(ha)004:3150: kha rag khyung btsun rdo rje dpal gyi yum //
NK029(ha)004:3151: mo btsun khu chos rdo rje g.yar mo gsil //
NK029(ha)004:3152: skong btsun de mo rdo rje bod khams skyong //
NK029(ha)004:3153: lho'i skyi mthing rdo rje g.ya' ma skyong //
NK029(ha)004:3154: byang gi rma ting rdo rje ting lo btsun //
NK029(ha)004:3155: btsan la rol pa'i rdo rje sman gcig ma //
NK029(ha)004:3156: gangs kyi yum chen rdo rje g.yu bun ma //
NK029(ha)004:3157: gdal la btsan mo rdo rje ye ge mchog /
NK029(ha)004:3158: skyi mthing gangs kyi rdo rje la rol sman //
NK029(ha)004:3159: yang 'brog gser thang rdo rje 'brog srin mo //
NK029(ha)004:3160: khrag mthung chen mo rdo rje sgyu dril ma //
NK029(ha)004:3161: mi g.yo brtan ma'i rdo rje sa 'dzin mo //
NK029(ha)004:3162: de ltar gangs ri'i rgyud la gnas pa yi //
NK029(ha)004:3163: bstan ma chen mo bcu gnyis rnams //
NK029(ha)004:3164: bdud rtsi sman gyis g.yab dor gnas //
NK029(ha)004:3166: bcol ba'i 'phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK029(ha)004:3167: bdag cag rnal 'byor 'dir 'dus dang //'khor du gtogs pa'i yon bdag gis //
NK029(ha)004:3168: rkyen la bab na rkyen bzlog cig /
NK029(ha)004:3169: sho la bab na sho gtor cig /
NK029(ha)004:3170: khram la bab na khram chog cig /
NK029(ha)004:3171: rims nad yam nad bcad pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:3172: ci la gyur pa'i nad rnams kun //
NK029(ha)004:3173: yud tsam gyis ni med par mdzod //
NK029(ha)004:3174: ma h+aa ma sa la kha hi /
NK029(ha)004:3182: de nas rting shag yig brgya dang bcas pa brjod //
NK029(ha)004:3183: bsngo ba smon lam gyis rgyas gdab //
NK029(ha)004:3184: phun sum pa'i bkra shis brjod //
NK029(ha)004:3185: de nas rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor bsdu'o //
NK029(ha)004:3186: slar rdo rje sems dpa'i skur skad cig gis bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:3189: spyod lam gyi bya ba rnams bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:3190: zhi ba'i sngon rtogs rdzogs so //
NK029(ha)004:3191: de ltar dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)004:3192: byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK029(ha)004:3193: mchod pa 'bul ba'i cho 'phrul dang gsum po 'di /
NK029(ha)004:3195: bum bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor drug dang /
NK029(ha)004:3196: mdun bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor drug po re la /
NK029(ha)004:3198: 'on kyang ma lcogs na gcig tu bsdus kyang grub po /
NK029(ha)004:3199: gnyis pa sngon 'gro rab gnas kyi rten rnams la byug pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:3200: sku gzugs pa'i rnam lnga dang /
NK029(ha)004:3201: til mar khu dang shing shun lngas phyis ste /
NK029(ha)004:3202: spos kyi dri zhim par byas la bzhag go /
NK029(ha)004:3203: dang po ba'i rnam lngas byug pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:3204: mkhar ba'i snod du ba'i rnam lnga bsres la dkyil
NK029(ha)004:3205: 'khor gyi lha bstan pa'i me long nang gi gzugs
NK029(ha)004:3206: brnyan la byug / sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha ni h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:3210: de nas u dum w+aa ra /
NK029(ha)004:3214: spar pa de lnga'i shun pa phye ma'i lde gus byugs /
NK029(ha)004:3216: de nas ras kyi phyi bzhin rat+na pra ban tsa ra ha s+w+aa h+aa bkru ba'o //
NK029(ha)004:3217: de nas dri lnga'i chus dri bskyed de /
NK029(ha)004:3219: a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ye sh+r+ai ye h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:3221: gu ru'i chas gos lnga ser por byas la /
NK029(ha)004:3222: spyi don gnyis pa ting nge 'dzin gyi lha bskyed pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:3223: thal mo khong stong du sbyar la /
NK029(ha)004:3224: mah+aa shu nya ta d+harma d+hartu swa b+ha wa +aat+ma ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)004:3226: rab tu gnas par 'os pa'i rten thams cad stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK029(ha)004:3227: de nas bdag gtso bor gsal ba'i thugs kha'i h+aum las /
NK029(ha)004:3228: 'byung pa lnga'i yi ge e yam mam sum lam ram byung nas 'byung rims bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:3229: b+h+rum las gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:3230: de nas bdag yab yum sbyor ba'i byang sems las /
NK029(ha)004:3231: lha so so'i sa bon brgyad dam /
NK029(ha)004:3233: de las lhag pa gang mos ston la /
NK029(ha)004:3234: 'od du zhu ba la phyag mtshan yig 'bru grangs dang mnyam pa /
NK029(ha)004:3236: zhi ba'i lha dkyil 'khor bsdus pa'am /
NK029(ha)004:3238: rgyas pa la sogs mngon rtogs bzhin gsal bar bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:3239: de nas dbang bskur ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:3240: ma h+aa shu nya ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:3241: chos dbyings ye shes kyi ngo bo mi bskyod pas dbang bskur zhing rdo rje spyi bor btugs /
NK029(ha)004:3242: ma h+aa a ta ri sha dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham //
NK029(ha)004:3243: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi ngo bo'i rnam par snang mdzad kyis dbang bskur zhing /
NK029(ha)004:3244: rdo rje dpral par gtug go /
NK029(ha)004:3245: rdo rje sna ltag g.yas su gtugs la /
NK029(ha)004:3246: mah+aa sa ma ta dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:3247: mnyam nyid ye shes kyi ngo bo rin chen 'byung ldan gyi dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)004:3248: rdo rje rtag par gtugs la /
NK029(ha)004:3249: mah+aa pra ta pra be sha na dz+nya na badz+ra swa b+ha wa a d+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:3250: sor rtogs ye shes kyi ngo bo snang ba mtha' yas kyi dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)004:3251: rdo rje rna ltag g.yon par gtugs la /
NK029(ha)004:3252: ma h+aa kri t+ya nya sh+tha na dz+nya na badz+ra swab+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:3253: bya grub ye shes kyi ngo bo don yod grub pas dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)004:3255: na mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang /
NK029(ha)004:3259: 'phrin las dang zhing khams zag pa med pa'i mi
NK029(ha)004:3260: zad pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden pa dang
NK029(ha)004:3261: / bden pa chen po'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK029(ha)004:3262: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)004:3263: rigs lnga ye shes lngas dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)004:3264: rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar lhun gyis grub pa'i don /
NK029(ha)004:3265: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3266: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)004:3267: srid pa gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3268: spyi bor rdo rje gtugs la /
NK029(ha)004:3269: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swab+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)004:3270: lha rnams kyi dbu'i nang du /
NK029(ha)004:3271: sku rdo rje sku mdog dkar po re res byin gyis rlabs /
NK029(ha)004:3272: rdo rje mgrin par gtugs la /
NK029(ha)004:3273: sarba ta th+aa ga ta w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)004:3275: gsung rdo rje sku mdog dmar po re res byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)004:3276: rdo rje thugs khar gtugs la /
NK029(ha)004:3277: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko&a ham /
NK029(ha)004:3278: thugs khar thugs rdo rje sku mdog sngon po re res byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)004:3279: rdo rje lte bar gtugs la /
NK029(ha)004:3280: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa a nu ra ga badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:3281: lha rnams kyi lte bar yon tan rdo rje sku mdog ser po re res byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)004:3282: rdo rje gsang gnas su gtugs la /
NK029(ha)004:3283: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa pu tsa badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:3284: lha rnams kyi gsang gnas su /
NK029(ha)004:3285: mchod pa'i rdo rje sku mdog ljang khu re res byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)004:3287: na mo phyogs bcu dus bcu bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad sku dang /
NK029(ha)004:3291: zhing khams zag pa med pa /
NK029(ha)004:3292: zad mi shes pa brgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:3293: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis brten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)004:3298: 'phrin las mi zad pa brgyan gyis 'khor lo lhun gyi grub pa'i don /
NK029(ha)004:3299: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3300: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)004:3301: srid pa gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3302: gsum pa ye shes pa spyan drangs zhing stim pa la snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:3303: h+aum dmigs med mkha' ltar dag cing khyab pa'i sku //
NK029(ha)004:3304: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK029(ha)004:3305: thugs rje'i ngang can chos sku dag pa las //
NK029(ha)004:3306: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:3307: badz+ra sa man dza h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:3309: ho yod med stong pa shin tu rnal 'byor mthus //
NK029(ha)004:3310: nam mkha' bzhin du dam tshig nye bar gshegs //
NK029(ha)004:3311: yeshesa rgya mtsho rnam par grol ba'i klong //
NK029(ha)004:3312: mi gnas mi dmigs nam mkha'i dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK029(ha)004:3313: tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs thams cad dbyings kyi lha //
NK029(ha)004:3314: longs spyod rdzogs mdzad rol pa chen po'i sku //
NK029(ha)004:3315: rdo rje sems dpa' bskal bzang dpal khyod bdag /
NK029(ha)004:3316: thabs kyi ma rmongs bde chen dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK029(ha)004:3317: ye shes sgyu ma rnam par rol pa'i sku //'phags rje sprul pa mang po 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK029(ha)004:3318: thabs dang shes rab che la mnga' mnyes pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:3319: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs par bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:3320: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa ka ru ni ka tri sha ya ho //
NK029(ha)004:3327: brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:3328: h+aum bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK029(ha)004:3329: thugs rje chen po byon pa legs //
NK029(ha)004:3330: bdag cag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK029(ha)004:3331: dgyes shing bstan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)004:3332: badz+ra sa ma ya dza h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:3335: 'gro mgon tshur gshegs gdan la bzhugs //
NK029(ha)004:3336: khyod kyi bsod nams stobs kyi gdan byung bas //
NK029(ha)004:3337: mi 'jigs stobs kyi glang po dang //
NK029(ha)004:3338: cang shes dang ni dbang gi rma bya dang //
NK029(ha)004:3339: thogs med nam mkha' lding gi khri bshams te //
NK029(ha)004:3340: nyi zla pad+ma rin chen gdan steng su //
NK029(ha)004:3341: stobs bcu rtsal mnga' 'gro ba'i mgon gyur bzhugs //
NK029(ha)004:3342: ma rig mun sel rin chen sgron me bzhugs //
NK029(ha)004:3343: bdud rigs stong mdzad thar pa'i lam ston bzhugs //'gro ba 'dren mdzad thugs rje'i lcags kyu bzhugs //
NK029(ha)004:3344: bcings pa grol mdzad byang chub lcam bral bzhugs //'gro drug sgrol mdzad sprul sku thub drug bzhugs /
NK029(ha)004:3345: bdud bzhi 'joms mdzad ta krid khro rgyal bzhugs //
NK029(ha)004:3346: bstan pa bsrungs mdzad chos skyong bsrungs ma bzhugs //
NK029(ha)004:3348: bzhi pa dbang po la sogs kyi skyon gsal ba ni /
