NK029(ha)004:3349: mig sman dang a mri tas byug pa'i gser gyi thur ma sor brgyad pa thog la /
NK029(ha)004:3350: spyan sngar rab rib rnam rtog skyon bsal ste //
NK029(ha)004:3351: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med mtshan nyid do //
NK029(ha)004:3352: srin zhu'i tshul gyi gser gyi thub ma 'di //
NK029(ha)004:3353: sna tshogs yangs pa'i spyan gyis dbye bgyis pas //
NK029(ha)004:3354: rang dang spyi yi mtshan nyid chos rnams la //
NK029(ha)004:3355: chos sku ji ltar gzigs cing mkhyen pa ltar //
NK029(ha)004:3356: sangs rgyas ye shes spyan gyi dngos grub ste //
NK029(ha)004:3357: bdag blo dmun long lta bu sel bar shog /
NK029(ha)004:3358: tsak+shu tsak+shu sa man ta tsak+shu b+hi shwa d+ha ni swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:3359: ces spyan dbye ba ltar byas ste //
NK029(ha)004:3362: na mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang /
NK029(ha)004:3366: 'phrin las zhing khams zag pa med pa zad mi
NK029(ha)004:3367: shes pa'i brgyan gyis 'khor lo'i bka' bden pa dang
NK029(ha)004:3368: / bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyi /
NK029(ha)004:3369: deng rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la gser gyi
NK029(ha)004:3370: thur mas spyan phyes pas ye shes kyi spyan phun
NK029(ha)004:3372: deng yon gyi bdag po che ge mo dang /
NK029(ha)004:3373: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)004:3374: srid pa gsum gyis sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3375: gser gyi snyan gzhar thogs la /
NK029(ha)004:3376: ma 'gags gsal ba'i skyon rnams rnam dag kyang //
NK029(ha)004:3377: sems can ma lus bag chags bsal slad du //
NK029(ha)004:3378: gser gyi spab gzhar snyan gsal tshul 'di yis //
NK029(ha)004:3379: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can thams cad kyis //
NK029(ha)004:3380: dus gsum rgyal bas legs par gsungs pa yis //
NK029(ha)004:3381: bstan pa'i theg pa phyi nang ma lus kun /
NK029(ha)004:3382: skye ba kun tu thob pa'i dngos grub stsol /
NK029(ha)004:3383: tib bya ka rata na ye yo swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:3384: snyan gsal bar ltar byas la /
NK029(ha)004:3385: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK029(ha)004:3386: de ring rab du gnas pa'i lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)004:3387: gser gyi snyan gzhar gyi snyan spab bsal nas /
NK029(ha)004:3388: lha'i snyan rnam par dag pa /
NK029(ha)004:3389: de ring yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3390: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)004:3391: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3392: gser gyi rmang rtse thogs pa /
NK029(ha)004:3393: shangs kyi rlung gis khams su skyod mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)004:3394: dbang gi mchog gi dri chab yul la rol //
NK029(ha)004:3395: thabs dang shes rab tshul gyi 'gro don mdzod //
NK029(ha)004:3396: nyon mongs skyon bral ye nas rnam dag la //
NK029(ha)004:3397: skur bsti ri mo gser gyi spar tsher gyis //
NK029(ha)004:3398: shangs kyi spu gsal rtogs pa'i dra ba bcom //
NK029(ha)004:3399: ye shes thog med rlung gi bka' bskyed nas //'og min bla med gnas su phyin par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3400: tib bya g+ha d+ha ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:3401: shangs kyi spu 'thog pa ltar byas la /
NK029(ha)004:3403: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)004:3404: gser gyi spar tsher gyi shangs kyi spu rtogs pas /
NK029(ha)004:3405: pha rol sems kyis rnam grangs shes pa'i don /
NK029(ha)004:3406: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3407: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)004:3408: srid pa gsum gyi bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3409: gser gyi ljags gzhar thogs la /
NK029(ha)004:3410: ljags kyi dbang po rnam dag nas //
NK029(ha)004:3411: ro rnams thams cad mkhyen pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)004:3412: sems can rnams gyi don slad du //
NK029(ha)004:3413: ljags kyi dri ma bsal bar bgyi //
NK029(ha)004:3415: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK029(ha)004:3416: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la //
NK029(ha)004:3417: gser gyi ljags gzhar gyis ljags bzhar bas /
NK029(ha)004:3418: gsung rab mos pa so sor 'chad pa'i 'bras bus /
NK029(ha)004:3419: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3420: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)004:3421: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3422: dngul gyi tshem shing thogs la //
NK029(ha)004:3423: dpal gyi 'gul nas tshangs pa'i ljags phyung bas /
NK029(ha)004:3424: cir yang 'gyur ba'i ljags kyis dbyibs bkram ste //
NK029(ha)004:3425: brgyad khri bzhi stong chos sgo ston mdzad pas //
NK029(ha)004:3426: tshems dkar bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rnam dag la //
NK029(ha)004:3427: rin chen mchog grub dngul gyi tshems shing gis //
NK029(ha)004:3428: bskur sti ri mo tshems kyi sgo gsal nas //
NK029(ha)004:3429: bdag cag gsung gi dngos grub thob gyur nas //'gro drug skad du dam chos ston par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3431: ces tshems kyi dri ma gsal ba ltar byas la /
NK029(ha)004:3433: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)004:3435: tshems kyi dri ma bsal bas /
NK029(ha)004:3437: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3438: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)004:3439: srid pa gsum gyi bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3440: dung gi so mngas thogs la /
NK029(ha)004:3441: dbu lo rin chen lcang lor 'khyil ba yis //
NK029(ha)004:3442: mthon mthing g.yas su 'khyil ba'i lcang lo 'di //
NK029(ha)004:3443: mdzes pa'i gtsug gtor 'bar bas brgyan pa ltar //
NK029(ha)004:3444: lha mi kun gyi lta bas mi ngom pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:3445: dug gsum dri bral mtshan ma mi mnga' yang //
NK029(ha)004:3446: bskur sti ri mo dung gi so mngas gis //
NK029(ha)004:3447: shad pas dug gsum skyon rnams rang byang nas //
NK029(ha)004:3448: bdag dang 'gro kun rnam grol mchog thob shog /
NK029(ha)004:3450: ces pas longs sku rnams kyi dbu skra shad pa ltar byas la /
NK029(ha)004:3451: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)004:3452: dung gi so mngas kyis dbu skra shad pa thams cad ma 'dres par 'gro ba'i don byed pa /
NK029(ha)004:3453: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3454: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)004:3455: srid pa gsum gyi bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3456: gser gyi chen po thogs la /
NK029(ha)004:3457: rgyal ba'i dbu gtsug mthon mthing ldan pa la /
NK029(ha)004:3458: nyon mongs sdug bsngal dri mas ma gos ste //
NK029(ha)004:3459: rin chen 'bar bas sdug bsngal kun las 'phags //
NK029(ha)004:3460: bltas pas mi ngom mtshan ma'i skyon bral yang //
NK029(ha)004:3461: bskur sti ri mo gser gyi chen po 'dis //
NK029(ha)004:3462: dbu skra zhabs sen 'brel pa'i tshul bstan nas //
NK029(ha)004:3463: dug gsum zung ngu rtog pa ku bcom nas //
NK029(ha)004:3464: sdug bsngal nyes pa bral nas bde thob ste //
NK029(ha)004:3465: thar pa'i mchog la bdag cag gnas gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3467: sprul sku rnams kyi dbu skra breg pa ltar byas nas //
NK029(ha)004:3469: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la //
NK029(ha)004:3470: gser gyi chen pas thub pa drug gi dbu skra breg pas /
NK029(ha)004:3471: dug gsum zug ngu thams cad dang bral ba'i don /
NK029(ha)004:3472: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3473: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)004:3474: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3475: de dag kyang lhag pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbang du'o //
NK029(ha)004:3476: thun mongs la sprul sku la so mngas mi dgos /
NK029(ha)004:3477: longs sku la chen pa mi dgos /
NK029(ha)004:3479: de ni tha mal pa'i skyon dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)004:3480: zag med mngon shes thob pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK029(ha)004:3481: lnga pa zhi ba'i lha rnams la che ba'i yon tan brgyan chas kyi dbang bskur ba gnyis ste /
NK029(ha)004:3482: thun mongs dang khyad par ro //
NK029(ha)004:3483: dang po bum pa'i dbang ni /
NK029(ha)004:3484: rnam rgyal bum pa blangs la sngon gleng bzhi brjod /
NK029(ha)004:3486: phun sum tshogs pa'i bkra shis brjod cing /
NK029(ha)004:3487: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni /
NK029(ha)004:3488: lha rnams kyis ni khrus gsol ltar /
NK029(ha)004:3489: lha yi chu ni dag pa yis /
NK029(ha)004:3490: de bzhin bdag gis sku khrus gsol /
NK029(ha)004:3491: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ye sh+ri ye h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:3492: ces dbu la bzhag pa'i tshul bya /
NK029(ha)004:3493: swa b+ha wa ces phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi thugs
NK029(ha)004:3494: kha nas rigs kyi yum bzhi byung nas ye shes
NK029(ha)004:3498: dbu la rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i don dran par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:3500: rten rab tu gnas pa'i lha rnams la rigs lnga'i dbu brgyan gyis /
NK029(ha)004:3502: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar rtogs nas 'khor
NK029(ha)004:3503: ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad
NK029(ha)004:3505: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad ye shes lngar mdzad pa'i don /
NK029(ha)004:3506: deng yon gyi bdag po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3507: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa thams cad dang /
NK029(ha)004:3508: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3510: dbu brgyan gyi mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:3514: de nas bum chu blug la /
NK029(ha)004:3515: rigs lnga yab yum sbyor ba'i chu rgyun gyi dbang bskur bas /

NK029(ha)004:3535: gser gyi snyan cha khog stong can bsam /

NK029(ha)004:3570: gser gyi dpung brgyan mu tig ha ra dang bcas pa bsam /
NK029(ha)004:3573: dpung brgyan gyis mnga' gsol bas /

NK029(ha)004:3577: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /

NK029(ha)004:3579: phyag gdub kyi mnga' gsol ni /
NK029(ha)004:3581: rat+na'i phyag gdub dang bcas pa bsam /
NK029(ha)004:3583: che ge mo phyag gdub kyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3584: srog chags bsad pa la sogs pas /
NK029(ha)004:3585: yan lag tshul khrims dag pa'i don /
NK029(ha)004:3587: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /

NK029(ha)004:3594: srid pa gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3597: sham thabs ras kyi gzhi ma ba ti dang /

NK029(ha)004:3603: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /

NK029(ha)004:3605: d+h+ai las seng ge la sogs pa'i sems can chen po lnga bsam /
NK029(ha)004:3607: che ge mo'i seng ge la sogs pa'i sems can chen po lnga /
NK029(ha)004:3608: gdan khri la mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3609: che ba'i yon tan lhun gyis grub ste /
NK029(ha)004:3610: mthar phyin pa'i sa non pa'i don /
NK029(ha)004:3612: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor srid pa gsum rin po che'i khri'i mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:3614: rat+na'i khri rkang mdzod mig dang bcas pa lha dang lha mo mang po lang ling can bsam /
NK029(ha)004:3616: che ge mo'i nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK029(ha)004:3619: thabs thugs rje chen pos yongs su khyab pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:3620: shes rab chen pos mtha'i lta ba ngan pa thams cad sel ba dang /

NK029(ha)004:3623: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:3624: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams kyis
NK029(ha)004:3625: thob par gyur cig /'od zer gyi mnga' gsol ba
NK029(ha)004:3626: ni / +aah h+aum swa h+aa lnga 'phro 'dus pas /
NK029(ha)004:3627: bden pa che 'od zer gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3628: chos thams cad bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes su gsal bas /

NK029(ha)004:3631: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:3632: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i don /
NK029(ha)004:3633: phyogs bcu'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor kyi mnga' gsol ni /

NK029(ha)004:3635: bden che ge rgyab rten zla dkyil gyis mnga' gsol bas /

NK029(ha)004:3638: phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can

NK029(ha)004:3641: sku mdog mthing kha la sogs pa dkyil 'khor gyi
NK029(ha)004:3642: lha so so rang gi sku mdog gsal bar bsam
NK029(ha)004:3644: che ge mo'i lha rnams kyi sku mdog gi mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3645: gting dpag dka' ba mi 'gyur ba'i chos nyid do //
NK029(ha)004:3646: skyon gyis ma gos pa'i sems nyid /
NK029(ha)004:3647: yon tan gyi che ba rgyas pa /
NK029(ha)004:3649: sna tshogs rol pa'i 'phrin las la sogs pa /
NK029(ha)004:3651: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:3652: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3653: dbu gsum gyi mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:3655: dbu gsum gsal bar byas la /
NK029(ha)004:3658: dbu gsum gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3659: rnam thar sgo gsum thob nas /
NK029(ha)004:3660: khams gsum gyi don mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)004:3661: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis phyag drug gi mnga' gsol ba /
NK029(ha)004:3664: phyag drug gsal bar bya ste /
NK029(ha)004:3666: phyag drug gi mnga' gsol bas /

NK029(ha)004:3671: zhabs bzhi gsal bar byas la /
NK029(ha)004:3674: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhis lhun grub kyi sa
NK029(ha)004:3675: la ma bsgrod par phyin cing bdud bzhi zil gyis
NK029(ha)004:3677: yon bdag dang phyogs bcu'i srid pa ljags kyi mnga' gsol /
NK029(ha)004:3679: ljags dmar ser glog ltar 'khyugs par sgom /

NK029(ha)004:3686: skye shi'i rtsa ba gcod cing sgrib pa thams cad zad par byed pa /
NK029(ha)004:3687: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can ral pas mnga' gsol pas /
NK029(ha)004:3688: dza'i spro bsdus ral pa mthon mthing lcang lo can bskyed la /

NK029(ha)004:3693: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /

NK029(ha)004:3701: mkhas pas gdul bya thams cad chus mi gson par /
NK029(ha)004:3703: phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can phyag mtshan drug gi mnga' gsol ba /

NK029(ha)004:3707: phyag mtshan gyi mnga' gsol bas /

NK029(ha)004:3710: phyogs bcu'i srid pa de rnams kyi mnga' gsol ba'o //
NK029(ha)004:3711: don drug pa chu dag gis sku khrus gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:3712: gzhung gi phyag 'tshal dkyil 'khor gsum po'i lha'i sku la khrus gsol bas /

NK029(ha)004:3718: de nas bden pa so so'i 'dod gsol bya /
NK029(ha)004:3720: che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)004:3722: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams dang gnyis su med par 'jal ba'i don /
NK029(ha)004:3724: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /

NK029(ha)004:3728: phyag rgya'i p+au dza phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3729: phyag rgya dam tshig gi sgo nas /
NK029(ha)004:3730: phyag rgya bzhi yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu /
NK029(ha)004:3731: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum kun tu bzang po'i p+au dza phul te /
NK029(ha)004:3732: bden che ge'i lha rnams la kun tu bzang po'i p+au dza phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3733: bdag nyid chen po'i p+au dzas longs spyod pa'i skal ba /
NK029(ha)004:3734: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can phyag dang zhabs gsil la /

NK029(ha)004:3736: sems can nyes byas dri ma sbyang slad du /
NK029(ha)004:3737: rgyal ba'i phyag zhabs dag ni bsil bgyis pas /

NK029(ha)004:3740: phyi nang gi dri ma thams cad yongs su dag pa'i don /
NK029(ha)004:3741: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum chu gtsang gis khrus gsol la /
NK029(ha)004:3742: ye shes sku la nyon mongs mi mnga' yang /
NK029(ha)004:3743: sems can nyon mongs bag chags sbyang slad du /
NK029(ha)004:3744: rgyal ba'i sku la chu gtsang khrus gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3745: sems can nyon mongs bag chags dag par shog /

NK029(ha)004:3747: nyon mongs pa'i bag chags kyi dri ma thams cad dag /
NK029(ha)004:3748: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyi yung chab gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3749: ye shes sku la rab rib mi mnga' yang //
NK029(ha)004:3750: sems can ma rig mun pa bsal slad du //
NK029(ha)004:3751: rgyal ba'i sku la yung chab khrus gsol bas //
NK029(ha)004:3752: rmongs pa'i rab rib ma lus dag par shog /

NK029(ha)004:3754: nyon mongs pa shes bya'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)004:3755: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu /
NK029(ha)004:3757: phyogs bcu'i srid pa 'dag chal gyi khrus gsol la /
NK029(ha)004:3758: rnam dag sku la dri ma mi mnga' yang /
NK029(ha)004:3759: sems can sdug bsngal dri ma gsal slad du /
NK029(ha)004:3760: 'dag chal dag gi sku khrus 'di gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3761: tshul khrims mngon par byang chub sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)004:3763: bden pa che ge 'dag chal gyi khrus gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3764: nyon mongs pa rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ste /
NK029(ha)004:3765: tshul khrims kyi phung po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3766: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku /

NK029(ha)004:3771: sems can mu ge'i sgrib pa sbyang slad du /
NK029(ha)004:3772: rat+na 'bru chab 'di dag gsol ba yis /
NK029(ha)004:3773: ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po chos kyi sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)004:3774: bden che 'bru chab kyi sku khrus gsol bas //
NK029(ha)004:3775: rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag ste /
NK029(ha)004:3776: ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3777: chos kyi sku la nyes pa'i bag chags dri ma
NK029(ha)004:3778: thams cad dag yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa spos
NK029(ha)004:3779: chab gsol la / 'phrin las lhun rdzogs bde gshegs sku gzugs la /
NK029(ha)004:3780: spos mchog dri yis sku khrus 'di gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3781: dri mchog stong gsum kun tu 'byung ba yis /
NK029(ha)004:3782: shes rab phung po sprul sku thob par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3783: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la spos mchog dri yis sku khrus gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3784: 'od gsal shes rab kyi phung po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3787: phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum sman chab gsol la /
NK029(ha)004:3788: rdo rje'i sku mchog nam mkha'i rang bzhin la /
NK029(ha)004:3789: dri med chab kyis sku khrus 'di gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3790: nyon mongs duh kha nad 'joms rgyal po 'di /
NK029(ha)004:3791: rnam grol phung po rdo rje'i sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)004:3793: che ge mo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la /
NK029(ha)004:3794: sman chab kyi sku khrus gsol bas /
NK029(ha)004:3795: nyon mongs pa'i nad thams cad dag ste /
NK029(ha)004:3796: rnam par grol ba'i phung po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3799: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:3800: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3802: chos rnams yongs su rdzogs pa'i sku mchog la /
NK029(ha)004:3803: rat+na lnga chab sku khrus 'di gsol bas /

NK029(ha)004:3806: bden che ge rat+na lnga chab gsol la /
NK029(ha)004:3807: sems can ma lus re ba bskong ste //
NK029(ha)004:3808: rnam par grol ba'i ye shes mthong ba'i phung po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3810: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa ras kyi sku phyis la //
NK029(ha)004:3811: thugs rje lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs la /
NK029(ha)004:3812: srid zhu gus phyir ras kyis sku phyis pas /
NK029(ha)004:3813: las dang nyon mongs bag chags kun spangs nas /
NK029(ha)004:3814: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sgo thob shog /
NK029(ha)004:3815: bden che ge ras kyi sku phyis pas /
NK029(ha)004:3816: las dang nyon mongs thams cad dag nas /
NK029(ha)004:3817: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sgo thob /
NK029(ha)004:3818: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum bdun pa phyi nang p+au dza dbul ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:3819: kun tu bzang po gzhung nas len dang /
NK029(ha)004:3820: phyag dang zhabs bsil yang 'dir mdzad /
NK029(ha)004:3821: las gzhung gi me tog dbul ba'i tshig yang 'dir brjod /
NK029(ha)004:3823: yon tan lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs la /
NK029(ha)004:3824: rat+na mdzes pa'i me tog 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3825: log lta'i nyon mongs tha ba kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)004:3826: lta bas mi ngoms mdzes pa'i sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)004:3827: push+pe sngags tshig gis me tog dbul /
NK029(ha)004:3828: bde che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la rat+na'i me tog phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3830: tshogs thams cad yongs su rdzogs nas lta bas mi ngoms pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)004:3832: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:3833: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can rnams kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3835: mchog tu rnam par dag pa'i sku mnga' ba'i //
NK029(ha)004:3836: sangs rgyas sku la bdug spos 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3837: dam tshig sdom pa'i nyes pa kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)004:3838: ye shes thugs rjes ma lus 'dren par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3840: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la gdug spos phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3841: theg pa so so'i sdom pa'i dri ma las grol ste /
NK029(ha)004:3842: dam tshig rnam par dag nas thugs rje chen po dang /
NK029(ha)004:3844: srid pa ma lus pa yongs su 'dzin pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)004:3846: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:3847: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3849: thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas sku gzugs la /
NK029(ha)004:3850: mun pa snang byed mar me 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3851: ma rig 'thib po'i mun pa kun gsal nas /
NK029(ha)004:3852: sangs rgyas spyan mnga' yongs su rdzogs par shog /'bul /
NK029(ha)004:3853: a lo ke sngags kyi tshig brjod /
NK029(ha)004:3854: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la mar me phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3855: lhan cig skyes pa'i gti mug las byung pa'i /
NK029(ha)004:3856: rab rib yongs su dag pas /
NK029(ha)004:3859: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:3860: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3862: snyigs ma lnga nyid 'bras bur yongs rdzogs pa'i /
NK029(ha)004:3863: sangs rgyas sku la dri chab 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3864: mya ngan zug ngu'i gdung ba kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)004:3865: 'od zer sna tshogs 'gyed pa'i sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)004:3867: bden che ge'i lha rnams la dri chab phul pas /
NK029(ha)004:3868: mya ngan gyi gdung ba thams cad dang bral nas 'od zer mtha' yas 'gyed pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)004:3870: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:3871: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3872: sman mchod lugs bzhin gzhung nas slangs bya /
NK029(ha)004:3873: ye shes sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa yis /
NK029(ha)004:3874: sangs rgyas sku la bdud rtsi 'adiphula bas /
NK029(ha)004:3875: dug lnga gdod nas sems su dag pa yi /
NK029(ha)004:3876: ye shes sku lnga lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3877: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la bdud rtsi lnga phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3878: dug lnga ma spangs gnas su dag nas /
NK029(ha)004:3879: ye shes sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i don /
NK029(ha)004:3881: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:3882: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3883: b+ha ling lugs bazhinah+aum bza' ces gzhang nas blangs /
NK029(ha)004:3885: chos rnams longs spyod rdzogs grub pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:3886: sangs rgyas sku la gtor ma 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)004:3887: rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)004:3888: gsang ba'i longs spyod yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3889: bden che ge gtor ma phul bas rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung ba thams cad dang bral nas /
NK029(ha)004:3890: gsang ba'i longs spyod rdzogs pa'i don /
NK029(ha)004:3891: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyis p+au dza byas la /
NK029(ha)004:3892: bde gshegs sku la ting 'dzin mchod phul bas //
NK029(ha)004:3893: phyi nang gsang don ma lus kun rdzogs te /
NK029(ha)004:3894: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes nas //'bras
NK029(ha)004:3895: bu mtha' yas kun la longs spyod shog bden pa
NK029(ha)004:3896: brjod / che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3897: dngos po ma lus pa'i ngo bo nyid rang bzhin gyi sku dang /
NK029(ha)004:3898: ye shes su lhun gyis grub pa /
NK029(ha)004:3900: spyod yul yongs su dag pa /
NK029(ha)004:3901: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa sgrol mchod sngags gzhung nas slangs tshig brjod la /
NK029(ha)004:3902: ye shes spyod yul yongs dag pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:3903: sangs rgyas sku la ta gan 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3904: khams gsum dug sum rtsad nas dag gyur ste /
NK029(ha)004:3905: sku gsum dngos grub lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3906: bden che ge ta gan 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3907: dug gsum yongs su dag nas /
NK029(ha)004:3908: sku gsum lhun gyis grub ste /
NK029(ha)004:3911: phyogs bcu'i srid pa sbyor mchod tshig sngags bsam rgyud bya /
NK029(ha)004:3913: sangs rgyas sku la g+ha na 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3914: phyi nang byang chub sems su rnam dag ste /
NK029(ha)004:3915: mtha' yas snyoms par 'jug pa thob par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3916: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor kyi lha rnams la g+ha na sbyor ba'i p+au dza 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3917: thabs dang shes rab kyi spyod pas snod bcud thig le chen po'i ye shes su dag ste /
NK029(ha)004:3918: mtha' yas lhun gyis grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin /
NK029(ha)004:3920: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:3921: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad
NK029(ha)004:3922: kyis thob par gyur cig /'dod yon lnga yi p+au
NK029(ha)004:3923: dza phul la / mtha' yas ldan dang bral ba med pa yi //
NK029(ha)004:3924: sangs rgyas sku la 'dod yon lnga phul bas //
NK029(ha)004:3925: mtha' la zhen pa'i gdung pa kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)004:3926: bde ba chen po'i thabs rnams rdzogs par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3927: bden che ge'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la 'dod yon lnga phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3928: longs spyod yongs su dag pa sogs pa gcig pa'i thabs yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK029(ha)004:3930: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:3931: srid pa gsum gyi bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:3932: lha la glu ye shes kyis p+au dza phul ste /
NK029(ha)004:3933: lang tshor rab rgyas glu dbyangs sgrogs byed pa /
NK029(ha)004:3934: smad byung glu yi mchod pa 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3935: dbang po'i zhen chags gdug pa kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)004:3936: mngon shes legs thob kun gyis bkur bar shog /
NK029(ha)004:3938: na mo phyogs che ge che ba'i ye shes mngon par mthong nas /
NK029(ha)004:3939: so so'i skye bo la sogs pa thams cad kyi bskur gnas su gyur pa /
NK029(ha)004:3940: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa lha mo cig tu spros
NK029(ha)004:3941: la rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa phul la
NK029(ha)004:3942: / s+au ra to'i tshig gis dbul /
NK029(ha)004:3943: gdangs snyan sgra yi mchod pa dam pa 'di /
NK029(ha)004:3944: rab 'byams sangs rgyas dgongs pa rdzogs phyir 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:3945: zhen 'dzin 'khrul pa ma lus kun bral na /
NK029(ha)004:3946: rna ba'i dga' ston phyogs bcur 'gyed par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3949: che ge mo'i thabs mkhas pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyis bya
NK029(ha)004:3950: ba mang pos bdag gzhan gyi don thams cad 'grub
NK029(ha)004:3951: par yon phyogs srid pa lhab lhub bla res la
NK029(ha)004:3952: sogs phul la / gzi byin khyad par shin tu 'phags pa yi /
NK029(ha)004:3953: sangs rgyas sku la lhab lhub bla bre 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3954: log pa'i lta ba mtha' dag kun spangs nas /
NK029(ha)004:3955: 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med thob par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3956: bden na mo phyogs che ge thams cad thugs rje'i dbang gis bla bres brdal ba chen po /
NK029(ha)004:3958: phyogs bcu'i srid pa 'phan phul la /
NK029(ha)004:3959: mdzes pa'i dar lce g.yo ba phyogs bcur bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:3960: sangs rgyas sku la mdzes 'phan 'di phul bas /
NK029(ha)004:3961: sems can log pa'i g.yo ba kun bral nas /
NK029(ha)004:3962: mkhyen pa'i ye shes thogs pa med par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3963: bden pa na mo che ge thams cad bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes cir yang mdzes pas /
NK029(ha)004:3964: shes bya thams cad khong du chud cing thams cad 'dir ston pas /
NK029(ha)004:3969: skyabs chen 'khor yug mdzes pa'i brgyan dang ldan //
NK029(ha)004:3970: sangs rgyas sku la gdugs mchog 'di phul bas //'khor ba'i tsha gdung sdug bsngal kun bral nas //
NK029(ha)004:3971: thams cad skyobs pa'i mthu dang ldan par shog /
NK029(ha)004:3972: bden na mo phyogs che ge thams cad thugs rje'i
NK029(ha)004:3973: skyabs kyis mtha'i duhkhasa gdungs pa bsil bar byed pa
NK029(ha)004:3974: / yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa rgyal mtshan phul la /
NK029(ha)004:3975: mi mthun phyogs las rgyal ba rgyal mtshan 'dir //
NK029(ha)004:3976: dus gsum sangs rgyas rnams la phul ba yis //
NK029(ha)004:3977: mtshan ma yod med kun dang bral gyur nas //
NK029(ha)004:3978: bdud bzhi la sogs kun las rgyal ba shog /
NK029(ha)004:3980: na mo che ge'i bdud bzhin las rgyal ba'i chos kyi tog chen po mngon du byung pa /
NK029(ha)004:3981: yon phyogs bcu'i srid pa yol ba phul la /
NK029(ha)004:3982: mi mthun gnod pa'i g.yo ba kun la skyob //
NK029(ha)004:3983: sangs rgyas sku la yol ba 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)004:3984: nyes tshogs mtha' dag ma lus kun bral nas //
NK029(ha)004:3985: thams cad skyobs pa'i bdag nyid chen por shog /
NK029(ha)004:3986: bden na mo che ge sems nyid rgya dang bral bar rtogs ste //
NK029(ha)004:3987: thams cad bdag nyid che bar skyob pa //
NK029(ha)004:3988: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa na bza' phul la /
NK029(ha)004:3989: byams mgon chen po kun la snyoms pa yis //
NK029(ha)004:3990: sangs rgyas sku la na bza' 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)004:3991: tha bas rgyags pa'i spyod pa kun bral ste //
NK029(ha)004:3992: gzi byin khyad par 'aphata pa'i sku thob shog /
NK029(ha)004:3993: bden na mo che ge tha bas rgyags pa'i spyod pa dang bral ste /
NK029(ha)004:3994: ngo tsha shes pa thams cad skyob cing gzi byin khyad par du 'phags pa /
NK029(ha)004:3996: phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gling bzhi man+dala rat+nasa sprul pa phul la /
NK029(ha)004:3997: 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la mnga' mnyes pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:3998: sangs rgyas sku la dkyil 'khor 'di phul bas //'phags pa'i nor gyis dbul ba kun bral ste //
NK029(ha)004:3999: ting 'dzin 'bum phrag yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK029(ha)004:4000: bden na mo che ge 'phags pa'i nor bdun dang /
NK029(ha)004:4004: yul zhing khang pa dang bcas pa dbul /
NK029(ha)004:4005: h'u 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la mnga' brnyes pa //
NK029(ha)004:4006: bde gshegs sku la yul mkhar 'di 'bul bas //
NK029(ha)004:4007: yul snang 'dzin pa'i 'ching ba kun bral nas //'phags pa'i zhing khams rnam dag thob par shog /
NK029(ha)004:4009: che ge mo'i zhing khams dang /
NK029(ha)004:4010: gzhal yas khang yongs su dag pa /
NK029(ha)004:4012: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:4013: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i bran pho mo phul ste /
NK029(ha)004:4015: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par 'phags yi //
NK029(ha)004:4016: bde gshegs sku la pho mo'i bran phul bas //
NK029(ha)004:4017: log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs spong nas //'khor rnams yongs smin tshogs la dbang byed shog /
NK029(ha)004:4019: che ge mo 'khor gsum dag ste dbang bskur ba /
NK029(ha)004:4021: phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i bu dang bu mo phul ste /
NK029(ha)004:4023: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par 'phags yi //
NK029(ha)004:4024: bde gshegs sku la lcam sring 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)004:4025: log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs su 'dul /
NK029(ha)004:4026: sprul pa'i gdul bya mtha' dag dbang byed shog /
NK029(ha)004:4027: bden che ge mo'i sprul pa bsam yas kyi khams gsum ma lus pa'i don la dbang byed pa /
NK029(ha)004:4028: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa chung ma phul ste /
NK029(ha)004:4030: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par 'phags yi //
NK029(ha)004:4031: bde gshegs sku la gzung ma 'di phul bas //
NK029(ha)004:4032: log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs su 'dul //
NK029(ha)004:4033: gsang spyod yongs su dag pa thob par shog /
NK029(ha)004:4035: che ge mo'i gsang ba'i longs spyod dag pa /
NK029(ha)004:4036: yon bdag phyogs bcu' srid pa gsum gyis rol mo ye shes kyi p+au dza phul te /
NK029(ha)004:4038: rang bzhin rnam dag bde gshegs sku gzugs la /
NK029(ha)004:4039: glu dbyangs snyan pa'i mchod pa 'di 'bul bas /
NK029(ha)004:4040: chos rnams skye 'gag med pa'i ngo bo la /
NK029(ha)004:4041: 'gro ba kun gyi spyod yul thob par shog /
NK029(ha)004:4043: rdo rje'i spo la phyin ste /
NK029(ha)004:4044: chos sgra chen po sems can ma lus pa'i rgyud yongs su grol bar byed pa /
NK029(ha)004:4045: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i srid pa gsum gyis tshogs gzhung bzhin phul ste /
NK029(ha)004:4046: yongs su smin pa phun sum tshogs pa yi //
NK029(ha)004:4047: bde gshegs sku la tshogs mchod 'di 'bul bas //
NK029(ha)004:4048: rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK029(ha)004:4049: gsang ba'i longs spyod yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK029(ha)004:4051: che ge mos bsod nams dang ye shes kyis tshogs su rdzogs pa /
NK029(ha)004:4052: yon bdag phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:4053: srid pa gsum gyis bsdus pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:4054: brgyad pa bden pa'i byin brlabs byas te /
NK029(ha)004:4056: slob dpon gyi g.yas pas yung dkar dang rdo rje gsor /
NK029(ha)004:4059: yon bdag gis me tog thogs la /
NK029(ha)004:4060: dam tshig rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4061: rig pa btul shugs kyi bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4062: rig pa 'dzin pa rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4063: lam yongs su dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4064: dam tshig dang sdom pa rnams kyis bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4065: chos mnyam pa nyid kyi bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4066: ngo bo nyid lhun gyis grub pa'i byin brlabs kyi bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4067: sa rnams yongs su non pa'i yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4068: ta tha rnams kyis mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams ji srid du /
NK029(ha)004:4070: che ge'i don yongs su ma rdzogs kyi bar du
NK029(ha)004:4071: brtan par bzhugs nas sems can kyi don yongs su
NK029(ha)004:4076: ces yungs dkar dang me tog dor /
NK029(ha)004:4077: dgu pa yon bdag gis bskor ba bya /
NK029(ha)004:4078: slob dpon gyis smon lam gdab /
NK029(ha)004:4080: cho ga'i lha rnams la bskor ba byas la /
NK029(ha)004:4081: dus 'di nas ji srid snying po byang chub la thug gi bar du /
NK029(ha)004:4083: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:4084: sems can thams cad mos pa yongs su mi nyams shing /
NK029(ha)004:4085: chos thams cad bdag nyid chen por lhun gyis grub pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:4086: ho chos nyid byang chub sems kyi bden pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4087: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las
NK029(ha)004:4088: mi zad pa brgyan gyi 'khor lor sangs rgyas pa'i
NK029(ha)004:4089: bden pa dang / de bzhin gshegs pa 'khor dang bcas pa'i thugs rje chen po'i byin brlabs dang /
NK029(ha)004:4093: cho ga las kyi rim pa'i gzhung rdzogs par bya ba'i byin brlabs kyis /
NK029(ha)004:4094: deng 'dir yon bdag che ge mos /
NK029(ha)004:4095: ting 'dzin yon bdag che ge mos /
NK029(ha)004:4096: dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs su gsol ba'i sems bskyed nas /
NK029(ha)004:4097: sku dang brgyan chas bzhengs su gsol ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:4098: yo byad dka' bas bsdus ste /
NK029(ha)004:4099: rab tu gnas pa gzhung bzhin byas nas /
NK029(ha)004:4100: bstan par bzhugs su gsol ba'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK029(ha)004:4103: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor ma lus pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4104: srid pa gsum gyi sems can thams cad dkyil 'khor 'di dang nam du yang mi 'bral zhing /
NK029(ha)004:4105: de dag gi phung po dang /
NK029(ha)004:4107: skye mched thams cad dkyil 'khor 'di yi ngo bor
NK029(ha)004:4108: lhun gyis grub pa'i sangs rgyas 'grub par gyur cig
NK029(ha)004:4112: zhi ba'i lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi rab gnas cho ga rdzogs so //
NK029(ha)004:4114: bla ma dang yi dam gyi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)004:4115: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i sbyin bsreg gi rim pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:4116: zhi khro gang byed gzhung bsrang /
NK029(ha)004:4119: rnam rgyal bum pa dang las bum byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)004:4120: zhi khro snying po 'dzab tu bsgrang /
NK029(ha)004:4121: mchod bstod tshar ba dang bdag 'jug blangs /
NK029(ha)004:4122: de nas me thab bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:4124: spangs su chags pa gang ba bya /
NK029(ha)004:4125: de'i dbus su rtse khru gang dbus su zlum por bskor /
NK029(ha)004:4126: sor bzhi nang du bskyal la zlum por bskor /
NK029(ha)004:4127: de'i sor bzhi gyen du rtsigs /
NK029(ha)004:4128: de nas sor bzhi nang du 'jal zlum por bskor /
NK029(ha)004:4129: de'i nang du mtho gang ba gcig yong ste /
NK029(ha)004:4130: de mthur bsag pa brus la nang du sor bzhi tsam 'ong bar bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:4131: de la me'i sa bon ram bri bar bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:4132: de'i steng du shug pa la sogs pa'i shing dkar po khru gang pa tsam du btubs ste /
NK029(ha)004:4133: gcig gi steng du gcig bzhag la brtsigs par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:4134: steng du mtha' nas bskor ba'i tshul du brtsigs la khong seng can du cung zad bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:4135: shing med na ba glang gi lci bas kyang gzhung bshad do //
NK029(ha)004:4136: de nas rnal 'byor pa kha shar du bltas la /
NK029(ha)004:4138: khyad par rang gi mchod rdzas bshams /
NK029(ha)004:4139: g.yon phyogs su thun mong gi mchod rdzas bshams /
NK029(ha)004:4140: phyi rim gru chad lha snams sgo la sogs pa grub chad bri bar bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:4142: mar la sogs bsreg rdzas ni /
NK029(ha)004:4143: thabs kyi yan lag yon bdag rgyas /
NK029(ha)004:4144: ces pas thabs kyang rgyas par bya'o //'byor ba 'phel ba'i phyir mar dang /
NK029(ha)004:4145: gzi brjid 'phel ba'i phyir yam shing dang /
NK029(ha)004:4146: lhag par shes rab 'phel ba'i phyir bud shing dang /
NK029(ha)004:4147: bdag bsrung ba'i phyir ku sha dang /
NK029(ha)004:4148: nad zhi ba'i phyir nyungs dkar dang /
NK029(ha)004:4149: bsod nams rgyas pa'i phyir 'bras dang /
NK029(ha)004:4150: sdig pa dag pa'i phyir til dang /
NK029(ha)004:4151: nor dang 'bru 'phel ba'i phyir so ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:4152: stobs che ba'i phyir sran ma dang /
NK029(ha)004:4153: dbang thang rgyas par bya ba'i phyir nas dang /
NK029(ha)004:4154: tshe 'phel ba'i phyir dur ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:4156: shes rab che ba'i phyir 'o ma dang /
NK029(ha)004:4158: shing gshags pa'i rtser mar byugs la /
NK029(ha)004:4159: brgya rtsa brgyad dam nyi shu rtsa gcig gam /
NK029(ha)004:4160: bdun bdun gyi gang 'grub bsham mo //
NK029(ha)004:4161: zhi rgyas dbang drag kha bsgyur du shes par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:4162: thab kyi drung du zhi ba la shar /
NK029(ha)004:4165: drag po la las gang byed kyi phyogs su 'dug la /
NK029(ha)004:4166: yang snying po brjod cing nang mchod kyis yo byad bsang /
NK029(ha)004:4168: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum yongs su gyur pa'i thab zhi ba la dkar zlum po /
NK029(ha)004:4169: mu ran la rdo rje'i 'phreng bas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)004:4170: rgyas pa la gru bzhi gser po /
NK029(ha)004:4171: mu ran la rin po che'i 'phreng bas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)004:4172: dbang la zla gam dmar po /
NK029(ha)004:4173: mu ran la pad+ma'i 'phreng bas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)004:4174: drag po la gru gsum nag po /
NK029(ha)004:4175: mu ran la rdo rje gdengs pas bskor ba /
NK029(ha)004:4176: phyogs 'dis phyed la rgya'i phyed kyi dpangs dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:4177: dwangs zhing thogs pa med pa las dang mthun pa'i bud shing rtsigs pas gang par bskyed nas /
NK029(ha)004:4178: slar yang h+aum gis byin gyis brlabs po /
NK029(ha)004:4179: 'jam po gsum la bsreg rdzas g.yas dang /
NK029(ha)004:4181: drag po la bsreg rdzas g.yon dang /
NK029(ha)004:4182: mchod rdzas g.yas su bsham mo //
NK029(ha)004:4183: re re la 'ang +aah h+aum las byung ba'i rdzas dwangs zhing thogs pa med par bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:4184: las so so'i sngags kyis byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)004:4185: de nas yi dam kyi snying po'i mthar /
NK029(ha)004:4189: drag po la g.yon bskor ste /
NK029(ha)004:4190: shar lho nas me sbar la bslug cing /
NK029(ha)004:4191: badz+ra dz+wa la'i sngags brjod la /
NK029(ha)004:4193: me de bsang zhing gsos nas teng nge 'dzin gyis dpal chen po'i thugs kha nas /
NK029(ha)004:4194: yi ge ram dmar po 'od dang bcas pas thab khu du byung /
NK029(ha)004:4195: de las me ril po gcig tu gyur /
NK029(ha)004:4196: de las spro bsdus byas pa las /
NK029(ha)004:4197: ag+ne dz+wa la dz+wa la h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:4199: me lha drang srong khros pa'i cha byad can /
NK029(ha)004:4201: phyag g.yas dang po na lcags kyu /
NK029(ha)004:4203: g.yon dang po na lcags kyu /
NK029(ha)004:4205: zangs kyi ra skyes la chibs pa /
NK029(ha)004:4206: dur khrod kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa /
NK029(ha)004:4207: ye shes kyi me lha mchod cing spyan drangs pa'i rim pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:4209: h'u ye shes sman kyi spyod yul nas /
NK029(ha)004:4210: me lha drang srong 'khor dang bcas /
NK029(ha)004:4211: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis /
NK029(ha)004:4212: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs me'i lha /
NK029(ha)004:4213: sems can don la dam tshig dgongs /
NK029(ha)004:4216: ag ne ye dz+nya na sa ma ye e h+ya hi /
NK029(ha)004:4218: mah+aa ka ru ni ka kri sha ho /
NK029(ha)004:4222: zhes phyag rgya rnam bzhis shar lho nas spyan drangs nas /
NK029(ha)004:4223: h+aum tshangs pa 'jig rten mgon gyi sras //
NK029(ha)004:4224: gzi brjid 'bar ba me'i lha //'dod pa thams cad rab bsgrub phyir //
NK029(ha)004:4225: thugs rjes sems can don mdzad pa //'bar ba'i gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)004:4226: ag ne ye sa ma ye tish+tha badz+ra /
NK029(ha)004:4227: zhes pas dbyer med par stim zhing bzhugs su gsol /
NK029(ha)004:4228: h+aum pad+ma rigs las grub pa yi //
NK029(ha)004:4229: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /'phrin las kun gyis dpang po mdzad //
NK029(ha)004:4231: ag ne ye a la la hoh drang srong chen po sngon chad ma dar ba'i //
NK029(ha)004:4232: ting 'dzin dbang bsgyur zhal zas bdud rtsi rnams //
NK029(ha)004:4233: dag cing gtsang mar spyar ste 'bul lags kyis //
NK029(ha)004:4234: ye shes thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol /
NK029(ha)004:4235: h+aum lha yi rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK029(ha)004:4236: ra skyes chibs nas glog las mgyogs //
NK029(ha)004:4237: bsreg rdzas kun gyi phyag tshangs mdzad //
NK029(ha)004:4238: tshim byed khyod la mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:4239: na ma sa man+ta bud+ha nam /
NK029(ha)004:4240: b+ai ma la ag ne ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:4241: tshil chen dang mar me bsgreng ngo //
NK029(ha)004:4242: h+aum tshangs pa 'jig rten mgon gyi sras /
NK029(ha)004:4243: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /'byung po yongs la skyabs pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)004:4244: thugs dam dbang gi rgyud bskul ba //
NK029(ha)004:4245: rig pa grub pa'i drang srong mchog /
NK029(ha)004:4246: nyon mongs bsreg mdzad shes rab 'od //
NK029(ha)004:4247: bskal pa'i me ltar gzi brjid 'bar //
NK029(ha)004:4248: mngon shes rdzu 'phrul zhabs dang ldan //
NK029(ha)004:4249: thabs kyi sprul pas ra la chibs //
NK029(ha)004:4251: bdud rtsi bcud ldan g+han+d+he bsnams //
NK029(ha)004:4252: chos kyi bdud rtsi yongs la bsil //
NK029(ha)004:4253: nyes pa'i skyon bral tshangs par spyod //'jig rten gnas kyang mya ngan 'das //
NK029(ha)004:4254: zhi ba mnyes kyang thugs rje che //
NK029(ha)004:4255: de la bstod de phyag 'tshal kyang //
NK029(ha)004:4256: h+aum me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK029(ha)004:4257: mnyam pa'i ngang la kun snang yang //
NK029(ha)004:4258: chos nyid ngang las ma g.yos pa //
NK029(ha)004:4259: ye shes sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)004:4261: ye shes klo yangs 'khyiil ba'i ham khung 'dir /
NK029(ha)004:4262: dam rdzas bdud rtsi sbyar ba'i sbyin bsreg 'di /
NK029(ha)004:4263: drang srong me lha'i zhal du mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:4264: bdag la sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol /
NK029(ha)004:4265: na ma sarba pany+tsa a mri ta b+ha lim ta ag+ne swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:4268: ho me lha drang srong gi rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa la 'phrin las su gsol ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:4269: me 'bar ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs nas
NK029(ha)004:4270: sbyin bsreg gi rdzas rnams ye shes kyi zhal du
NK029(ha)004:4274: dbang bskur bar gsol ba btab pas /
NK029(ha)004:4275: lha rnams kyis mchod cing dbang bskur bas lus thams cad gang /
NK029(ha)004:4276: dri ma thams cad dag chu lhag ma spyi bor lud pa las /
NK029(ha)004:4277: zhi ba la rnam par snang mdzad kyis dbu brgyan /
NK029(ha)004:4278: rgyas pa la rin chen 'byung ldan /
NK029(ha)004:4280: drag po la don yod grub pas dbu brgyan par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)004:4281: de nas bzang zhing thog pa med pa'i sku sha dag byed du 'bul ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:4282: sku sha 'di ni gtsang zhing dge /
NK029(ha)004:4283: dkon mchog gsum gyi dag byed de //
NK029(ha)004:4284: lha rnams kyi yang dag byed yin //
NK029(ha)004:4285: sa las skyes pa'i snying po mchog /
NK029(ha)004:4286: bdag cag la bgegs med par mdzod cig /
NK029(ha)004:4287: ces brjod la phyogs mtshams brgyad nas 'bul lo //
NK029(ha)004:4288: de nas de'i zhal nas 'od kyi sbu gu byung nas mar khu gsol bar bsam zhing /
NK029(ha)004:4289: ag+ne te wa ri shi ha bya ka bya di bya ma h+aa na ye di bye /
NK029(ha)004:4290: zhes pa'i mthar zhi ba la /
NK029(ha)004:4291: sdig pa dang sgrib pa bar du gcod pa thams cad shin ting ku ru ye swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)004:4292: rgyas pa la tshe dang bsod nams dang 'byor pa thams cad pusha ting ku ru ye //
NK029(ha)004:4293: dbang la che ge mo pa sham ku ru ho /
NK029(ha)004:4294: drag po la che ge mo ma ra ya phata /
NK029(ha)004:4297: de nas ag+ne ye zhes pa'i mthar phyi mchod nang mchod phul nas /
NK029(ha)004:4299: zhu ba'i rdzas rnams zhal dang /
NK029(ha)004:4300: gong bu'i rdzas rnams phyag dang /
NK029(ha)004:4301: yam shing 'bar ba'i dkyil du 'bul bar bya ste /
NK029(ha)004:4306: sarba p+aa pam d+ha ha na badz+ra swa h+aa /
NK029(ha)004:4316: badz+ra mah+aa b+ha la ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:4322: badz+ra a mri te ha ta badz+ra ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:4323: ku sha rnams byin gyis brlabs la 'bul lo //
NK029(ha)004:4324: ag+ne ye 'ba' zhig gis dbul lo //
NK029(ha)004:4325: mthar rten gyi tshig rnams sngar bshad pa bzhin no //
NK029(ha)004:4330: dbang la me tog 'bras bu dmar po /
NK029(ha)004:4331: drag po la me tog sngon po'i dug sna tshogs /
NK029(ha)004:4334: til la sogs pa la ag+ne ye shin+tam ku ru ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:4335: zas mchog la sogs pa la /
NK029(ha)004:4336: ag+ne ye pusha tang ku ru ye /
NK029(ha)004:4337: me tog dmar po la sogs la /
NK029(ha)004:4338: ag+ne ye pa shang ku ru ye swah+aa /
NK029(ha)004:4339: khrag la sogs pa la ag+ne y+ae ma ra y+aa phata /
NK029(ha)004:4341: 'jam po gsum la lag pa g.yas dang /
NK029(ha)004:4342: drag po la g.yon pas 'bul lo //
NK029(ha)004:4343: sreg rdzas phul ba'i mthar mchod cing bstod nas /
NK029(ha)004:4345: ag+ne ye dz+wa la ram zhes pas me lha 'bar ba'i rnam par bsam mo /
NK029(ha)004:4347: 'phrin las so so'i dbang gis bsgyur la /
NK029(ha)004:4353: so so'i nyams dang cha lugs dang ldan zhing /
NK029(ha)004:4354: de'i thugs ka nas 'od 'phros pa'i pho nya rnams kyis las so sor mdzad par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)004:4355: de ni 'jig rten pa'i me lha mchod pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:4356: de nas me lha'i lto bar b+h+rum b+hi sha b+hi
NK029(ha)004:4357: shud+ha sogs gzhal yas khang dang lha rnams sngags kyis
NK029(ha)004:4359: zhi khro gang byed spyan drangs la stim /
NK029(ha)004:4360: de la shu nya ta dz+ny+aa na la sogs pa'i dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)004:4361: sku gsung thugs kyi lho bsgom /
NK029(ha)004:4362: bde bar gshegs so nas mchod pa 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:4363: de nas mar la sogs pa bsreg rdzas lag tu thogs ste /
NK029(ha)004:4364: badz+ra d+h+rika mum d+ha du shwa ri kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)004:4365: zhes pas brgya rtsa brgyad dang lha gzhan yang 'dra'o //
NK029(ha)004:4366: badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka kro ti shwa ri kha hi /
NK029(ha)004:4369: rgyas pa la rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka kro ti shwa ri kh+aa hi /
NK029(ha)004:4370: dbang la pad+ma he ru ka kro ti shwa ri kh+aa hi //
NK029(ha)004:4371: drag po la karma he ru ka kro ti shwa ri kha hi /
NK029(ha)004:4374: bsreg rdzas bstun ste dbul ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:4375: h+aum rdo rje rigs mchog 'khor ba stong mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)004:4376: dus gsum 'gyur ba med cing sra brtan sku /
NK029(ha)004:4377: rdo rje sems dpa' che la sbyin bsren bsreg mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:4378: h+aum de bzhin rigs mchog long spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)004:4379: nam mkha' dang 'dra cis kyang ma slad pa'i /
NK029(ha)004:4380: rnam par snang mdzad che la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:4381: h+aum rin chen rigs mchog mi zad gter ldan pa'i /
NK029(ha)004:4382: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyis brgyan pa'i sku /
NK029(ha)004:4383: rin chen 'byung ldan che la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:4384: h+aum pad+ma'i rigs mchog ma chags cis ma gos /
NK029(ha)004:4385: tshe dang ye shes nam mkha'i mthar mnyam pa /
NK029(ha)004:4386: snang ba mtha' yas che la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:4387: h+aum las kyi rigs mchog rgyud drug stong mdzad pa /
NK029(ha)004:4388: 'gro ba'i don la skyo ngal mi mnga' ba'i /
NK029(ha)004:4389: don yod grub pa che la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:4390: h+aum ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i ho ma khung du /
NK029(ha)004:4391: chags pa'i rgyud lnga'i bag chags ma lus bsreg sbyangs nas /
NK029(ha)004:4392: sman dang bdud rtsi dam rdzas mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4393: dam nyams dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)004:4394: skye med rnam dag hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4395: chos can skye ba'i yam shing las //
NK029(ha)004:4396: spros med byang chub ye shes mes //
NK029(ha)004:4397: mtshan ma'i bag chags bsreg sbyang 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4398: rnam dag b+ha ga'i hmo khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4399: chags pa'i bag chags yam shing la //
NK029(ha)004:4400: bde chen byang chub sems spar ste /
NK029(ha)004:4402: dpal chen zhal gyi hmo khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4403: nyon mongs lnga'i yam shing la //
NK029(ha)004:4404: ye shes lnga'i me spar ste /
NK029(ha)004:4406: snang srid nam mkha'i hom khung du //'byung ba bzhi'i yam shing la //
NK029(ha)004:4407: phyag rgya tshogs kyi me sbar ste //
NK029(ha)004:4408: snang srid dngos po bsreg sbyangs 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4409: thab chen lnga'i hom khung du //'khor ba'i sdug bsngal yam shing la //
NK029(ha)004:4410: ye shes chen po'i me klong du //
NK029(ha)004:4412: klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hmo khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4413: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i yams shing la //
NK029(ha)004:4414: bsreg rdzas skye ba'i chos yin ste //
NK029(ha)004:4415: rang bzhin nyid la thim par mdzod //
NK029(ha)004:4416: nyon mongs lnga'i dam rdzas dag /
NK029(ha)004:4418: phung po lnga'i dam rdzas dag /
NK029(ha)004:4419: thabs mchog yab lnga'i sku la 'bul //'byung lnga 'dus pa'i bsreg rdzas rnams //
NK029(ha)004:4420: shes rab yum bzhi'i klong du 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4421: h+aum dam nyams dam bskongs dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)004:4422: h+aum nam mkha'i dbyings phyug ma ni ye nas rnam rtog bral //
NK029(ha)004:4423: thugs kyi longs spyod sna tshogs rdzogs mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)004:4424: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyis yum //
NK029(ha)004:4425: yum chen dbyings phyug ma la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:4426: rdo rje dbyings phyug ma ni ye nas rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)004:4427: longs spyod rdzogs mdzad de bzhin gshegs pa'i yum //
NK029(ha)004:4428: sangs rgyas kun gyis sku yi mchod mnga' ba'i //
NK029(ha)004:4429: yum chen sangs rgyas spyan la sbyin bsreg mchod pa 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4430: h+aum rin chen dbyings phyug ma ni ye nas gter dang ldan //
NK029(ha)004:4431: yon tan rin chen mang po'i'abyunga gnas yum //
NK029(ha)004:4432: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum mchog ma ma ki /
NK029(ha)004:4433: yon tan gter 'dzin khyed la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4434: h+aum pad+ma dbyings phyug ma ni 'dod chags skyon dang bral //
NK029(ha)004:4435: gsungs rabs sgra yi mchod pa mnyes mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)004:4436: dus gsum rgyal ba kun gyi gsung mnga' ba //
NK029(ha)004:4437: yum chen na bza' dkar la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4438: h+aum las kyi dbyings phyug ma ni dug gsum rol
NK029(ha)004:4439: bar mdzad //'phrin las sna tshogs ma lus grub pa
NK029(ha)004:4440: mo //'phags pa'i sa bcur sgrol ba sgrol mdzad ma
NK029(ha)004:4441: // yum chen dam tshig sgrol la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4442: h+aum ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //'byung ba lnga yi bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:4443: sman dang dam rdzas bdud rtsi mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4444: dam nyams dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)004:4445: skye med rnam dag hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4446: zhes pa rnams bar bar du 'adre'o //
NK029(ha)004:4447: h+aum bskal bzang sems dpa' brgyad rnams ni //
NK029(ha)004:4448: bde bar gshegs pa kun gyis sras mchog ste //
NK029(ha)004:4449: yon tan mi zad sprul pa bsam yas pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:4450: byang chub sems dpa' brgyad la sbyin bsreg mchod pa 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4451: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4452: rnam shes brgyad gyi bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:4453: sman dang dam rdzas bdud rtsi mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4454: dam nyams dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)004:4455: h+aum sgeg mo 'phreng thog rin chen glu gar can //
NK029(ha)004:4456: nam mkha' mnyam pa'i mchod pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK029(ha)004:4457: bde gshegs rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)004:4458: byang chub lha mo brgyad la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4459: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4460: yul brgyad bag chags ma lus bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:4461: sman dang dam rdzas bdud rtsi mcho da par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4462: dam nyams dam bskongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)004:4463: h+aum ye shes thugs rje nam mkha'i mtha' khyab pa //
NK029(ha)004:4464: byed pa thams cad rdo rje kun tu bzang //
NK029(ha)004:4465: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor kun gyi 'byung gnas gtso //
NK029(ha)004:4466: kun bzang yab yum gnyis la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4467: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4468: yid chos bag chags ma lus bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:4469: sman dang dam rdzas bdud rtsis dam nyams dam bskongs ye shes rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po nas //
NK029(ha)004:4470: gnyen po'i stobs kyis so sor 'dul mdzad pa //'phrin las rgya mtsho'i yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK029(ha)004:4471: thub pa chen po drug la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4472: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4473: rgyud drug bag chags ma lus bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:4474: sman dang bdud rtsi dam rdzas dam nyams dam bskongs rta mgrin la sogs khro rgyal chen po bzhi //
NK029(ha)004:4475: gdug pa 'dul zhing 'phrin las rdzogs mdzad pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:4476: gshin rje stobs chen rta mgrin bdud rtsi 'khyil /
NK029(ha)004:4477: khro rgyal bzhi la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4478: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4479: bdag rtogs rnam bzhi'i bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:4480: sman dang bdud rtsi dam rdzas dam nyams dam bskongs
NK029(ha)004:4481: mthu dang rdo rje gdong mo mgyogs ma pho nya
NK029(ha)004:4482: bzhi // tshad med bzhi rdzogs gsang ba yum gyi ngang //
NK029(ha)004:4483: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrogs dril bu ma //
NK029(ha)004:4484: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4485: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4486: rtag chad bzhi yi bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:4487: sman dang bdud rtsi dam rdzas rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams kyis bzhes nas kyang //
NK029(ha)004:4488: nam mkha' mnyam pa'i dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)004:4489: bsgrub mchog rnams pa stsol zhing bstan par mdzod //
NK029(ha)004:4490: h+aum ye shes rdo rje nyon mongs 'khor ba 'joms //
NK029(ha)004:4491: thabs ldan mtshon cha'i bskal pa dngos po 'jig /
NK029(ha)004:4492: zhe sdang tshul gyis zhe sdang 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)004:4493: badz+ra he ru ka la sbyin bsreg mchod par ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4494: sman dang dam rdzas bdud rtsi mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4495: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //'gro rnams 'dul zhing gshegs mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)004:4496: shes rab nam mkha'i bskal pas 'joms //
NK029(ha)004:4497: gti mug tshul gyis gti mug 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)004:4498: bud+ha he ru ka la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4499: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4500: sman dang dam rdzas bdud rtsi bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)004:4501: rin chen dbyings ltar re ba kun bskong zhing //
NK029(ha)004:4502: bdag med zhi gnas chu'i bskal pas 'a khru //
NK029(ha)004:4503: nga rgyal tshul gyis nga rgyal 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)004:4504: rat+na he ru ka la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4505: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi 'khor ba'i 'dam du pad ltar sku 'khrungs shing //
NK029(ha)004:4506: lhag mthong me chen bskal pa'i me chen bsreg /'dod chags tshul gyis 'dod chags 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)004:4507: pad+ma he ru ka la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4508: ye shes klog yangs 'khyil ba'i ho khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4509: sman dang bdud rtsi dam rdzas bla med sku gsung
NK029(ha)004:4510: thugs kyi 'phrin las rgya mtsho 'gro ba'i don mdzad
NK029(ha)004:4511: pa // shes rab thog med bskal pa'i rlung gi bskyod //
NK029(ha)004:4512: phrag dog tshul gyis phrag dog 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)004:4513: karma he ru ka la sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4514: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4515: sman dang bdud rtsi dam rdzas bla med sku gsung
NK029(ha)004:4516: thugs kyi ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba sman bla
NK029(ha)004:4517: med thugs kyi longs spyod sna tshogs mi dmigs shing
NK029(ha)004:4518: // brtson 'grus mthar phyin zhe sdang rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)004:4519: rtag pa reg bya' mchod pas mnyes mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)004:4520: sra bstan rdo rje dbang bskur khro mo rgyal //
NK029(ha)004:4521: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i sbyin bsreg 'di //
NK029(ha)004:4522: badz+ra kro ti'i sku la mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4523: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi h+aum sku'i longs spyod sna tshogs mi dmigs shing //
NK029(ha)004:4524: shes rab mthar phyin gti mug rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)004:4525: phyag rgya gzugs kyis mchod pas mnyes mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)004:4526: chos dbyings nam mkha'i dbang phyug khro mo rgyal //
NK029(ha)004:4527: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4528: sman dang dam rdzas 'bar ba'i sbyin bsreg 'di //
NK029(ha)004:4529: bud+ha kro ti ma la mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4530: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi h+aum yon tan longs spyod sna tshogs mi dmigs shing //
NK029(ha)004:4531: sbyin pa mthar phyin nga rgyal rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)004:4532: ting 'dzin ro yi mchod pas mnyes mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)004:4533: bdag med zhi gnas dbang bskur khro mo rgyal //
NK029(ha)004:4534: ye shes klong yangs dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i sbyin bsreg 'di //
NK029(ha)004:4535: rat+na kro ti shwa ri ma la mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4537: h+aum gsung gi longs spyod sna tshogs mi dmigs shing //
NK029(ha)004:4538: tshul khrims mthar phyin 'dod chags rnam par dag /
NK029(ha)004:4539: gsung rab sgra yi mchod pas mnyes mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)004:4540: lhag mthong ye shes dbang phyug khro mo rgyal //
NK029(ha)004:4541: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hmo khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4542: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i sbyin bsreg 'di //
NK029(ha)004:4543: pad+ma kro ti shwa ri ma la mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4544: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //'phrin las longs spyod sna tshogs mi dmigs shing //
NK029(ha)004:4545: bzod pa mthar phyin phrag dog rnam pa dag /
NK029(ha)004:4546: tshul khrims dri yi mchod pas mnyes mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)004:4547: thog med las la dbang bskur khro mo rgyal //
NK029(ha)004:4548: yeshesa klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4549: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i sbyin bsreg 'di //
NK029(ha)004:4550: karma kro ti shwa ri ma la mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4551: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi h'u /
NK029(ha)004:4552: koo ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams ni //'jigs byed yab yum rol ba'i sras mchog ma //
NK029(ha)004:4553: lus tshul sku mdog phyag mtshan ma nges gsal //
NK029(ha)004:4554: thugs rje so so'i 'phrin las mdzad pa la //
NK029(ha)004:4555: spros med ye shes 'bar ba'i hmo khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4556: rnam shes brgyad kyi bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:4557: ye shes lnga ldan sbyin bsreg mchog par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4558: dam nyams dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)004:4559: h+aum seng ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams kyang //
NK029(ha)004:4560: dpa' chen dbang phyug rol pa'i sras mchog ma //
NK029(ha)004:4561: smon lam dbang gi 'khor ba'i cha 'dzin ma //
NK029(ha)004:4562: thugs rjes so so'i 'phrin las grub mdzad ma //
NK029(ha)004:4563: spros med ye shes 'bar ba'i hmo khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4564: yan lag bzhi'i bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:4565: ye shes lnga ldan sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4566: dam nyams dam bskongs mthu dang dngos grub rtsol /
NK029(ha)004:4567: h+aum rdo rje sring 'gro la sogs sga ma bzhi //
NK029(ha)004:4568: dgyes pa'i byang chub sems las sku bskyed ma //
NK029(ha)004:4569: thugs rje dbang gi so so'i 'phrin las mdzad //
NK029(ha)004:4570: dkyil 'khor sgo bzhir rngam gzugs gnas pa la //
NK029(ha)004:4571: spros med ye shes 'bar ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4572: dam nyams dam bskongs yan lag bzhi'i bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:4573: ye shes lnga ldan sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4574: dam nyams dam bskong mthu dang h+aum mdzad la sogs khro bo chen po bcu //
NK029(ha)004:4575: khros pa'i byang chub sems las sku bskyed pa //
NK029(ha)004:4576: steng 'og phyogs bcu kun gyi bdud 'dul zhing //
NK029(ha)004:4577: rngam pa'i stobs kyi rab brjid mtshon cha rnams //
NK029(ha)004:4578: spros med ye shes 'bar ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4579: mi dge bcu'i bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:4580: ye shes lnga ldan sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4581: dam nyams dam bskongs dbang dang dbang grub stsol //
NK029(ha)004:4582: h+aum ma sring la sogs dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //'jig rten lha chen rnams kyi chung ma ste //
NK029(ha)004:4583: las kyi dbang gi mtshan nyid ma 'dres so sor gsal /
NK029(ha)004:4584: dpal chen slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK029(ha)004:4585: spros med ye shes 'bar ba'i hom khung du //
NK029(ha)004:4586: sgal tshig nyi shu brgyad kyis bag chags bsreg sbyangs nas //
NK029(ha)004:4587: ye shes lnga ldan sbyin bsreg mchod par 'bul //
NK029(ha)004:4588: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)004:4590: gzhan yang phyi yi mchod pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:4591: nang bdud rtsi'i mchod pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:4592: yid las byung ba'i mchod pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:4594: gang 'byor gyis mchod nas gtor ma phul la bsreg rdzas rnams sngar ltar byin gyis brlabs ste /
NK029(ha)004:4595: bsreg rdzas de dag gang la bsnyen pa song pa'i sngags kyis 'bul lo //
NK029(ha)004:4596: grangs ni zhi ba la brgyad //
NK029(ha)004:4597: rgyas pa la brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK029(ha)004:4598: dbang la nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK029(ha)004:4599: drag po la drug cu tham pa rnams phul ba'i
NK029(ha)004:4600: thog ma dang tha ma'i spel tshig dang sbyar ro
NK029(ha)004:4602: shin tu mang du phul ba'i mthar //
NK029(ha)004:4603: g+hu ya dz+nya na la sogs pa'i rjes su so
NK029(ha)004:4604: so'i spel tshig dang bcas pa ci rigs par dbul
NK029(ha)004:4607: mar ni me'i tshang du phul la //
NK029(ha)004:4608: mthar lha'i sngags spel tshig dang bcas pas mar dgang bslugs gsum 'bul lo //
NK029(ha)004:4609: slar yang 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab /
NK029(ha)004:4610: ma 'byor pa dang nyams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4611: gang yang bdag rmongs blo yis ni //
NK029(ha)004:4612: bgyis pa dang ni bgyid brtsal ba //
NK029(ha)004:4613: de kun mgon pos bzod par mdzo //
NK029(ha)004:4614: ces lan gsum gyis bzod par gsol nas //
NK029(ha)004:4615: khyed kyi sems can don kun mdzod //
NK029(ha)004:4616: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK029(ha)004:4617: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs nas kyang /
NK029(ha)004:4618: slar yang 'byon par mdzad du gsol //
NK029(ha)004:4619: yi ge brgya pa'i sngags brjod la gshegs par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:4621: dam tshig pa bdag nyid la bsdu'o /
NK029(ha)004:4622: thabs kyi dbus nas thal ba cung zad blangs pa
NK029(ha)004:4623: dpral bar skus pa ni dam tshig pa bdag la
NK029(ha)004:4624: bsdu ba'o //'jin rten las 'das pa'i me lha mchod
NK029(ha)004:4625: pa ste de ni dngos gazhi'o //
NK029(ha)004:4626: de nas mar blug gzar gang thabs kyi dbus su blugs nas /
NK029(ha)004:4627: dz+wa la ram zhes brjod pas 'jig rten pa'i me
NK029(ha)004:4628: lha gsal bar dmigs nas snga ma bzhin mchod cing
NK029(ha)004:4629: bstod nas / bsreg rdzas rnams rdzogs par phul ba'i mthar mar dgang blugs gsum dbul lo //
NK029(ha)004:4632: ag+he ye na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo /
NK029(ha)004:4633: la sogs pa lan gsum gyis phul nas /
NK029(ha)004:4634: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba btab la /
NK029(ha)004:4636: bdag chags las dang po pa'i gang zag du gyur pas /
NK029(ha)004:4639: cho ga 'khrul pa la sogs pa'i nyes pa thams cad bzod par gsol /
NK029(ha)004:4641: dbyu gu gsum pa'i phyag rgya las 'gyed pa'i tshul du bya zhing /
NK029(ha)004:4643: sid d+hi tam g+ha ts+tsha ha bya 'bu ka /
NK029(ha)004:4646: sarba sid+hi ku ru sha me /
NK029(ha)004:4648: me lha'i ye shes pa gshegs su gsol la //
NK029(ha)004:4649: snga ma bzhin dam tshig pa rang la stim //
NK029(ha)004:4651: tsa ru bza' ba la longs spyod //
NK029(ha)004:4655: de ltar bu'i cho ga phun sum tshogs pa'i sbyin bsreg byas pas /
NK029(ha)004:4656: bzlas pa'i lhag chad kyi nyes pa dag par 'gyur zhing /
NK029(ha)004:4657: gsang sbyang gi nyes pa 'dzin pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4658: rang gi lhag pa'i lha gnyes nas mchog dang thun
NK029(ha)004:4659: mongs gi dngos grub bstsol bar 'gyur ba nyid do
NK029(ha)004:4660: // gnyis pa 'jug cing dbang gi rim pa la /
NK029(ha)004:4664: yon tan rnam bcus rgyas shes bya /
NK029(ha)004:4666: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang /
NK029(ha)004:4667: khrus dgab dri dang lus dbul dang /
NK029(ha)004:4668: bgegs bskrad lhar brlab dam tshig sbyin /
NK029(ha)004:4669: de nyid dbog dang chu nan dang /
NK029(ha)004:4670: sgrag dang rin chen dor ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:4671: lha dbab pa dang nan tan dang /
NK029(ha)004:4672: mig dbye dkyir 'khor bstan pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4673: tshogs mchod yon rnams bco brgyad do //'di yis yan lag rdzogs par 'gyur /
NK029(ha)004:4676: dad brtson gsum dang btul zhugs gsum /
NK029(ha)004:4677: gang la snang ba de'i snod /
NK029(ha)004:4680: slob dpon bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang len pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4681: slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)004:4689: dbang phyug gis snyim par me tog gi 'phreng ba thogs ste /
NK029(ha)004:4690: dkyil 'khor kyi shar sgor gus pas 'dug ste /
NK029(ha)004:4691: dkyil 'khor de nyid 'og min gyi gnas rten dang brten par dmigs la /
NK029(ha)004:4694: h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:4695: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK029(ha)004:4696: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa /
NK029(ha)004:4697: zhes rig pa'i me tog dor bas /
NK029(ha)004:4698: sngags brjod pa'i go rim bzhin /
NK029(ha)004:4699: bdag dkyil 'khor kyi lha rnams dang /
NK029(ha)004:4700: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las dbyer med par bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:4701: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK029(ha)004:4702: yon tan 'phrin las smad po che //
NK029(ha)004:4703: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK029(ha)004:4704: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK029(ha)004:4706: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams 'od du zhu nas /
NK029(ha)004:4707: bdag dbang phyug la phog pas /
NK029(ha)004:4708: dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang dgongs pa tha mi dad par mos la /
NK029(ha)004:4712: zhes brjod pas go rim bzhin /
NK029(ha)004:4713: ye shes rdo rje'i dam tshig dus la bab po /
NK029(ha)004:4717: de ltar gnas nas bskul ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:4719: de dag ni bsdus pa'i rim pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:4721: slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa ltar /
NK029(ha)004:4723: zhugs pa'i yon tan dang bcas pas /
NK029(ha)004:4724: phyi nang gi dbang rgyas par blangs zhing 'jug go /
NK029(ha)004:4725: gnyis pa slob dpon gyis 'jug par gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:4726: rdo rje ye shes thob byed pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:4727: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis //
NK029(ha)004:4729: bdag gi slob ma gzhugs par bya //
NK029(ha)004:4731: snyim pa'i me tog dkyil 'khor gyi lha la dor ba'i blos /
NK029(ha)004:4732: dor ba'i tshul byas pas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams
NK029(ha)004:4733: zhal 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis slob bu dkyil 'khor du
NK029(ha)004:4734: chug cing / dbang bco brgyad snod dang 'tsham par bskur bar rigs so //
NK029(ha)004:4735: zhes gnang ba thob par mos la //
NK029(ha)004:4736: me tog 'phreng ba spyi bor bcing ngo //
NK029(ha)004:4737: gnyis pa dbang len pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:4744: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum /
NK029(ha)004:4745: slob ma la ji ltar bskur ba ltar /
NK029(ha)004:4746: slob dpon rang gis kyang dbang legs par len no //
NK029(ha)004:4747: gnyis pa slob ma dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba la gnyis ste /
NK029(ha)004:4748: slob ma dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4766: lha bsgom par nan tan bya ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:4771: slob bu rnams phyir phyung nas /
NK029(ha)004:4772: dri bzang po'i chus khrus byas la /
NK029(ha)004:4773: gos gsar pa dang ldan par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:4775: ma rig pa dang 'dod chags kyi dri mas gnyis med kyi ye shes sgribs so //
NK029(ha)004:4777: ras sam dar dmar po mig dgab cing /
NK029(ha)004:4778: dar la sogs pa las byas pa'i me tog rin po che'am /
NK029(ha)004:4780: dbyar gyi dus su me tog dngos kyang rung ste /
NK029(ha)004:4782: gnas khang gi nang du gus pa dang bcas pa'i tshul gyis 'dug la /
NK029(ha)004:4783: rdor sems gtso bo khyod la 'dud //
NK029(ha)004:4784: thar pa chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK029(ha)004:4785: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK029(ha)004:4786: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song ste //
NK029(ha)004:4787: theg chen khang par gzhugs pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:4788: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la rtsol //
NK029(ha)004:4791: dkyil 'khor du chug cig par gsol ba 'debs par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:4794: bu khyod ci la dga' zhes dris pa'i lan du /
NK029(ha)004:4796: skal ba bzang la bdag daga'o //
NK029(ha)004:4798: dbang phyug gi las mkhan gyis rdo rje phyed /
NK029(ha)004:4799: slob bu rnams kyi lag du sbyin la //
NK029(ha)004:4800: bu khyod tshur shog ci bde ba'i //
NK029(ha)004:4801: las spyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK029(ha)004:4802: sku gsung thugs kyis rdo rje gzung //
NK029(ha)004:4803: rdzogs pa'i ye shes bde chen dang //
NK029(ha)004:4804: dmigs pa med par gnas phyir du //
NK029(ha)004:4805: ser sna spangs pa'i dwangs yid kyis //
NK029(ha)004:4806: stong zhing rang sems brtan par gzung //
NK029(ha)004:4807: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK029(ha)004:4808: zhes dbang phyug gi mdun du slob bu rnams drangs so //
NK029(ha)004:4809: bzhi pa lus dbul ba ni //
NK029(ha)004:4811: spyi bor thal mo sbyar bas /
NK029(ha)004:4812: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis sku gsung thugs dang /
NK029(ha)004:4813: yon tan 'phrin las kyis ye shes thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)004:4814: sangs rgyas rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa rnams la lus phul bar dmigs la /
NK029(ha)004:4815: sarba bud d+ha pu tsa sas+tha na ya ad ma nam nyir+ya ta ya mi /
NK029(ha)004:4816: zhes lan gsum kyang phyag btsal bar bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:4817: yang thal mo smin mtshams su sbyar la /
NK029(ha)004:4818: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ye shes thob pa'i snod du rung bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)004:4819: da ltar gyis sangs rgyas bla ma rnams la lus 'bum bar dmigs la /
NK029(ha)004:4820: +aa tsar+ya p+au tsa sas+tha ya ad ma nam nir+ya ta ya mi /
NK029(ha)004:4822: yang thal mo snying khar sbyar nas /
NK029(ha)004:4823: sems can thams cad kyi don mi dor zhing mthar phyin par bya ba'i don du /
NK029(ha)004:4824: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad la lus phul bar dmigs la /
NK029(ha)004:4825: pa ka la pa ta p+au tsa sas+tha ya ad ma nam /
NK029(ha)004:4827: zhes phyag sngar bzhin btsal lo //
NK029(ha)004:4828: lnga pa tshe mi yal ba bya ba'i phyir bgegs bskrad pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:4829: dbang phyug gi thugs kha'i sa bon las /
NK029(ha)004:4830: yi ge b+h+rum re slob ma rnams kyi dpral bar 'phros /
NK029(ha)004:4831: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud d+he zhes brjod pas /
NK029(ha)004:4832: zla gam dmar po'i gzhal yas khang /
NK029(ha)004:4833: gnam sgo gcig pa khyud can gcig bsgom /
NK029(ha)004:4834: de'i nang du h+aum zhes brjod pas /
NK029(ha)004:4835: slob ma'i tshe'i dngos po thams cad h+aum la bsdu /
NK029(ha)004:4836: badz+ra h+aum ka ra h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:4838: h+aum ka ra sngon po tshe'i bum pa bsnams pa cig du bsam /
NK029(ha)004:4839: zla gam gyi gnam sgo la /
NK029(ha)004:4840: badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa la h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:4842: khro bo mi g.yo ba ljang nag ral gri dang /
NK029(ha)004:4843: bsdig 'dzub can bskyed nas sgo bsrungs bar bsam nas /
NK029(ha)004:4844: yi dam lha'i nga rgyal gyis bi sh+aa badz+ra'i sngags kyis sprul pas spro /
NK029(ha)004:4845: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK029(ha)004:4846: 'dir 'dus pa'i slob bu rnams la gnod cing 'tshe
NK029(ha)004:4847: ba'i 'byung po thams cad 'dir ma gnas par dengs
NK029(ha)004:4848: byer cig / sum b+ha ni sum+b+ha ni h+aum zhes lan gsum gyis bskrad de /
NK029(ha)004:4849: drug pa lhar brlabs pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:4850: rdo rje slob dpon gyis lag pa g.yas kyi sor
NK029(ha)004:4851: mo'i bre kha lnga la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la
NK029(ha)004:4852: gnas pa'i dpa' bo 'bru lnga dang /
NK029(ha)004:4853: g.yon gyis sor mo'i bre kha lnga la gnas pa'i dpa' mo 'bru lnga bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:4855: zhes dpa' bo dpa' mo sbyar /
NK029(ha)004:4857: badz+ra b+han d+ha zhes phyag rgya bsdam /
NK029(ha)004:4858: bden pa brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK029(ha)004:4859: slob bu 'di rnams kyi rgyud la yod pa'i las kyi sgrib pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4860: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4861: lta ba dman pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4862: chos kyis 'phongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4863: bag chags ngan pa'i sgrib pa la sogs te /
NK029(ha)004:4864: sgrib pa'i phung po ji rnyed pa thams cad phyag rgya'i 'od zer 'dis bral ba gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:4866: zhes pa'i sngags mang du brjod cing /
NK029(ha)004:4867: phyag rgya spros pas 'bru bcu rigs lnga yab yum du gyur pa sbyor ba mdzad pas /
NK029(ha)004:4868: byang chub kyi sems su zhu ba'i 'od zer gyis /
NK029(ha)004:4869: slob bu rnams kyi sgrib pa mtha' dag bsreg shing /
NK029(ha)004:4870: h+aum ka ra dang mi g.yo ba gnyis yang 'od du zhu nas /
NK029(ha)004:4871: slob bu rnams kyi rnam shes dang ga cig tu gyur ste /
NK029(ha)004:4872: dngul chu zhun ma lta bur gnas de /
NK029(ha)004:4873: cho ga gsum gyis rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog
NK029(ha)004:4874: dkar po brgyan cha lugs dang ldan par bskyed la
NK029(ha)004:4875: / shu nya ta la sogs pa'i sngags kyis dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)004:4876: gnas gsum du rdo rje gtug cing /
NK029(ha)004:4878: byin gyis brlabs par bsgoms la /
NK029(ha)004:4879: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra la sogs pa brjod /
NK029(ha)004:4880: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rtags su /
NK029(ha)004:4881: dpral bar sku yis lha snang mdzad dkar po /
NK029(ha)004:4882: 'khor lo dkar po gyis mtshan pa 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:4883: de bzhin du mgrin pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4884: snying khar gsung thugs kyi lha 'dra'o //
NK029(ha)004:4885: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgyas /
NK029(ha)004:4886: badz+ra ka wa tsi rak+sha rak+sha zhes rdo rje'i go khrab dkon /
NK029(ha)004:4887: rdo rje bsrungs pa'i phyag rgya dang /
NK029(ha)004:4888: trum gi rdo rje gnod sbyin dang /
NK029(ha)004:4889: khro bo mi 'chi thal sbyor gnyis kyis lus gyi gnas drug bsrungs par bsgom mo //
NK029(ha)004:4890: bdun pa dam tshig sbyin pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:4892: a la la ste mchod par 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:4893: a la la ste mnyes par mdzod /
NK029(ha)004:4894: a la la ste dam tshig bskongs /
NK029(ha)004:4895: a la la ste dngos grub stsol /
NK029(ha)004:4896: dpal ldan rdo rje sku 'chang ba /
NK029(ha)004:4897: mi phyed rdo rje sku rang bzhin /
NK029(ha)004:4898: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni /
NK029(ha)004:4899: rdo rje'i sku ru mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)004:4901: dbang phyug gis b+han+d+ha bdud rtsi cung zad blug la /
NK029(ha)004:4902: +aah h+aum zhes brjod cing sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin yig 'bru gsum gsal bar bsgom la /
NK029(ha)004:4903: badz+ra a mri ta h'u hrihth+aah zhes pa'i sngags lan gsum gyi bdud rtsi chur byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK029(ha)004:4904: dbang phyug gi phyag g.yas pa rdo rje dang bcas pa'i srin lag gi bdud rtsi blangs la /
NK029(ha)004:4905: slob bu rnams kyi dpral bar zhes brjod cing thig le byas la dkar po bsam /
NK029(ha)004:4906: de las 'od zer dkar po 'phros pas /
NK029(ha)004:4907: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis sku yi byin brlabs bsdus nas /
NK029(ha)004:4908: dpral bar la thim par bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:4909: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka ya badz+ra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:4910: zhes brjod cing byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK029(ha)004:4911: slob bu dam tshig thob par bsam /
NK029(ha)004:4913: dpal ldan rdo rje gsung 'chang ba /
NK029(ha)004:4914: mi phyed rdo rje gsung rang bzhin /
NK029(ha)004:4915: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni /
NK029(ha)004:4916: rdo rje gsung du mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)004:4918: slob bu'i mgrin par thig le byas pa'i +aah yis 'phro 'dus /
NK029(ha)004:4919: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+ha
NK029(ha)004:4920: wa ata ma ko&a hamh sngags kyis gsung gi dam
NK029(ha)004:4923: dpal ldan rdo rje thugs 'chang ba /
NK029(ha)004:4924: mi phyed rdo rje'i thugs rang bzhin //
NK029(ha)004:4925: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas ni /
NK029(ha)004:4926: rdo rje'i thugs su mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)004:4928: slob bu'i snying khar thig le byas pa'i /
NK029(ha)004:4930: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+ha wa
NK029(ha)004:4931: ata ma ko&a hamh kyis thugs kyi dam tshig thob
NK029(ha)004:4932: par bsam mo // brgyad pa dam tshig 'bog pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:4933: dbang phyug gi slob bu'i snying khar rdo rje bzhag la /
NK029(ha)004:4934: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:4935: dam nyams ma 'dres med pa la //
NK029(ha)004:4936: nam yang smra bar ma byed cig /
NK029(ha)004:4937: theg pa chen po ston byed pa'i //
NK029(ha)004:4938: nga la brnyas dang smad mi rung //
NK029(ha)004:4939: sku gsung thugs la rtags gnas shing //
NK029(ha)004:4940: ma lus sems can don gyis shig ces bago'o //
NK029(ha)004:4941: dgu pa chu nan bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:4942: tsan dan dkar dmar sbyar ba'i chu la /
NK029(ha)004:4943: cho ga gsum gyis rdo rje sems par bskyed cing /
NK029(ha)004:4945: bdud rtsir zhu bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:4946: thog mar skyon gyi sgo nas /
NK029(ha)004:4948: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK029(ha)004:4949: dam tshig nyams na bsreg par byed //
NK029(ha)004:4950: rdo rje'i ni gtung bar gyis /
NK029(ha)004:4954: slob bu'i lce la lan gsum bzhag go /
NK029(ha)004:4955: yon tan gyi sgo nas chu nan bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:4956: de bas na bu khyod kyis /
NK029(ha)004:4957: dam tshig 'di dag srungs bar gyis //
NK029(ha)004:4958: dam tshig bsrungs na dngos grub thob //
NK029(ha)004:4959: rdo rje bdud rtsi'i chu 'thungs shig /
NK029(ha)004:4963: lan gsum slob bu'i lce la bzhag go /
NK029(ha)004:4964: slob bu kun la chu nan zin rjes thog tu //'di skad do //
NK029(ha)004:4965: de ltar bdud rtsi'i chu de /
NK029(ha)004:4966: bzhag pa lce la bzhag kyang /
NK029(ha)004:4967: bab pa snying gi dkyil du babs nas /
NK029(ha)004:4968: gal ste dam tshig ma bsrungs na /
NK029(ha)004:4969: chu de rdo rje gnod sbyin zhes bya ba /
NK029(ha)004:4970: lcags kyi sdig pa mgo dgu par gyur nas /
NK029(ha)004:4972: tshe thung zhing nad mang ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:4973: tshe phyi mar dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gyis nyams thag par 'gyur ro //
NK029(ha)004:4974: dam tshig bsrungs na chu de rdo rje sems dpar gyur nas /
NK029(ha)004:4975: des rtag tu byin gyis brlab cing /
NK029(ha)004:4978: nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)004:4979: gdon stong phrag brgyad bcus mi tshugs pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:4980: phyi mar bla na med pa'i byang chub thob nas /
NK029(ha)004:4981: sems can thams cad mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las
NK029(ha)004:4982: 'das pa'i gnas su 'dren pa'i ded dpon byed par
NK029(ha)004:4984: bcu pa dam bsgrags pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:4985: dbang phyug gi phyag g.yas pa rdo rje dang bcas pa gcig /
NK029(ha)004:4986: slob bu rnams kyi spyi bor bzhag la /
NK029(ha)004:4987: thabs dang shes rab sems nyid kyis //
NK029(ha)004:4988: rtag tu dgos pa med bgyis la //'dod pa lnga'i yon tan spyod //
NK029(ha)004:4989: gzhan yang stong khams thams cad na //
NK029(ha)004:4990: shes rab dbyings dang 'dod don gzhan //
NK029(ha)004:4991: rab 'bring tha mas thams cad spyod //
NK029(ha)004:4992: gzhan yang dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:4993: skye bo gang zhig dam la gnod //
NK029(ha)004:4994: brtul zhugs can gyis de drongs la //
NK029(ha)004:4995: khrag chen snying la btung bar bgyis //'di la mi bya cung zad med //
NK029(ha)004:4996: sems nyid theg par rab nges nas //
NK029(ha)004:4997: nyon mongs 'dod lnga kun spyod kyang //
NK029(ha)004:4999: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK029(ha)004:5000: bya dang mi bya cung zad med //
NK029(ha)004:5002: bcu gcig rin chen dor ba ni /
