NK029(ha)004:6574: brgyad pa dbang thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)004:6576: de dag ni tshom bu gsum pa'i phyag rgya'i dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)004:6577: bzhi pa tshom bu lnga pa'i dbang la /
NK029(ha)004:6579: 'bras bu go rims lnga gong dang mtshungs la /
NK029(ha)004:6582: rtogs tshogs thams cad ma spangs gnas su dag par bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:6584: gong gi dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i rigs lnga yab yum bcu la /
NK029(ha)004:6585: rang gi rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad
NK029(ha)004:6586: brgyad kyis bskor bas pho brang gi lha lnga bcu
NK029(ha)004:6588: khro bo yab yum nyi shu'i bsgrag tshig ni /
NK029(ha)004:6591: khro rgyal khrag 'thung yab yum sku //
NK029(ha)004:6592: steng gi phyogs nas bgegs byung ba //
NK029(ha)004:6593: nyi zla'i gdon tshogs thams cad kun //
NK029(ha)004:6594: h+aum chen ka ra nyi kyis bzlog /
NK029(ha)004:6595: badz+ra kro ta h+aum ka ra h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:6597: khrag 'thung kun gyi dbyug pa'i dbang //
NK029(ha)004:6598: khro rgyal khrag 'thung yab yum sku //
NK029(ha)004:6599: shar gyi phyogs nas bgegs byung ba //
NK029(ha)004:6600: dri za'i gdon tshogs thams cad kun //
NK029(ha)004:6601: rnams par rgyal ba nyid kyis bzlog /
NK029(ha)004:6602: badz+ra kro ta bi dza ya h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:6604: h+aum khrag 'thung kun gyi dbyug pa'i dbang /
NK029(ha)004:6605: khro rgyal khro 'thung yab yum sku //
NK029(ha)004:6606: shar lho'i phyogs nas bgegs byung ba //
NK029(ha)004:6607: drang srong gdon tshogs thams cad kun //
NK029(ha)004:6608: dbyug pa sngon po rnams kyis bzlog /
NK029(ha)004:6609: badz+ra kro d+ha ni la dan tra h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:6612: khrag 'thung kun gyi be con dbang //
NK029(ha)004:6613: khro rgyal khrag 'thung yab yum sku //
NK029(ha)004:6614: lho'i phyogs nas bgegs byung ba //
NK029(ha)004:6615: grul bum gdon tshogs thams cad kun //
NK029(ha)004:6616: gshin rje gshed po nyid kyis bzlog /
NK029(ha)004:6617: badz+ra kro d+ha ya man ta ka h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:6620: khrag 'thung kun gyi spu gri'i dbang //
NK029(ha)004:6621: khro rgyal khrag 'thung yab yum sku //
NK029(ha)004:6622: lho nub 'tshams nas bgegs byung ba //
NK029(ha)004:6623: srin po'i gdon tshogs thams cad kun //
NK029(ha)004:6624: mi g.yo mgon po nyid kyi bzlog /
NK029(ha)004:6625: badz+ra kro d+ha ar+ya a tsa la h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:6627: h+aum khrag 'thung kun gyi ral gri'i dbang //
NK029(ha)004:6628: khro rgyal khrag 'thung yab yum sku //
NK029(ha)004:6629: nub kyi phyogs nas bgegs byung ba //
NK029(ha)004:6630: klu yi gdon tshogs thams cad kun //
NK029(ha)004:6631: rta mgrin rgyal po nyid kyis bzlog /
NK029(ha)004:6632: badz+ra kro ta ha ya g+hi ba h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:6634: h+aum khrag 'thung kun gyi b+han+ha'i dbang //
NK029(ha)004:6635: khro rgyal khrag 'thung yab yum sku //
NK029(ha)004:6636: nub byang 'tshams nas bgegs byung ba /
NK029(ha)004:6637: rlung lha'i gdon tshogs thams cad kun //
NK029(ha)004:6638: gzhan gyis mi thub nyid kyi bzlog /
NK029(ha)004:6639: badz+ra kro ta a pa r+aa tsi ta h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:6641: h+aum khrag 'thung kun gyis rgya gram dbang //
NK029(ha)004:6642: khro rgyal khrag 'thung yab yum sku //
NK029(ha)004:6643: byang gi phyogs nas bgegs byung ba //
NK029(ha)004:6644: gnod sbyin gdon tshogs thams cad kun //
NK029(ha)004:6645: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa nyid kyis bzlog /
NK029(ha)004:6646: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+ta li h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:6648: h+aum khrag 'thung kun gyi 'khor lo'i dbang //
NK029(ha)004:6649: khro rgyal khrag 'thung yab yum sku //
NK029(ha)004:6650: byang shar 'tshams nas bgegs byung ba //
NK029(ha)004:6651: dbang ldan gdon tshogs thams cad kun /
NK029(ha)004:6652: khams gsum rnams rgyal nyid kyis bzlog /
NK029(ha)004:6653: badz+ra kro ta tree lo kya bi dza ya h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:6655: h+aum khrag 'thung kun gyi tho ba'i dbang //
NK029(ha)004:6656: khro rgyal khrag 'thung yab yum sku //'og gi phyogs nas bgegs byung ba //
NK029(ha)004:6657: sa bdag gdon tshogs thams cad kun //
NK029(ha)004:6658: stobs chen rgyal po nyid kyis bzlog /
NK029(ha)004:6659: badz+ra kro ta ma h+aa ba la h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:6665: rtog tshogs rang la lha tshogs rnams stim mo //
NK029(ha)004:6666: bdun pa phyag rgya'i dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK029(ha)004:6667: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK029(ha)004:6668: dbang rnams thob par ma byas na //
NK029(ha)004:6669: nyan pa la sogs rtsoms pa rnams //'bras bu med cing brlag par 'gyur //
NK029(ha)004:6671: brgyad pa dbang thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)004:6672: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK029(ha)004:6673: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:6674: tshe ring bde ba phun sum 'tshogs //
NK029(ha)004:6675: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK029(ha)004:6677: de dag ni tshom bu lnga pa'i phyag rgya'i dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)004:6678: phyis phan pa'i dbang bcu'i las kyi rim pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:6679: phyi lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)004:6680: de yang phan dbang bcu po thob pas /
NK029(ha)004:6681: skye ba 'dir tshe ring ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:6682: bde ba phun sum 'tshogs pa thob pa la phan /
NK029(ha)004:6683: phyi mar mtho ris dang thar pa thob pa la
NK029(ha)004:6684: phan pa'i phyir phan pa'i dbang zhes tha snyad du
NK029(ha)004:6685: bya'o // gnyis pa nang nus pa'i dbang la lnga ste /
NK029(ha)004:6686: bdag don du brtson 'grus nus pa la nyan dbang dang /
NK029(ha)004:6688: gzhan don du brtson 'grus nus pa la /
NK029(ha)004:6691: bdag gzhan gnyis kyi don du brtson 'grus nus pa
NK029(ha)004:6692: la rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang
NK029(ha)004:6693: ngo // dang po la brgyad de /
NK029(ha)004:6700: nyan dbang ma thob pa'i skyon dang /
NK029(ha)004:6702: dang po rgyu la mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:6703: slob bu rna ba gnyis 'dom rtsa na /
NK029(ha)004:6704: sgra nyan pa thos shes reg shes kyi thig le gnas pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:6705: gnyis pa lhan gcig byeed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:6706: ka p+aa la rin chen 'byung ldan gyi rab gnas can no //
NK029(ha)004:6709: dbang bskur du rung ba'i slob bu ste /
NK029(ha)004:6710: mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)004:6711: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:6712: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:6713: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:6714: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:6715: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:6716: bzhi pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:6717: dbang snga ma phan dbang gi go phyes nas /
NK029(ha)004:6718: phyi ma nyan dbang skye ba'i rgyu byed pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:6722: nus pa dngos su ba skyed de /
NK029(ha)004:6723: rno la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)004:6725: phan dbang bcu'i rjes su nyan dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)004:6726: drug pa las rim lnga las /
NK029(ha)004:6728: dbang phyug kun bzang yab yum du sgom pa'i sbyor 'tshams nas /
NK029(ha)004:6730: slob bu rnams kyi rna ba gnyis kyi 'dom rtsar 'phros pa las /
NK029(ha)004:6731: gzhal yas khang dbus 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:6732: gru chad la sgo khyud can /
NK029(ha)004:6733: 'khor lo'i lte ba dang rtsibs bzhi la nyi zla
NK029(ha)004:6734: pad+ma sum rtsegs kyi gdan re re dang sgo khyud
NK029(ha)004:6735: bzhi la nyi ma'i gdan re re bsgom /
NK029(ha)004:6736: gdan sum rtsegs lnga'i steng du /
NK029(ha)004:6737: dbang phyug gi thugs kha nas tram ser po zung re re dang /
NK029(ha)004:6738: sgo bzhir nyi gdan la shar sgor h'u dzah lho sgor h'u h'u /
NK029(ha)004:6740: byang sgor h'u hoh 'phros par bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:6741: tram tram tram tram tram tram tram tram tram tram /
NK029(ha)004:6746: yig 'bru rnams 'od du zhu ba las /
NK029(ha)004:6747: 'khor lo'i lte ba'i gdan la rin po che dang /
NK029(ha)004:6749: shar rtsibs la rin chen myu gu dang phreng ba /
NK029(ha)004:6750: lhor nyi ma dang me tog /
NK029(ha)004:6751: nub tu rgyal mtshan dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)004:6752: byang du so'i phreng ba dang bsil yab /
NK029(ha)004:6753: shar sgor thod dbyug dang lcags kyu /
NK029(ha)004:6754: lho sgo ra rdo rje rtse lnga dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)004:6755: nub sgor thod sprul dang lcags sgrogs /
NK029(ha)004:6756: byang sgor sna tshogs rdo rje dang dril bu rnams bsam /
NK029(ha)004:6763: badz+ra pa sha k+aa pa la sh+r+ai kha /
NK029(ha)004:6766: spar sang gis 'phro 'dus 'od du zhu ba las go rims bzhin du /
NK029(ha)004:6767: badz+ra rat+na tram sam b+ha wa tram /
NK029(ha)004:6768: lte ba'i 'od phung yongs su gyur pa las /
NK029(ha)004:6770: yab kyi phyag g.yas pas rin po che dang /
NK029(ha)004:6771: g.yon dril bu 'dzin cing yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:6772: yum gyi g.yon phyogs nas g.yas pa dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:6775: shar rtsibs la rdo rje rin chen ni /
NK029(ha)004:6776: rin chen myu gu bsnams pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:6777: phreng ba mas phreng ba bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:6781: rdo rje gzi brjid nyi ma bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:6782: me tog ma me tog bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6786: rdo rje rgyal mtshan bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6787: zhags pa ma zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6791: rdo rje bzhad pa tshes kyi phreng ba bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:6792: rdo rje bsil ma bsil yab bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6793: de ltar gtso 'khor yab yum thams cad kyang /
NK029(ha)004:6794: sku mdog gser gtso ma lta bu zhi ba'i tshul dang ldan pa /
NK029(ha)004:6795: brgyan chas bcu gnyis brgyan pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:6796: dbus kyi gtso bo rdo rje dkyil dkrung /
NK029(ha)004:6798: yum rnams kyi g.yon zur nas 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:6799: ya man ta krid h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)004:6800: badz+ra a ng+gu sha dzahshara sgor gshin rje smug nag be con /
NK029(ha)004:6801: rdo rje lcags kyu ma sngon mo lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6804: lho sgor stobs po che ser nag rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6805: rdo rje zhags pa ma ser mo zhag pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6808: nub sgor rta mgrin dmar nag /
NK029(ha)004:6809: thod pa sbrul gyis dkris pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6810: rdo rje lcags sgrog ma dmar mo lcags sgrog /
NK029(ha)004:6811: big nan ta kri ta h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:6814: ljang nag sna tshogs rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6815: rdo rje dril bu ma ljang khu dril bu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6816: sgo ba yab yum brgyad po thams cad kyang nyi
NK029(ha)004:6817: ma'i gdan la zhal phyir phyogs pa yab g.yon brkyang
NK029(ha)004:6818: dang / yum g.yas brkyang gis gyad kyi dor thabs kyis bsgrad pa /
NK029(ha)004:6819: khro bo'i chas kyis brgyan pa /
NK029(ha)004:6820: me phung gi klong na bzhugs pa bskyed do //
NK029(ha)004:6821: tshul 'di dag ni 'chad par 'gyur ba'i sgom pa'i
NK029(ha)004:6822: dbang la sogs lha bskyed pa thams cad la shes
NK029(ha)004:6823: par bya'o // de ltar bskyed pa'i dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor gyi lha bco brgyad pa la /
NK029(ha)004:6825: k+aa ya w+aak+ka tsit+ta byin gyis brlabs /
NK029(ha)004:6826: rang bzhin gyi gnas nas ye shes kyi lha bac+wa brgyad po /
NK029(ha)004:6827: sa ma ya dzas snyan gsan dbab /
NK029(ha)004:6828: e h+ya hi spyan drangs dzahh+aum bam hos stim /
NK029(ha)004:6829: k+aa ya wa k+aa tsi tas brtan par byas nas /
NK029(ha)004:6830: kun bzang zhal bsil bzhi bsnol gyis sngags rang gis mchod nas sa ma ya ho /
NK029(ha)004:6832: zhes sbyor ba'i brdas bskul nas snyoms par zhugs lha
NK029(ha)004:6833: yab yum slob bu dang bcas pa rjes chags kyi
NK029(ha)004:6835: 'od phung seng po las rin chen 'byung ldan du bskyed la /
NK029(ha)004:6836: dbang phyug gi rgyud kyi po ti'am ka p+aa la
NK029(ha)004:6837: rin chen 'byung ldan gyi rab gnas dang ldan pa
NK029(ha)004:6838: bsnams la / gnyis pa bsgrag tshig ni /
NK029(ha)004:6839: tram gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gi /
NK029(ha)004:6840: gsang ba kun la nyan pa pya /
NK029(ha)004:6841: gsang ba'i don nyid rtag pa la /
NK029(ha)004:6842: gzhan la smra bar bya ba min /
NK029(ha)004:6844: gsum pa bskur gnas slob bu'i lag par dbang rdzas gtad /
NK029(ha)004:6846: sgra reg byed nyan shes kyi thig le la ba stim /
NK029(ha)004:6847: lnga pa sngon chad bka' phyi nang gi don la
NK029(ha)004:6848: thog pa med par mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag
NK029(ha)004:6849: nas / da phyin chad nyan nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skye bar bsgom la /
NK029(ha)004:6851: rigs kyi bu 'di rnams la nyan pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)004:6852: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' phyi nang thams cad la
NK029(ha)004:6853: thogs pa med par nyan nus pa'i dbang dam pa
NK029(ha)004:6855: bdun pa dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK029(ha)004:6856: nyan dbang ma thob na nyan pa rtsom pa la sogs 'bras bu med cing brlag pa'i skyon no //
NK029(ha)004:6858: nyan pa la dbang 'byor pa'i yon tan yod do //
NK029(ha)004:6859: gnyis pa bsgom dbang la brgyad de /
NK029(ha)004:6860: rgyu rkyen ngo bo 'bras bu go rim las rim skyon yon tan no //
NK029(ha)004:6861: dang po la mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:6862: snying gi 'dom rtsa dran byed reg shes kyi thig le'o //
NK029(ha)004:6863: gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:6865: yi dam gang yin gyi rab gnas can no //
NK029(ha)004:6868: dbang bskur du rung ba'i skyes bu de /
NK029(ha)004:6869: mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)004:6870: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:6871: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:6872: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:6873: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:6874: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma ste /
NK029(ha)004:6875: yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:6876: bzhi pa de ma thag rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:6877: nyan dbang gi go phyes nas bsgom dbang thob ma rag pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:6881: nus pa dngos su bskyed pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:6882: rno la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)004:6884: nyan dbang gi rjes su bsgom dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)004:6885: drug pa las rim la lnga las /
NK029(ha)004:6887: dbang phyug kun bzang yab yum du bsgom pa'i sbyor 'tshams nas /
NK029(ha)004:6888: yi dam gang yin gyi kha dog can gyi b+h+rum chad de /
NK029(ha)004:6889: slob bu rnams kyi snying gi 'doms rtsar 'phros pa las /
NK029(ha)004:6890: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa sngar bzhin bskyed la /
NK029(ha)004:6891: cho ga gsum gyis lha bac+wa brgyad bskyed de /
NK029(ha)004:6892: slob bus me tog dor ba'i dus su rin po che'i rigs la me tog phog na /
NK029(ha)004:6893: rin chen 'byung ldan gyis gtso byas pa'i lha bac+wa brgyad po /
NK029(ha)004:6894: bshad ma thag pa'i nyan dbang gi skabs ltar bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:6895: gal te pad+ma'i rigs la phog nas /
NK029(ha)004:6896: snang ba mtha' yas kyi gtso byas pa'i lha bac+wa brgyad po /
NK029(ha)004:6897: 'chad par 'gyur ba'i 'chad dbang gi skabs ltar bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:6898: de bzhin du las kyi rigs la me tog phog na /
NK029(ha)004:6899: don yod grub pas gtso byas pa'i lha bac+wa brgyad 'phrin las kyi skabs ltar bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:6900: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la me tog phog na
NK029(ha)004:6901: rnam par snang mdzad kyis gtso byas pa'i lha bac+wa
NK029(ha)004:6902: brgyad bskyed do // dbang phyug gi thugs kha nas
NK029(ha)004:6903: dbus kyi 'khor lo la dkar po zung lnga dang
NK029(ha)004:6904: brgyad bskyed do // / sgo khyud bzhi la /
NK029(ha)004:6905: h+aum dzahh+aum h+aum h+aum bamhh+aum hoh rnams spros la s+pha
NK029(ha)004:6906: ra sang gi spro bsdus 'od du zhu ba las
NK029(ha)004:6907: / dbus kyi lte ba nas go rim bzhin 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:6913: rdo rje rtse lnga dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)004:6915: sna tshogs rdo rje dang dril bu rnams su gyur par bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:6926: slar spar sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)004:6927: phyag mtshan rnams go rim ltar /
NK029(ha)004:6931: rnam par snang mdzad 'khor lo bsnams pa la /
NK029(ha)004:6932: sangs rgyas spyan ma dril bu bsnams pas 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:6935: rdo rje sems dpa' dang sgeg mo ma me long bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6938: rdo rje rgyal po lcags kyu dang /
NK029(ha)004:6939: spos me ma spos khang bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6942: rdo rje chags pa 'da' gzhu dang /
NK029(ha)004:6943: rdo rje skyo kha ma lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6946: rdo rje legs pa se gol brdebs pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:6947: rdo rje gsal bkra ma sgron le bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6948: yab yum bcu po thams cad kyang sku mdog dkar po rgyan tshul dang ldan par bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:6949: ya man ta kri ta h'u /
NK029(ha)004:6957: zhes sgo ba yab yum brgyad po bskyed do //
NK029(ha)004:6958: sku mdog phyag mtshan rigs gang yin kyang kun mthun ste sngar nyan dbang du bshad pa bzhin no //
NK029(ha)004:6959: de bzhin du mgo ma la /
NK029(ha)004:6960: yang me tog rdo rje'i rigs la phog pa'i slob
NK029(ha)004:6961: ma rnams la mi skyod pas gtso byas pa'i lha
NK029(ha)004:6963: 'khor lo'i lte ba rtsibs dang ldan pa las /
NK029(ha)004:6965: sgo bzhi la h+aum dzahh+aum h+aum h+aum bam h+aum ho
NK029(ha)004:6966: rnams 'phros pa s+phar sang gi spro bsdus 'od du
NK029(ha)004:6967: zhu ba las / phyag mtshan du gyur par bsgom ste /
NK029(ha)004:6971: rin po che dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:6975: rdo rje rtse lnga dang zhags pa /
NK029(ha)004:6977: sna tshogs rdo rje dang dril bu rnams bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:6978: s+phar sang gi 'phro 'dus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK029(ha)004:6980: badz+ra d+ha ri shwa ra h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:6981: mi skyod pa rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6982: chos kyi dbyings phyug mas dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:6985: sems dpa' rdo rje 'khor lo bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:6986: brtan ma rdo rje dril bu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6990: rin chen rdo rje rin po che bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6991: 'bar ma rdo rje dril bu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6994: chos rdo rje pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:6995: sdud ma rdo rje dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:6998: las kyi rdo rje ral gri bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:6999: bskyod ma rdo rje dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:7000: de ltar yum lnga char dril bu bsnams nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:7001: yab yum bcu kha sku mdog mthing kha /
NK029(ha)004:7002: brgyan tshul dang ldan par bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7003: de ltar mi bskyod pas gtso byas pa'i lha bac+wa brgyad po dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed la /
NK029(ha)004:7006: ye shes pa snyan gsan dbab drangs bstim brtan /
NK029(ha)004:7007: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK029(ha)004:7008: sbyor ba'i brdas bskul ba la sogs pa sngar bzhin bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:7009: mdor na rang gi yi dam gang yin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed la /
NK029(ha)004:7011: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sras chen po /
NK029(ha)004:7012: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bzung /
NK029(ha)004:7013: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mchod la /
NK029(ha)004:7014: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor /
NK029(ha)004:7019: snying gi 'dom rtsar dran byed rtog shes kyi thig le la stim /
NK029(ha)004:7020: lnga pa sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye ni /
NK029(ha)004:7021: sngar phan chad lha rtog dbyer med bsgom mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)004:7022: da bsgom nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skye bar bsgom la /
NK029(ha)004:7025: lha dang mi rtog pa thams cad la thogs pa
NK029(ha)004:7026: med pa'i ting nge 'dzin sgom pa'i dbang dam pa
NK029(ha)004:7027: thob par gyur cig bdun pa ma thob pa'i skyon
NK029(ha)004:7028: ni / bskyed rdzogs sgom mi nus pa la sogs pa'i skyon yod do //
NK029(ha)004:7030: nyan bsgom mthar phyin mngon du gyur pa'i yon tan yod do //
NK029(ha)004:7031: gsum pa 'phrin las kyi dbang la brgyad kyi dang po la rgyu la mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:7032: lag pa gnyis gyi 'dom rtsa'i bskyod byed reg shes kyi thig le'o //
NK029(ha)004:7033: gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:7034: rgya gram don grub gyi rab gnas can no //
NK029(ha)004:7035: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi'i dang po rgyu'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7036: dbang bskur du rung pa'i slob bu ste /
NK029(ha)004:7037: mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)004:7038: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7039: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7040: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7041: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7042: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o /
NK029(ha)004:7043: bzhi pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7044: sgom dbang thob pas go phyes nas /
NK029(ha)004:7045: 'phrin las kyi dbang thob la ma rag pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7049: nus pa dngos su bskyed pa ste rno la ngar rtags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)004:7051: bsgom dbang gi rjes su 'phrin las kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)004:7052: drug pa las rim pa lnga'i bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)004:7053: dbang phyug yab yum kun bzang yab yum du bskyed
NK029(ha)004:7054: pa'i sbyor 'tshams nas b+h+rum ljang khu slob bu'i lag
NK029(ha)004:7055: pa gnyis kyis 'doms rtsar 'phros pa las /
NK029(ha)004:7056: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa sngar bzhin bskyed la /
NK029(ha)004:7060: h+aum dzahh+aum h+aum h+aum bamhh+aum ho /
NK029(ha)004:7062: s+pha ra sang gi spro bsdus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK029(ha)004:7069: badz+ra p+aa sha ka p+aa la /
NK029(ha)004:7073: rdo rje rgya gram dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:7074: ral gri dang gar gyi phu dung /
NK029(ha)004:7075: rdo rje'i go cha dang dung chos /
NK029(ha)004:7076: phag rgod kyi mche ba dang dril bu /
NK029(ha)004:7077: khu tshur dang lha'i nam bzar gyur pa /
NK029(ha)004:7078: s+phar sang gi spro bsdus sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed do //
NK029(ha)004:7079: badz+ra a mo ka sid+hi a /
NK029(ha)004:7080: badz+ra ta re ye ha zhes pas /
NK029(ha)004:7081: don yod grub pa rgya gram bsnams pa la /
NK029(ha)004:7082: sgrol ma dril bu bsnams pas 'khyud pa /
NK029(ha)004:7085: rdo rje las ral gri ba snams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7086: rdo rje gar ma gar bsgyur ba /
NK029(ha)004:7089: rdo rje bsrung ba go cha bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7090: rdo rje dbyug pa ma dri'i dung chos bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7093: rdo rje gnod sbyin phag rgod kyi mche ba bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7094: rdo rje dril bu ma dril bu bsnams pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7097: rdo rje khur tshul khu tshur bcangs pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7098: rdo rje gnod sbyin rma bya'i sgro rgya gram bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7099: yab yum bcu kha yang sku ma dog ljang khu rgyan tshul dang ldan par bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7108: zhes sgo khyud bzhi la sgo ba yab yum sku mdog phyag mtshan sngar bzhin bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7109: de ltar bskyed pa'i dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor la /
NK029(ha)004:7117: bzhi bsnol gyis mchod sbyor ba'i brdas bskul bas snyoms par zhugs pa'i bde bas /
NK029(ha)004:7118: lha bac+wa brgyad slob bu dang bcas pa 'od du zhu ba las don yod grub par bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:7120: khyod ni rdo rje las yin gyis /
NK029(ha)004:7121: las rnams ma lus khyod kyis byos /
NK029(ha)004:7123: khyod kyi dgongs pa byed pa yin /
NK029(ha)004:7125: bskur gnas ni lag par dbang rdzas rgya gram gtad /
NK029(ha)004:7127: lag pa gnyis 'dom rtsa'i skyod byed kyi thig le la stim /
NK029(ha)004:7128: lnga pa ni sngon chad 'phrin las bzhis 'dul ma
NK029(ha)004:7129: nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skye bar bsam zhing
NK029(ha)004:7132: 'phrin las rnam bzhis srid pa gsum sems can ma
NK029(ha)004:7133: lus pa'i don ji lta ba 'dul ba bzhin byed
NK029(ha)004:7134: pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:7138: bzhi pa 'chad dbang la brgyad kyi dang po rgyu
NK029(ha)004:7139: la gnyis kyi dang po mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni
NK029(ha)004:7140: / lce'i 'dom rtsa myong byed reg shes kyi thig le'o //
NK029(ha)004:7141: gnyis pa lhan cig pa byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:7142: dung chag shing 'khor lo gsum mtha' yas kyi rab gnas can no //
NK029(ha)004:7143: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi'i dang po rgyu'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7144: dbang bskur du rung pa'i skyes bu ste /
NK029(ha)004:7145: mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)004:7146: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7147: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7148: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7149: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7150: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7151: bzhi pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7152: 'phrin las kyi dbang thob pas go phyes nas /
NK029(ha)004:7157: nus pa dngos su ba skyed pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:7158: rno mtshon la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)004:7160: 'phrin las kyi dbang gi rjes su 'chad dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)004:7162: drug gi dang po bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)004:7163: dbang phyug kun bzang yab yum du gsal ba'i sbyor
NK029(ha)004:7164: 'tshams nas b+h+rum slob bu'i lce'i steng du 'phros pas
NK029(ha)004:7165: / gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa sngar bzhin gsal la /
NK029(ha)004:7166: 'khor lo la gdan gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)004:7168: sgo khyud la h+aum dzahhum h+aum h+aum bo h+aum ho /
NK029(ha)004:7169: s+pha ra sang gi spro bsdus 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las /
NK029(ha)004:7173: tsakra po ta bak+sha ko ke pa /
NK029(ha)004:7175: badz+ra pa sha ka pa la sh+ri kha la /
NK029(ha)004:7181: 'khor lo dang lcags sgrog rnams bskyed la s+phar sang
NK029(ha)004:7182: gi spro bsdus 'khor lo'i lte ba la snang ba
NK029(ha)004:7183: mtha' yas yab yum pad+ma dang dril bu bsnams pa
NK029(ha)004:7184: bskyed / de bzhin du rtsibs bzhi la /
NK029(ha)004:7185: rdo rje chos pad+ma kha 'byed pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7186: rdo rje glu len pa pi wang bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7192: rdo rje gsal ka ma sgron me bsnams pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7193: sgo ba yab yum rang rang gis sngags kyis bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7198: sbyor ba'i brdas bskul snyom par zhugs pa rjes chags kyi mes /
NK029(ha)004:7199: lha bac+wa brgyad slob bu dang bcas pa 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung dmar po las /
NK029(ha)004:7200: snang ba mtha' yas su gyur par bsam /
NK029(ha)004:7202: gyis bdud rtsi bla med kyis /
NK029(ha)004:7203: dad ldan skyes bu ngom par byos /
NK029(ha)004:7204: rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can la /
NK029(ha)004:7205: mthun par gsang bsgrag gzhan du min /
NK029(ha)004:7210: 'khor lo dung chags shing gsum las /
NK029(ha)004:7212: lag pa g.yas su dung dang /
NK029(ha)004:7213: g.yon du chags shing gtad la /
NK029(ha)004:7216: lce la gnas pa'i smra byed reg shes kyi thig
NK029(ha)004:7217: le la stim zhing sngon chad sems can gyi shes
NK029(ha)004:7218: rgyud la / chos kyi 'khor lo bskor mi nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)004:7219: da chos kyi 'khor lo rgyun mi 'chad par bskor
NK029(ha)004:7220: nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par bsgom zhing
NK029(ha)004:7222: 'chad pa'i dbang bskur bas sems can thams cad kyi shes pa'i rgyud la /
NK029(ha)004:7223: theg pa mtha' dag gi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:7224: bdun pa dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK029(ha)004:7225: dbang ma thob par 'chad pa la sogs byas na /
NK029(ha)004:7226: 'bras bu med cing brlag par 'gyur ba'i skyon yod do //
NK029(ha)004:7227: brgyad pa dbang thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)004:7229: tshe ring bde skyid phun sum 'tshogs pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7230: phyi mar mtho ris dang thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur ro //
NK029(ha)004:7231: lnga pa rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams gyi dbang la /
NK029(ha)004:7232: brgyad kyi dang po rgyu la gnyis kyi dang po mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:7233: yan lag lnga'i 'dam rtsa na bskyod byed reg shes kyi thig le lnga gnas pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7234: gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:7235: rdo rje dril bu kun bzang yab yum kyi rab gnas can no //
NK029(ha)004:7236: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi'i dang po'i slob ma ste /
NK029(ha)004:7237: mi mthun phyogs gyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)004:7238: mthun phyogs gyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o /
NK029(ha)004:7239: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7240: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7241: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7242: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7243: bzhi pa de ma theg pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7244: 'chad dbang thob pas rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams gyi dbang thob pa'i sgo phye ste /
NK029(ha)004:7247: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyii dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)004:7248: bzhi pa 'bras bu ni nus pa dngos su bskyed pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:7249: rno mtshon la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)004:7252: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)004:7253: drug pa las rim la lnga'i dang po bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)004:7254: dbang phyug yab yum kun bzang yab yum du gsal ba'i sbyor 'tsham gyi /
NK029(ha)004:7257: lag 'thil g.yas g.yon rnams su 'phros pas /
NK029(ha)004:7258: b+h+rum bi shwa b+ai shud d+he'i sngags lan lnga brjod pas /
NK029(ha)004:7259: mgo la sogs pa'i gnas lngar gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa cha lnga bskyed la /
NK029(ha)004:7260: mgo'i gzhal yas khang gi dbus kyi 'khor lo la /
NK029(ha)004:7262: de bzhin du lag pa g.yas pa h+aum zung lnga lag pa g.yon pa la swa zung lnga /
NK029(ha)004:7263: rkang pa g.yon pa la am zung lnga /
NK029(ha)004:7264: g.yas pa la h+aa zung lnga /
NK029(ha)004:7273: bshang lam rnams su h+aum zung re re bkod la /
NK029(ha)004:7275: lha bdun bcu rang rang gi phyag mtshan du gyur te /
NK029(ha)004:7276: de yang s+phar sang gi spro bsdus /
NK029(ha)004:7277: lha bdun bcu rang rang gi bskyed sngags kyis sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed do //
NK029(ha)004:7278: thog mar slob bu'i mgo la bskyed pa'i gzhal yas
NK029(ha)004:7279: khang gi 'khor la gnas pa'i nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan
NK029(ha)004:7280: la / dbus kyi lte ba la /
NK029(ha)004:7283: tsakra g+han+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7287: zhes rnams snang yab yum bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7296: zhes rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje dang /
NK029(ha)004:7297: la s+ye ma me long bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7303: sam ha ra na h'u badz+ra ra dza /
NK029(ha)004:7305: zhes rdo rje rgyal po lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7306: d+hu pe ma spos khang bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7315: zhes rdo rje chags pa 'da' gzhu 'gengs pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7316: rdo rje lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7325: zhes rdo rje legs pa se gol brdeb pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7326: rdo rje sgrol ma sngo po 'phreng ba bsnams pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7327: lag pa g.yas kyi gzhal yas khang gi gdan gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)004:7330: cho ga gsum gyis lha bskyed de /
NK029(ha)004:7331: h+aum h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7337: mum da du shwa ri h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:7338: zhes mi skyod pa yab yum bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7340: h+aum h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7344: zhes sems dpa' rdo rje dang /
NK029(ha)004:7345: brtan ma rdo rje skur brten ma /
NK029(ha)004:7346: g.yas su h+aum h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7348: rat+na dz+wa la s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7349: sam ha ra na h'u rat+na badz+ra h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:7351: zhes rin chen rdo rje rin chen 'bar ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:7352: 'bar ma rdo rje me 'od bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7353: rgyab du h+aum h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7359: zhes chos kyi rdo rje pad+ma dang /
NK029(ha)004:7360: bsdud ma rdo rje spo ti bsnams pa g.yon du h+aum h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7367: zhes rdo rje 'phrin las shang lang dang /
NK029(ha)004:7368: bskyod ma rdo rje ba dan bsnams pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7369: lag pa g.yon gyi gzhal yas khang gi 'khor lo'i lte ba la /
NK029(ha)004:7370: swa swa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7372: rat+na g+han+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7374: swa rat+na d+h+rika mam mo ha ra ti swah+aa zhes rin chen 'byung ldan yab yum bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7383: zhes rdo rje rin chen rin po che'i myu gu dang phreng ba bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7384: g.yas su s+w+aa s+w+aa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7386: sur+ya push+pe s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7390: rdo rje gzi brjid nyi ma dang /
NK029(ha)004:7391: me tog ma me tog bsnam pa /
NK029(ha)004:7392: rgyab du s+w+aa s+w+aa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7394: ke du pa sha s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7398: zhes rdo rje rgyal mtshan dang /
NK029(ha)004:7399: rdo rje zhags pa ma zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7400: g.yon du s+w+aa s+w+aa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7402: ha s+ye ra ti s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7404: badz+ra ha s+ye s+w+aa badz+ra rat+na s+w+aa zhes /
NK029(ha)004:7405: rdo rje gzhad pa tshems kyi 'phreng ba ston pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7406: rdo rje bsil yab rin po che'i bsil yab bsnams pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7407: rkang pa g.yon gyi gzhal yas khang gi 'khor lo'i lte ba la /
NK029(ha)004:7408: am am s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7410: pad+ma g+han+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7412: a ro lika am pyam ra ga ra ti am /
NK029(ha)004:7413: zhes snang ba mtha' yas yab yum bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7415: am am s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7417: d+harma git+ti s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7422: rdo rje glu len ma pi wam bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7430: badz+ra a lo ke am zhes /
NK029(ha)004:7431: rdo rje rnon po ral gri dang /
NK029(ha)004:7432: rdo rje mar me ma mar me bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7433: rgyab du am am s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7435: tsakra spo ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7439: zhes rdo rje rgyu 'khor lo dang /
NK029(ha)004:7440: rdo rje lcags sgrog ma lcags sgrog bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7445: pak+sha ke pa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7450: rdo rje smra ba rdo rje'i lce dang rdo rje gsal kra ma rdo rje bsnams par bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7451: rkang pa g.yas pa'i gzhal yas khang gi 'khor lo'i lte ba la /
NK029(ha)004:7452: khang+gu ga n+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7456: don yod grub pa yab yum bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7458: ha ha s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7460: bi shwa badz+ra nirti s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7462: badz+ra karma h+aa badz+ra nirti h+aa /
NK029(ha)004:7464: rdo rje las sna tshogs rdo rje pad+ma /
NK029(ha)004:7465: rdo rje gar ma gar bsgyur ba'o //
NK029(ha)004:7469: rak+sha g+han+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7473: rdo rje bsrung ba go cha dang /
NK029(ha)004:7474: rdo rje tri ma dbyug pa'o /
NK029(ha)004:7475: rgyab tu h+aa h+aa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7477: tram tram g+han+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7481: zhes rdo rje gnod sbyin phag rgod kyi mche ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:7482: rdo rje dril bu ma dril bu bsnams pa'o /
NK029(ha)004:7483: g.yon du h+aa h+aa s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7485: san ti par she s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7489: rdo rje khu tshur skur brten pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7490: rdo rje reg ma lha'i nam bza' pan tsa li ka bsnams pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7495: gis spro bsdus 'od du zhu ba'i 'od phung las /
NK029(ha)004:7496: badz+ra b+han+ha s+pha ra na phata /
NK029(ha)004:7498: bcus khro bo bcu'i thugs phyag mtshan rdo rje dung dmar bcur gyur pa las /
NK029(ha)004:7499: sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7500: spyi gtsug tu badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum ka ra h+aum h+aum las /
NK029(ha)004:7501: h+aum ka ra sngo skya g.yas dkar /
NK029(ha)004:7503: phyag dang por rdo rje dang dung dmar /
NK029(ha)004:7505: tha ma gnyis phur pa 'dril ba /
NK029(ha)004:7506: dur drod kyi chas brgyad dang /
NK029(ha)004:7507: gar dgu'i brgyan pa dang 'od kyis yum sgra 'byin ma dang bcas par bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7508: de bzhin du 'chad par 'gyur ba'i khro bo thams cad kyang /
NK029(ha)004:7509: dbus zhal sku mdog dang mtshungs pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7510: phyag dang po gnyis rdo rje dang dung dmar /
NK029(ha)004:7511: bar ma gnyis rang btags kyi phyag mtshan 'dzin pa /
NK029(ha)004:7512: tha ma gnyis ri rab kyi phur pa 'dril ba /
NK029(ha)004:7513: dur khro kyi chas brgyad kyi brgyan zhing /
NK029(ha)004:7514: rang 'od kyi yum rdo rje snyem ma la sogs pa /
NK029(ha)004:7515: g.yas gtso bo la 'khyud nas g.yon pas dung dmar
NK029(ha)004:7516: gtso la stobs pa dang bcas me dpung gi klong
NK029(ha)004:7520: snying khar rnam rgyal dkar po zhal g.yas sngo skya /
NK029(ha)004:7521: g.yon sngon po kha tram tri shul bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7523: zhes nu kha g.yas la dbyug pa sngon po g.yas dkar /
NK029(ha)004:7525: dbyug pa dang me dpung bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7526: ya man ta ka h+aum h+aum zhes /
NK029(ha)004:7530: g.yon ljang ben con dang dgra s+t+wa bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7531: sog steng g.yas par ar+ya a tsa la h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:7533: mi g.yo mgon po sku mdog ljang dmar /
NK029(ha)004:7536: spu gri dang zhags pa bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7537: sog phrag tu h+ya g+h+ri ba h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:7542: ral gri dang sbrul zhags 'dzin pa'o /
NK029(ha)004:7543: sog steng g.yon du a pa ra dzi ta h+aum h+aum zhes /
NK029(ha)004:7544: gzhan gyis mi thub pa sngon po /
NK029(ha)004:7546: b+han rgya dang rnga yab bsnams pa /
NK029(ha)004:7548: a mri ta kun+da li h+aum h+aum zhes /
NK029(ha)004:7552: rgya gram dang dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7553: nu kha g.yon par tre lo kya bi dza ya h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:7555: khams gsum rnam rgyal ser po /
NK029(ha)004:7556: g.yas ljang g.yon du kha 'khor lo dang mche ba 'dzin pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7557: bshang khar ma h+aa ba la h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:7558: zhes stobs po che dung kha g.yas ser /
NK029(ha)004:7562: de ltar lha tshogs bdun bcu po la /
NK029(ha)004:7563: shu nya tas ye shes lnga'i dbang bskur la /
NK029(ha)004:7564: rang rang gi rigs kyi bdag po /
NK029(ha)004:7565: dbus na gnas pa'i rigs lngas dbu brgyan par bsgom la /
NK029(ha)004:7566: k+aa ya badz+ra la sogs sku gsung thugs byin gyis rlabs /
NK029(ha)004:7567: rang bzhin gyis gnas nas rang 'dra ba'i ye shes pa /
NK029(ha)004:7572: ka ya waka tsit+tasa brtan par byas /
NK029(ha)004:7573: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod pas /
NK029(ha)004:7574: lha yab yum thams cad phan tshun mkha' gsang brlabs /
NK029(ha)004:7576: snyom par zhugs pa'i bde ba chen pos /
NK029(ha)004:7577: slob bu dang bcas pa zhu bar gyur pa'i 'od phung sngon po las /
NK029(ha)004:7578: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po kun tu bzang po bsam /
NK029(ha)004:7580: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i thams cad kyi //
NK029(ha)004:7581: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK029(ha)004:7582: dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed pa po //
NK029(ha)004:7583: dkyil 'khor kun gyis sbyin pa mos //
NK029(ha)004:7586: dbang phyug gi rdo rje dang dril bu bsnol ma gtad de /
NK029(ha)004:7587: snying khar bsnol du bcug la /
NK029(ha)004:7589: yan lag lnga'i reg shes kyi thig le la /
NK029(ha)004:7591: sngon chad slob ma dkyil 'khor du zhugs cing dbang
NK029(ha)004:7592: bskur ba la sogs pa gzhan don bya bar mi
NK029(ha)004:7593: nus pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)004:7594: da dbang phyug chen por gyur ste /
NK029(ha)004:7595: bdag dang gzhan gyi don phun sum tshogs par spyod
NK029(ha)004:7596: cing sgrub nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par
NK029(ha)004:7599: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyis dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)004:7600: slob ma dkyil 'khor du zhugs cing dbang bskur pa
NK029(ha)004:7601: la sogs pa'i las thams cad byed pa'i rdo rje
NK029(ha)004:7602: rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang dam pa thob
NK029(ha)004:7603: par gyur cig / bdun pa bka' rab 'byams kyis dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK029(ha)004:7604: rtsa rgyud kyi le'u bcu pa las /
NK029(ha)004:7605: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK029(ha)004:7606: dbang rnams thob par ma byas na /
NK029(ha)004:7607: nyan pa la sogs rtsom pa rnams //'bras bu med cing brlag par 'gyur /
NK029(ha)004:7609: brgyad pa dbang thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)004:7611: dus 'di tshun chad rgyal ba'i sras /
NK029(ha)004:7612: ngan song thams cad med pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7613: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK029(ha)004:7614: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur /
NK029(ha)004:7616: de dag ni nang nus pa'i dbang gi las kyi rim pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:7617: nang nus kyi dkyil 'khor du bskur pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7619: bsgom dbang thob pas bdag don nus /
NK029(ha)004:7620: 'phrin las kyi dbang 'chad dbang thob pas gzhan don nus /
NK029(ha)004:7621: rdo rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang thob pas /
NK029(ha)004:7622: bdag gzhan thams cad kyi don phun sum tshogs pa nus pa'i phyir /
NK029(ha)004:7623: nus pa'i dbang zhes tha snyad du bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:7624: spyi don gsum pa zab mo'i dbang la /
NK029(ha)004:7625: gsang rgyud le'u bcu pa las /
NK029(ha)004:7626: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya mas /
NK029(ha)004:7627: bde ba'i 'bru tshogs gsal ba'i rgyun /
NK029(ha)004:7628: rdo rje lam nas pad mor dkyil /
NK029(ha)004:7629: rtse nas stim zhing dkyil 'khor bsgyur /
NK029(ha)004:7632: gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:7633: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:7634: bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur ba'o //
NK029(ha)004:7635: dang po la brgyad kyi dang po rgyud la gnyis kyi /
NK029(ha)004:7636: dang po mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:7637: kun rdzob tsam du skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong gi sems rang chas su gnas pa de'o //
NK029(ha)004:7638: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:7641: chos gsum bshad pa'i bu mo mtshan nyid dang ldan pa lo nyi shu lon pa de'o //
NK029(ha)004:7644: gsang dbang bskur du rung pa'i skyes bu ste /
NK029(ha)004:7645: mi mthun phyogs gyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)004:7646: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7647: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7648: bu mo lo nyi shu ma yum lnga la sogs pas byin gyis ba rlabs pa de'o //
NK029(ha)004:7649: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7650: gsang dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma ste /
NK029(ha)004:7651: yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o /
NK029(ha)004:7653: de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7654: dbang snga ma nang nus dbang lnga thob pas go phye nas /
NK029(ha)004:7655: gsang dbang 'byung ba'i rkyen byed pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:7656: gsang dbang thob la ma rag pa de'o //
NK029(ha)004:7657: gsum pa dbang gi ngo bo ni /
NK029(ha)004:7660: nus pa dngos su bskyed pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:7661: rno mtshon la ngar brtag pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)004:7663: nus dbang gi rjes su gsang dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)004:7664: drug pa las rim lnga'i dang po bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)004:7665: thog mar phyag rgya ma mtshan nyid brtag pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:7666: dam tshig rdo rje gsal bkra las /
NK029(ha)004:7667: pad can dung can ri mo can /
NK029(ha)004:7668: ba glang can dang lcugs phran can /
NK029(ha)004:7669: sdong gcig me rig chal ba brgyad /
NK029(ha)004:7670: bsnyen grangs snyed ring stod smad phyed /
NK029(ha)004:7671: yan lag phra 'jam tshig mig zlum /
NK029(ha)004:7672: dpral ba'i dbyes che mig kyus ring /
NK029(ha)004:7673: mig dpral dkyil na ud dpal mdog /
NK029(ha)004:7674: mchur zhing gnyis ka 'bring du bshad /
NK029(ha)004:7675: lus la chu rlung ga bur dri /
NK029(ha)004:7676: gsang thub shes rab spyod pa dal /
NK029(ha)004:7677: dad ldan 'grogs shing dad che ba /
NK029(ha)004:7679: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa bkug cing /
NK029(ha)004:7681: bza' btung longs spyod man+dala dang bcas pas bla ma la phul /
NK029(ha)004:7682: de nas bla mas yum la ji ltar 'os pa'i dbang bskur /
NK029(ha)004:7683: de nas yab yum gnyis bdag bskyed bsgoms ste /
NK029(ha)004:7684: yab kun du bzang por sgom pa'i gnas lnga rigs lnga yan lag bzhi la sgo ba bzhi bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7685: rgyas pa ltar na bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi lus dkyil bsgom /
NK029(ha)004:7687: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa gos shugs la shes /
NK029(ha)004:7688: yum kun du bzang mor sgom /
NK029(ha)004:7690: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7693: de la ye shes pa spyan drangs nas ba stim mchod bstod /
NK029(ha)004:7694: de nas yab kyi gsang ba'i h+aum las /
NK029(ha)004:7695: rdo rje dmar po rtse lnga pa rwa lnga la yab kyi 'bru lnga /
NK029(ha)004:7698: yum gyi mkha' la pad+ma 'dab brgyad /
NK029(ha)004:7699: ze 'bru la e mthing ka med 'od dang ldan pa bskyed la /
NK029(ha)004:7701: zhi ba'i bsnyen pa ci rigs par byed do //
NK029(ha)004:7703: dkyil 'khor sor bzhi'i tshad du bya gsungs pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7705: ka p+aa la'i steng gi me long la pad+ma 'dab
NK029(ha)004:7706: bzhi gru chad sgo 'dogs can la sogs bri zhing
NK029(ha)004:7707: / yum lnga sgo ma dang bcas pa la sogs bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7709: gsungs pa dang mtshungs par me long gi steng gi
NK029(ha)004:7710: rdo rje la rigs lnga sgo ba bzhi dang bcas
NK029(ha)004:7714: bsnyen pa dang bcas pa byed do //
NK029(ha)004:7715: de nas mdun bskyed kyi lha tshogs la gsang dbang
NK029(ha)004:7716: gi bdag 'jug bla ma yab yum gnyis kas len
NK029(ha)004:7717: no // de nas bus man+dala phul la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:7718: rdo rje slob dpon yab yum dgongs //'dod pa 'byung pa rin chen gter //
NK029(ha)004:7719: dgyes pa chen po thabs lam gyis /
NK029(ha)004:7720: chu bo bzhi las bdag sgrol mdzod /
NK029(ha)004:7723: bu khyod bsgrol dang thabs lam 'di //
NK029(ha)004:7724: rgyal ba yongs kyis sbas pa yin //
NK029(ha)004:7725: thabs chen gsang ba'i theg pa 'di //
NK029(ha)004:7726: gtsang smes 'ching ba sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK029(ha)004:7727: dri sha chu rnams bza' btung dang //
NK029(ha)004:7728: b+ha ga'i ye shes dkyil 'khor la //'o dang 'jib dang bsgreng ba dang //
NK029(ha)004:7729: sems chu gdung bar khyod nus sam /
NK029(ha)004:7731: e ma ho thabs lam ye shes phyir //
NK029(ha)004:7732: bdag ni ci yang mi nus med //
NK029(ha)004:7733: de dag bdag gis spyad par bgyi //
NK029(ha)004:7734: ji ltar spyad phyir bdag la bstsol /
NK029(ha)004:7736: de nas bla mas yab yum bde ba'i bstan chos bshad /
NK029(ha)004:7737: 'o dang 'khyud pa la sogs pas bde ba rgyas par byed /
NK029(ha)004:7738: de nas phyag rgya bzhis rol /
NK029(ha)004:7739: yum gyis mkha' la rgyal ba'i dal bskyed la /
NK029(ha)004:7740: thig le dbab la mchod pa 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:7741: de nas yum gyis byang sems dkar dmar du 'dres pa des /
NK029(ha)004:7742: slob bu la dbang bskur te /
NK029(ha)004:7743: bya dang bye'u'i tshul du bskur ba'i /
NK029(ha)004:7744: ba dang be'u'i tshul du bskur ba'am /
NK029(ha)004:7745: bung ba dang me tog gi tshul du bskur ba'am /
NK029(ha)004:7747: me long yu ba can gyi blang la bu ram
NK029(ha)004:7748: sogs pa'i mngar bsreg la lce thog du bzhug pas
NK029(ha)004:7749: / don dam rtog med kyi ye shes rgyud la skye /
NK029(ha)004:7750: tsit+ta'i snying gi nang du rigs drug gi sa bon yi ge drug sbyangs /
NK029(ha)004:7751: lus kyi rtsa gnas thig le dang bde bas gang par bsgoms la /
NK029(ha)004:7753: dri med skyon bral shel sgong mu tig 'dra //
NK029(ha)004:7754: pad+ma r+aa ga chags pa chen po'i gnas //
NK029(ha)004:7755: chos nyid dag pa'i 'gro don mthar phyin zhing /
NK029(ha)004:7756: byang chub sems kyi dbang mchog thob bya'i phyir /
NK029(ha)004:7757: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta yab kyi byang chub sems /
NK029(ha)004:7758: don dam dbyer med byang chub chen po'i ngang /
NK029(ha)004:7759: sin d+hur dmar po yum gyi byang chub sems /
NK029(ha)004:7760: thar pa'i lam mchog bde ba'i lam 'dren zhing /
NK029(ha)004:7761: 'khor ba'i lam las kun rgyal dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)004:7762: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)004:7763: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta ka ma la sid+hi h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:7766: lce thog tu bdud rtsi bzhag /
NK029(ha)004:7768: mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu la stim mo //
NK029(ha)004:7769: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang dag skye ni /
NK029(ha)004:7770: sngar phan chad gsang dbang ma thob pa'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)004:7771: longs spyod rdzogs pa yi sku thob pa'i nus pa skye bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:7773: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)004:7774: thabs shes gnyis su med par dbang 'byor nas /
NK029(ha)004:7775: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med cing 'du 'bral
NK029(ha)004:7776: med pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig bdun
NK029(ha)004:7777: pa skyon dang / brgyad par yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)004:7779: gnyis pa shes rab ye shes kyi dbang la brgyad
NK029(ha)004:7780: kyi dang po rgyu la gnyis kyi dang po mtshungs
NK029(ha)004:7782: don dam du skye ba med /
NK029(ha)004:7785: 'gro 'ong med pa'i byang chub kyi sems rang chas su gnas pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7786: gnyis pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:7790: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi'i dang po rgyu'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7791: dbang bskur du rung pa'i skyes bu ste mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)004:7792: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7793: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7794: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7795: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7796: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7797: bzhi pa de ma thag pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7798: gsang dbang thob par go phyes nas /
NK029(ha)004:7799: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob pa la ma rag pa'o /
NK029(ha)004:7801: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)004:7803: nus pa dngos su skyes pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:7804: rno la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)004:7806: gsang dbang gi rjes su shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)004:7807: drug pa rim pa lnga'i dang po bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)004:7808: gzungs ma lo bcu drug mtshan dang ldan pa bkug cing khrus byas /
NK029(ha)004:7811: longs spyod man+dala dang bcas pa bla ma la 'bul lo /
NK029(ha)004:7812: bla mas phyag rgya ma la dge bcu bshad /
NK029(ha)004:7817: bdag bskyed lus dkyil ltar rgyas par bsgom la /
NK029(ha)004:7818: spyan 'dren la sogs mchod bstod dang /
NK029(ha)004:7819: bsnyen pa 'bum tshar nas mdun bskyed me long dang /
NK029(ha)004:7820: rdo rje la dmigs pa'i mdun bskyed spyan 'dren mchod bstod bsnyen pa yan chad tshar ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:7821: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang bskur ste /
NK029(ha)004:7822: de nas slob bus thal mo sbyar la //
NK029(ha)004:7823: rdo rje dga' ma bdag la dgongs //'dod pa 'byung ba rin chen gter //
NK029(ha)004:7824: dgyes pa chen pos thabs lam gyis //
NK029(ha)004:7825: chu bo bzhi las bdag sgrol cig /
NK029(ha)004:7827: bu khyod smros dang thabs lam 'di /
NK029(ha)004:7828: rgyal ba yongs kyis sbas pa yin /
NK029(ha)004:7829: thabs chen gsang ba'i theg pa ru /
NK029(ha)004:7830: gtsang sbras 'ching ba sbyang ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)004:7831: dri sha chu dang bza' btung dang /
NK029(ha)004:7832: nga'i b+ha ga'i ye shes bzhi /
NK029(ha)004:7833: 'o dang gzhib dang drangs ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:7834: sems chu btung bar spyod nus sam /
NK029(ha)004:7837: thabs lam ye shes chen po'i phyir /
NK029(ha)004:7838: bdag ni ci yang mi nus med /
NK029(ha)004:7839: de dag bdag gis spyad par bgyi /
NK029(ha)004:7840: ci ltar spyad phyir bdag la bstsol /
NK029(ha)004:7842: de nas gnyis pa bsgrag tshig ni /
NK029(ha)004:7843: bla mas rig ma mtshan ldan gyi lag nas gzung ste /
NK029(ha)004:7844: slob ma la gtad pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:7845: skye med chos dbyings rig pa 'byung ba'i yum /
NK029(ha)004:7846: mtshan ldan rig ma mchog gis brgyan /
NK029(ha)004:7847: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med rol pa las /
NK029(ha)004:7848: lhag pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor spro /
NK029(ha)004:7849: 'phags mchog bde bsgrub 'bras bu kun mnyes pa /
NK029(ha)004:7850: gnyis med don spyod chos nyid dag pa'i brgyan /
NK029(ha)004:7851: dgyes pa'i ro mchog bde chen dbang thob shog /
NK029(ha)004:7852: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mah+aa gu h+ye pradz+ny+aa shwa ra swa b+ha wa ad+ma ko ham /
NK029(ha)004:7854: de nas 'dod pa'i bstan chos kyi bde ba rgyas pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7855: bde ba dbab pa'i thob gtum mo sbar ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:7856: rtsa rlung thig le bsgom pa'i thabs rnams slob la /
NK029(ha)004:7857: sha chen gyi tshod ma dang /
NK029(ha)004:7858: dri chen gyi bza' ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:7860: nye'u shing khu ba btung ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:7862: lus snum dang dri zhim pos byug la /
NK029(ha)004:7864: lus sems stong pa nyid las kun tu bzang mor bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7866: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi 'god /
NK029(ha)004:7867: mkha' ga sang las pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad e mthing khas mtshan pa /
NK029(ha)004:7868: e mthing ka me 'od dang ldan pa bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7869: bu rdo rje sems dpa' bsgoms la /
NK029(ha)004:7871: yan lag bzhi la sgo ba bzhi bskyed /
NK029(ha)004:7872: gsang ba h+aum las rdo rje dmar po rtse lnga pa bsgom pa'i r+aa la /
NK029(ha)004:7874: dbus kyi rtsa gsum la 'bru gsum sum mdor phata bsgom /
NK029(ha)004:7875: dri zhim po sbrang gi sbyar ba'i ril bu mur
NK029(ha)004:7876: zhing pad+ma la bltas ste yongs su rgyas nas phyag
NK029(ha)004:7879: spyi bo nas 'khor lo bzhi la rim pa bzhin dbab cing /
NK029(ha)004:7880: dga' ba bzhi'i ye shes bskyed la /
NK029(ha)004:7881: rang rig ye shes kyi ngo bo lhag pa byang
NK029(ha)004:7882: chub kyi sems ngo bo rdo rje nor bu'i rtser
NK029(ha)004:7883: phebs pa'i dus na gzung zhing bskyil ste /
NK029(ha)004:7884: de yang rlung bum pa can gzung pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7885: yig 'bru'i sbyor bas gzung ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:7886: lus kyi 'khrul 'khor gyi gzung ba la sogs pas thig les bzung pa'i dus na /
NK029(ha)004:7887: gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa thams cad dang bral ba'i
NK029(ha)004:7888: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes bde stong dbyer med
NK029(ha)004:7889: kyi chos nyid / 'od gsal dri ma med pa'i don /
NK029(ha)004:7890: ci bzhin ye mnyam chen po'i dgongs pa gnyis med
NK029(ha)004:7891: thig le nyag gcig gi rtogs pa ci lta ba
NK029(ha)004:7892: bzhin nyams su myong zhing ngo shes par gyur to
NK029(ha)004:7893: // de nas gnyis ka'i lag pa nas bzung nas /
NK029(ha)004:7894: bu khyod 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las //
NK029(ha)004:7895: grol zhing thar nas skad cig gis //
NK029(ha)004:7896: rdo rje nam mkha'i ye shes che //
NK029(ha)004:7897: bla ma chen po'i sar gnas su //
NK029(ha)004:7898: thams cad rigs kyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK029(ha)004:7899: gcig pu sa bzung mnga' brnyes nas //
NK029(ha)004:7900: bde khyab chen po'i 'phrin las kyis //
NK029(ha)004:7901: khams gsum sras su gzung bar byos //
NK029(ha)004:7906: bstim gnas bde ba la bde ba stim mo //
NK029(ha)004:7907: bdun pa dbang ma bskur ba'i skyon ni /
NK029(ha)004:7908: de kho na nyid kyi dbang bskur du mi rung pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7909: phyag rgya mo la brten pa'i bde ba lam du mi rung ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:7910: sbyor ba lam du mi slong ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:7911: lhan gcig skyes pa'i bde chen dang /
NK029(ha)004:7912: rang ngo mi 'phrod pa'i skyon yod do //
NK029(ha)004:7914: lam gyi dus na sa bcu gcig pa thob pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7915: 'bras bu'i dus na bde ba chen po'i sku thob pa'i yon tan yod do //
NK029(ha)004:7916: gsum pa bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur ba la brgyad kyi dang po /
NK029(ha)004:7917: rgyu la gnyis kyi dang po mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK029(ha)004:7918: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med /
NK029(ha)004:7920: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med /
NK029(ha)004:7921: dmigs pa nyid nas dmigs pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:7922: bden gnyis ye nas dbyer med par rang chas su gnas pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7923: gnyis pa mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni phyag rgya mo lo bcu gnyis ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7924: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi la dang po rgyu'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7925: dbang bskur du rung pa'i slob ma ste /
NK029(ha)004:7926: mi mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang bral zhing /
NK029(ha)004:7927: mthun phyogs kyi rgyu dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7928: gnyis pa dmigs pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7929: bu mo lo bcu gnyis mar rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7930: gsum pa bdag po'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7931: dbang bskur nus pa'i bla ma ste /
NK029(ha)004:7932: yon tan bcu bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7933: bzhi pa de ma theg pa'i rkyen ni /
NK029(ha)004:7934: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob pas /
NK029(ha)004:7935: bde ba chen po'i dbang thob pa'i sgo phye ste /
NK029(ha)004:7936: dbang thob la ma rag pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:7937: gsum pa dbang gi ngo bo ni /
NK029(ha)004:7938: bde ba chen po'i dbang ngo //
NK029(ha)004:7940: nus pa dngos su skyes pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:7941: rno mtshon la ngar btags pa lta bu'o //
NK029(ha)004:7943: shes rab ye shes kyi dbang gi rjes su bde ba chen po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)004:7944: drug pa las rim la lnga'i dang po bsam rgyud ni /
NK029(ha)004:7945: phyag rgya ma lo bcu gnyis ma bkug cing /
NK029(ha)004:7948: bza' btung longs spyod man+dala dang bcas pa bla mar 'bul /
NK029(ha)004:7949: de nas bla mas ji ltar 'os pa'i yum la dbang bskur la sbyor ba byas ste /
NK029(ha)004:7950: gzugs ma'i don dam pa'i lte ba nas /
NK029(ha)004:7951: zla ba tshes pa lta bu'i nang na byang chub
NK029(ha)004:7952: sems kyi thig le nyung dkar tsam zhig rang bzhin
NK029(ha)004:7953: gyis gnas pa la ting nge 'dzin gyis dmigs te
NK029(ha)004:7954: / gsang ba'i rdo rje ye shes kyi ro can dang /
NK029(ha)004:7957: yab kyi lhag pa'i b+ho d+hi thig le dang mkha' la gnas pa de basre'o //
NK029(ha)004:7958: de nas ru bab la pad+ma'i 'khyams na b+ho d+hi yod pa theb srin gyis blangs la /
NK029(ha)004:7959: gzungs ma'i lce thog tu bskur ro //
NK029(ha)004:7960: de nas ya ba yum gnyis kas bdag bskyed zhi
NK029(ha)004:7961: ba'i lha zhe gnyis snying po brjod pas rdzogs pa'i
NK029(ha)004:7963: sa man dzas snyan gsan dbab /
NK029(ha)004:7965: dzahh+aum bam hohsaganyisa su med par stim la /
NK029(ha)004:7966: mchod bstod bsnyen pa ci rigs pa bya /
NK029(ha)004:7967: mdun bskyed kyang gong ltar du bsnyen pa yan chad byas la /
NK029(ha)004:7969: de nas slob bu'i gung mo g.yas pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7970: gzungs ma'i gung mo g.yon pa rat+na'i 'phreng bas bcings ste /
NK029(ha)004:7971: de'i mdo' nas slob dpon gyis gzung ste /
NK029(ha)004:7973: bde ba chen po chos kyi sku //
NK029(ha)004:7974: shes rab thabs kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //'di dang skye ba thams cad du //
NK029(ha)004:7975: dngos grub ster bas 'di mi spongs //
NK029(ha)004:7976: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK029(ha)004:7977: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas khyod las byung //
NK029(ha)004:7978: spangs na rdo rje dbyings phyug rtsa //
NK029(ha)004:7979: dgug dang bsgom pa ma shes na //
NK029(ha)004:7980: rdo rje skal pa mtha' slas pa //
NK029(ha)004:7981: chos sku thob par mi 'gyur ro //
NK029(ha)004:7982: de'i don rgyas par bshad do //
NK029(ha)004:7989: thog ma gzung ma mthong pas bde ba g.yos pa dga' ba'o //
NK029(ha)004:7990: de dus gzungs ma byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:7991: srin lag sprel ba la sogs pa byas pas bde
NK029(ha)004:7992: ba skye ba mchog daga'o //'dod pa'i chos kyi cha
NK029(ha)004:7993: byed pa ni / dga' bral lo //
NK029(ha)004:7994: gzugs ma dang rang lus rdul zhing bem gyis song ba ni lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba'o //
NK029(ha)004:7996: rang dang gzungs ma gnyis ka la /
NK029(ha)004:7998: bde ba chen po'i tsakra ni dga' ba /
NK029(ha)004:7999: longs spyod de tsakra ni mchog daga'o //
NK029(ha)004:8000: dar ma tsakra ni dga' bral /
NK029(ha)004:8001: sprul pa'i tsakra ni lhan skyes so /
NK029(ha)004:8003: gu h+ya badz+ra tsa ba ni dga' ba /
NK029(ha)004:8004: rdo rje sked pa ni mchog dga' /
NK029(ha)004:8005: rdo rje'i bum pa ni dga' 'bral /
NK029(ha)004:8006: rdo rje'i rtse mo ni lhan cig skyes daga'o //
NK029(ha)004:8007: de rnams re re la yang thig le bzhi bzhi rtsis pas bcu drug ste /
NK029(ha)004:8010: bcu gsang ba'i sa bcu shes par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:8011: de ltar gdam ngag phog nas /
NK029(ha)004:8012: bus sbyor ba la snyom par 'jug ste /
NK029(ha)004:8013: rdo rje la h+aum gcig bkod de spro bsdu la /
NK029(ha)004:8014: rdo rje rtse lnga pa gcig tu gyur /
NK029(ha)004:8016: rtse mo yi bu gar phata nag po /
NK029(ha)004:8017: b+ha ga la phata nag po gcig bsam /
NK029(ha)004:8020: de'i dbus su e mthing kha gru gsum pa /
NK029(ha)004:8021: de'i steng du h+aum dmar po gcig bsgom /
NK029(ha)004:8022: de nas gzungs ma la 'dod pa'i bstan chos kyi cha rnams bya /
NK029(ha)004:8024: rdo rje phyed tsam pad+mara bsdams ste /
NK029(ha)004:8026: sra bar myong pas 'byung pa sa'i rdul cung zad gsher ba chu cung zad dro ba me /
NK029(ha)004:8027: de nas shes pa zhib tu brtags pas bde ba g.yo ba rlung ngo //
NK029(ha)004:8028: de nas bde ba bzlog ste thabs kyi bzlog pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:8030: phyag rgyas bzlog pa gsum las /
NK029(ha)004:8031: dang po ni bde ba g.yo ba tsam na /
NK029(ha)004:8032: rdo rje e tsam gcig pha tshad la phyung la /
NK029(ha)004:8033: lto ba rgal tshig la sbyar /
NK029(ha)004:8035: b+ho d+hi de slar ldog pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:8036: ting nge 'dzin gyi bzlog pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:8039: ro rkyang gnyis kyi rtsa sna dbus kyi kun d+har 'brel nas yod pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:8040: ro rkyang nas dbugs zhugs pa las /
NK029(ha)004:8041: kun d+har gyi lhag pa'i b+ho d+hi gyen la sna
NK029(ha)004:8042: 'khyil gyis ldog nas dkar chil gyis ldog par bsam
NK029(ha)004:8044: rdo rje'i rtsa ba nas phar /
NK029(ha)004:8045: sor mo gnyis kyi thub tshad mnan la ldog sprul pa'i 'khor lo nas gyen la de ltar ldog /
NK029(ha)004:8046: rdo rje'i rtsa ba nas dang /
NK029(ha)004:8048: rtse mo nas rim par ldog /
NK029(ha)004:8050: rdo rje rtsa ba'i dga' ba'i thig le bzhi'i theg
NK029(ha)004:8051: le gsum pa nas rdo rje sked pa'i mchog dag'i
NK029(ha)004:8052: / thig le gnyis pa ma chad ni gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa 'gag pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:8053: mchod dag'i thig le gnyis pa yan chad ni /
NK029(ha)004:8055: de nas rdo rje rtse mo /
NK029(ha)004:8056: lhan gcig skyes pa'i gnas su zla ba dang nyi ma'i thig le /
NK029(ha)004:8058: rang rang gi kha nas ma shor bar zin tsam nas /
NK029(ha)004:8059: rang rig pa'i don nyams su myong ba de kun tu 'od kyi sa'o /
NK029(ha)004:8060: de'i dus su rgyu'i zung 'jug nyi zla 'dres pas /
NK029(ha)004:8061: 'bras bu'i zung 'jug ye shes rang snang gi lha
NK029(ha)004:8062: dang lha mor snang bzhin du rang bzhin med pa'o
NK029(ha)004:8063: // de tsam na zhen pa med pa'i pad+ma can gyi sa'o //
NK029(ha)004:8064: de la smon lam gyi dbang gis gzugs sku gnyis 'byung ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:8065: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyis sa'o //
NK029(ha)004:8066: de ni theg pa 'og ma dang sgo bstun pa'o //
NK029(ha)004:8067: de nas rgyu 'bras bzlog pa'i theg pa ni /
NK029(ha)004:8068: nyi zla thig le rang gi gnas su rtse mo nas tshur bzlog pas rims gyis bsgrod de /
NK029(ha)004:8069: rdo rje'i rtsa bar byin pa ni kun du 'od kyi sa'o //
NK029(ha)004:8070: de nas sprul pa'i tsakrara phyin pa pad+ma can no //
NK029(ha)004:8071: thig le rang gnas su phyin pa las /
NK029(ha)004:8072: rang bzhin lhun grub gyi dkyil 'khor mthong ba ni /
NK029(ha)004:8073: tshogs chen gyis mngon du byas pa yin no //
NK029(ha)004:8074: gal te b+ho d+hi shor na /
NK029(ha)004:8075: byang sems h+aum dmar sha ltag bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:8076: 'theb srin gyis blangs la khong du mid do //
NK029(ha)004:8077: gzungs ma la yang sbyin no //
NK029(ha)004:8078: sbyor la mi rtog pa'i bde ba skyes pa'i dus su /
NK029(ha)004:8080: gzung ma mi dgos par mi rtog pa la blo gnas so /
NK029(ha)004:8082: yang dbang don de la blo gtad pas /
NK029(ha)004:8084: de ltar bsgom pa'i don la gnas par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:8085: bskur gnas lus kyi dbang po la bskur /
NK029(ha)004:8086: bstim gnas thig le la bstim /
NK029(ha)004:8087: sgrib pa gang dag nus pa gang skye ni /
NK029(ha)004:8088: bde ba chen po'i dbang thob pas shes bya'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK029(ha)004:8089: bde ba chen po'i dbang thob pa'i nus pa skye bar bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:8091: bdun pa dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK029(ha)004:8092: sems nyid rdzogs pa chen po yang dag don gyi lta ba mi rtogs pa /
NK029(ha)004:8093: gnas lugs chos nyid kyi don nyams su blang mi rung pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:8094: dngos grub gnyis 'dzin gyi mtshan ma sna tshogs kyis 'chings pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:8095: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa phyin ci ma log pa ngo ma 'phrod pa'i skyon yod do //
NK029(ha)004:8096: brgyad pa thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK029(ha)004:8097: kun tu bzang po dbyer ba med pa'i sa thob pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:8098: 'bras bu'i dus na chos kyi sku dang ngo bo nyid kyi sku thob po /
NK029(ha)004:8099: de dag rgyas par ni sangs rgyas gsang bas mdzad
NK029(ha)004:8100: pa'i dbang gi skabs nas dbang gi gal po la
NK029(ha)004:8101: sogs pa rnams su blta bar bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:8102: de dag ni gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gi las kyi rim pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:8104: shes rab ye shes ni b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor dang
NK029(ha)004:8105: dbyer med bde ba chen po ni sems kyi dkyil
NK029(ha)004:8107: de yang gsang dbang thob nas /
NK029(ha)004:8108: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga la longs spyod pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:8109: steng sgo 'khor lo'i man ngag sgom pa /
NK029(ha)004:8110: gsang ba shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob nas /
NK029(ha)004:8111: las kyi phyag rgya bsten pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:8112: 'og sgo khams gsum bsrub sbyor gyi man ngag sgom pa la dbang /
NK029(ha)004:8113: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang thob nas /
NK029(ha)004:8114: kun rdzob snod bcud sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK029(ha)004:8115: don dam bskor bdun ngo bo nyid kyi skur lhun gyis grub pa las ma g.yos par rtogs shing /
NK029(ha)004:8116: rang bzhin bden pa dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen po mngon du 'gyur pa'i don gsang ngo //
NK029(ha)004:8117: de yang thog ma gnyis ni dkyil 'khor b+ha ga dang /
NK029(ha)004:8118: dbang rdzas nyi zla byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK029(ha)004:8122: bung ba dang me tog gi tshul dang /
NK029(ha)004:8123: nyams len ka ra na'i bstan bcos brgyad dam drug bcu rtsa bzhi la sogs pa rnams ni /
NK029(ha)004:8124: 'jig rten pa rnams kyi gzhad gad kyi gnas su 'gyur ba'i phyir dang /
NK029(ha)004:8125: phyi ma blo chung ba rnams la rang gsang thabs kyi chod nas /
NK029(ha)004:8126: rang la gnas pa'i don de /
NK029(ha)004:8127: bstan kyang mi go mtshon kyang mi rtogs /
NK029(ha)004:8128: yon tan brjod kyang brod pa'i blo mi skye ba'i
NK029(ha)004:8129: phyir gsang ba zab mo'i dbang zhes tha snyad du
NK029(ha)004:8130: byas pa'o // don gsum pa rjes kyi bya ba la bdun ste /
NK029(ha)004:8131: dbang rtag sbyin zhing bka' sgo ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:8132: bum chu blud zhing smon lam 'debs pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:8133: dbang phyug gi dbang dbab cing slob bu'i lus 'bul ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:8134: btang rag gi mchod cing yon dbul ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:8135: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal gdab cing lhag bstan skyong ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:8136: dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing spyod lam rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:8137: lam rjes shis par bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)004:8140: dbang bac+wa brgyad rdzogs pa'i slob bu rnams gral la 'khod la /
NK029(ha)004:8141: dbang phyug gi rdo rje dril bu bsnams la //
NK029(ha)004:8142: sangs rgyas kun gyis rdo rje'i dbang //
NK029(ha)004:8143: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK029(ha)004:8144: sangs rgyas kun dang rab bsgrubs phyir //
NK029(ha)004:8145: rdo rje 'di ni khyod kyi long /
NK029(ha)004:8146: zhes brjod cing rdo rje gsor /
NK029(ha)004:8147: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK029(ha)004:8148: thabs dang shes rab dbang chen des //
NK029(ha)004:8150: chos la 'dod sbyin dbang bskur ro //
NK029(ha)004:8151: zhes brjod cing dril bu dkrol /
NK029(ha)004:8152: badz+ra g+han+de a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK029(ha)004:8154: rdo rje dril bu bsnol nas slob bu rnams kyi
NK029(ha)004:8155: lag pa g.yas g.yon du sbyin la rdo rje gsor
NK029(ha)004:8156: zhing dril bu dkrol du bzhug go /
NK029(ha)004:8157: kun rdzogs pa'i rjes thob su bden pa /
NK029(ha)004:8158: rigs kyi bu 'di rnams la dbang rtags rdo rje dril bu gtad de dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)004:8159: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pas 'gro ba
NK029(ha)004:8160: sens can gyi don rgyun mi 'chad pa byed pa'i
NK029(ha)004:8161: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:8162: ces brjod nas dbang phyug dbang khri la 'dug /
NK029(ha)004:8163: zhabs g.yas pas slob bu'i mgo la bzhag cing /
NK029(ha)004:8164: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyis /
NK029(ha)004:8165: rdo rje sems dpa' nga yin pas /
NK029(ha)004:8166: nga yi ji skad sgo ba bzhin /
NK029(ha)004:8167: bu khyod kyis ni bya dgos so //
NK029(ha)004:8169: gnyis pa ni dbang phyug bzhengs ste /
NK029(ha)004:8170: dbus kyi bum pa phyag du bzhes la /
NK029(ha)004:8171: dbu brgyan cod pan 'phreng ba dang //
NK029(ha)004:8172: go cha rgya mtshan phyag rgya dang //
NK029(ha)004:8173: gdugs dang bum pa bza' btung dang //
NK029(ha)004:8174: snying po lnga yi dbang bskur bas //
NK029(ha)004:8175: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK029(ha)004:8176: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK029(ha)004:8177: tshe rings bde ba phun sums tshogs //
NK029(ha)004:8178: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK029(ha)004:8181: slob bu rnams la slud cing /
NK029(ha)004:8182: tish+tha badz+ra zhes pas dbang brtan par bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:8183: bden pa bdag rdo rje che ge mos /
NK029(ha)004:8184: rdo rje che ge mo la sogs pa'i /
NK029(ha)004:8185: slob bu rnams sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i dbang bskur bas /
NK029(ha)004:8187: ngan song gsum la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal thams cad bral nas /
NK029(ha)004:8188: mtho ris bde ba phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan ste /
NK029(ha)004:8189: de las kyang rgyal ba'i sras /
NK029(ha)004:8190: rigs phun sum tshogs pa'i sras su nges par dbang gi 'bras bu ma lus pa thob nas /
NK029(ha)004:8191: srid pa'i sem can mtha' dag gi don yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:8193: rgyal khams thams cad du dus kyi 'khrug pa zhi bar gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:8194: mtshon gyi skal pa nyams par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:8195: mi nad phyug nad thams cad rgyun chad par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:8196: char chu dus su phebs par lo chu rtag tu legs ste /
NK029(ha)004:8197: sems can thams cad bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa'i bskal pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK029(ha)004:8200: dbang bac+wa brgyad kyi dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa rnams bsogs la /
NK029(ha)004:8201: dbang phyug kun tu bzang por gsal ba'i thugs kha'i h+aum las 'od 'phros pas /
NK029(ha)004:8202: dbang rdzas rnams rim pas sngar rab tu gnas pa'i lha gsal btab /
NK029(ha)004:8204: dbang phyug gi bskur gnas rnams su /
NK029(ha)004:8205: rang rang gi dbang rdzas gtugs pas /
NK029(ha)004:8206: 'od du zhu nas rang rang gi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu la bstim pas /
NK029(ha)004:8207: sngar bas kyang nus pa cher skyes par bsam la /
NK029(ha)004:8208: dbang rdzas thams cad kyi rab gnas bsdu ba zin pa dang /
NK029(ha)004:8209: slar yang thugs kha'i h+aum las 'od 'phros ste /
NK029(ha)004:8210: sngar dpang po'i tshul du bzhugs pa'i mdun gyi nam
NK029(ha)004:8211: mkha'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'od du zhu
NK029(ha)004:8212: nas dbang phyug la thim pas /
NK029(ha)004:8213: 'od dang gzi byin dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)004:8214: de nas slob bu rnams kyis phyag byas nas /
NK029(ha)004:8215: gus pa'i tshul gyis gnyis med rgyal ba'i mchog la rab gnas shing /
NK029(ha)004:8216: sku gsung thugs kyi rol pa cir ston pa'i /
NK029(ha)004:8217: bla med sman pa'i rgyal po dgongs su gsol /
NK029(ha)004:8218: zang zing rdzas kyi dgos pas ma 'brel kyang /
NK029(ha)004:8219: bdag 'dzin sdug bsngal rtogs pas bcings pa yi /
NK029(ha)004:8220: 'khor ba'i 'dam rdzab klong nas drangs pa'i phyir /
NK029(ha)004:8221: sbyor bas dmigs pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol /
NK029(ha)004:8223: sngar lus phul 'dod pa'i slob bu rnams kyis /
NK029(ha)004:8224: ci 'byor pa'i yon gyis lus bslu bar bya'o /
NK029(ha)004:8225: bzhi pa slob bu'i gtso bos /
NK029(ha)004:8226: ka pa la mtshan dang ldan pa bdud rtsis bkang ba mar chol dang bcas pa btegs la /
NK029(ha)004:8227: khyod ni ye nas sku gsung thugs kyi dpal //
NK029(ha)004:8228: dpal gyi phyag rgya mang po thob pa'i phyir //
NK029(ha)004:8229: dus gsum kun tu sangs rgyas yin pa'i rtags //
NK029(ha)004:8230: rdo rje che mchog khyod la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK029(ha)004:8232: dbang phyug zhal du grangs la /
NK029(ha)004:8234: de yang dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i dus su /
NK029(ha)004:8237: rtsa rgyud kyi lung dang mi 'gal bar phul la /
NK029(ha)004:8239: smin lam rgya chen bro gdab po /
NK029(ha)004:8243: lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa nas /
NK029(ha)004:8244: lhag phud bsre ba'i bar byas la /
NK029(ha)004:8246: lhag chog btang zhing bstan ma bskyang nas /
NK029(ha)004:8247: gtor ma rin chen mchod bstod gyis /
NK029(ha)004:8248: sems can thams cad yid la gang 'dod pa tshim par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:8249: drug pa thog mar dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kun bzang zhabs bsil /
NK029(ha)004:8250: bzhi bsnol gyis btang rag gi tshul du mchod nas /
NK029(ha)004:8251: yi ge brgya bas lhag chad bskang zhing /
NK029(ha)004:8254: dbang phyug gi ngo bo bsdams te /
NK029(ha)004:8255: shar sgo'i tshangs thig gi lam nas h+aum zhes brjod cing /
NK029(ha)004:8256: dbus kyi gtso bo'i gnas kyi bar du bsdu /
NK029(ha)004:8260: byang nas kyang de gzhal yas khang lha la bsdu /
NK029(ha)004:8262: gtso bo thugs ka'i sa bon la bsdu /
NK029(ha)004:8263: sa bon yang na dkyil 'khor la bsdu ste /
NK029(ha)004:8264: yang na me long la has btab pa bzhin du yal nas /
NK029(ha)004:8265: stong pa nyid kyi ngang la cung zhig bzhag /
NK029(ha)004:8268: ri mthon po'i rtse la skyal /
NK029(ha)004:8270: bum chu don du gnyer pa yod na sbyin /
NK029(ha)004:8271: med na mis ma 'gong pa'i sar spo /
NK029(ha)004:8272: rdzas dang yo byad rnams dben par 'tshags bya'o /
NK029(ha)004:8273: de ltar rtag pa'i mtha' bsal nas /
NK029(ha)004:8274: slar yang chad pa'i mtha' bsal ba'i don du /
NK029(ha)004:8275: skadaciga dran rdzogs su yi dam gang yin du rang nyid gsal btab la go bsgo /
NK029(ha)004:8277: dbang nod spyod lam ba zhir /
NK029(ha)004:8278: yi dam lha'i nga rgyal dang ldan zhing /
NK029(ha)004:8280: 'og phyogs kyi phur pa nas rtsams /
NK029(ha)004:8281: mtshams phur bcu po lugs bzlog tu bsdus la /
NK029(ha)004:8282: phur pa'i lha ye shes pa gshegs /
NK029(ha)004:8283: dam tshig pa bdag yi dam lha'i thugs khar bsdu'o //
NK029(ha)004:8284: de nas sgo byang bsdus te /
NK029(ha)004:8285: lha'i sgo byang ye shes pa gshegs /
NK029(ha)004:8286: dam tshig pa bdag la bsdu /
NK029(ha)004:8289: de nas phyi'i rgyal chen gyi tho rnams lugs bzlog tu bsdus ste /
NK029(ha)004:8290: sngar tho 'dzugs pa'i dus kyi mchod pa bzhin btang rag gi mchod la /
NK029(ha)004:8291: rgyal chen gshegs su gsol lo //
NK029(ha)004:8295: khud dkar po gtsang ma'i steng du /
NK029(ha)004:8296: ci 'byor pa'i bkra shis kyi rdzas /
NK029(ha)004:8297: bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs la /
NK029(ha)004:8299: bkra shis rab mchog dang bkra shis brgyad pa la sogs pa brjod cing /
NK029(ha)004:8300: bkra shis kyi rdzas dkyil 'khor rol par bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:8302: chos skyong gzhi bdag la btang rag btang ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:8303: skye bo la sbyin pa gtong ba la sogs pa bya'o //
NK029(ha)004:8304: de dag ni dbang bskur ba dang /
NK029(ha)004:8305: gnas bsrungs ba'i las kyi rim pa ste /
NK029(ha)004:8306: nub bzhi pa ste tha ma'i cho ga'o //
